data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A medical student who becomes a zombie joins a Coroner's Office in order to gain access to the brains she must reluctantly eat so that she can maintain her humanity. But every brain she eats, she also inherits their memories and must now solve their deaths with help from the Medical examiner and a police detective.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Crimson Peak
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In the aftermath of a family tragedy, an aspiring author is torn between love for her childhood friend and the temptation of a mysterious outsider. Trying to escape the ghosts of her past, she is swept away to a house that breathes, bleeds… and remembers.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Supergirl
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Twenty-four-year-old Kara Zor-El, who was taken in by the Danvers family when she was 13 after being sent away from Krypton, must learn to embrace her powers after previously hiding them. The Danvers teach her to be careful with her powers, until she has to reveal them during an unexpected disaster, setting her on her journey of heroism.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sense8
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: One gunshot, one death, one moment out of time that irrevocably links eight minds in disparate parts of the world, putting them in each other's lives, each other's secrets, and in terrible danger. Ordinary people suddenly reborn as "Sensates."

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bāhubali: The Beginning
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The young Shivudu is left as a foundling in a small village by his mother. By the time he’s grown up, it has become apparent that he possesses exceptional gifts. He meets the beautiful warrior princess Avanthika and learns that her queen has been held captive for the last 25 years. Shividu sets off to rescue her, discovering his own origins in the process.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ouija: Origin of Evil
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In 1965 Los Angeles, a widowed mother and her two daughters add a new stunt to bolster their séance scam business and unwittingly invite authentic evil into their home. When the youngest daughter is overtaken by the merciless spirit, this small family confronts unthinkable fears to save her and send her possessor back to the other side.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Wynonna Earp
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Wyatt Earp's great granddaughter Wynonna battles demons and other creatures with her unique abilities and a posse of dysfunctional allies - the only thing that can bring the paranormal to justice.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Unbreakable Kimmy Schmidt
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When a woman is rescued from a doomsday cult and lands in New York City, she must navigate a world she didn’t think even existed anymore.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sinister 2
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A young mother and her twin sons move into a rural house that's marked for death.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Edge of Seventeen
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Two high school girls are best friends until one dates the other's older brother, who is totally his sister's nemesis.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: London Has Fallen
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In London for the Prime Minister's funeral, Mike Banning discovers a plot to assassinate all the attending world leaders.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Good Witch
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description:
Cassie Nightingale, Middleton’s favorite enchantress, and her young-teenage daughter Grace, who shares that same special intuition as her mom, welcome Dr. Sam Radford and his son to town. When the New York transplants move in next to the Grey House, they are immediately spellbound by the mother-daughter duo next door, but Sam and Cassie quickly find they may not see eye to eye. With her signature charm, Cassie attempts to bring everyone together, ensuring all of Middleton is in for new changes, big surprises and, of course, a little bit of magic!

"Good Witch” is based on Bell’s beloved character Cassie, the raven-haired enchantress who kept audiences spellbound for seven installments of Hallmark Channel's longest-running and highest-rated original movie franchise of all time.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Kung Fu Panda 3
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Continuing his "legendary adventures of awesomeness", Po must face two hugely epic, but different threats: one supernatural and the other a little closer to his home.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Hush
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A deaf woman is stalked by a psychotic killer in her secluded home.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mr. Right
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A girl falls for the "perfect" guy, who happens to have a very fatal flaw: he's a hitman on the run from the crime cartels who employ him.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Boy
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An American nanny is shocked that her new English family's boy is actually a life-sized doll. After she violates a list of strict rules, disturbing events make her believe that the doll is really alive.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Wet Hot American Summer: First Day of Camp
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: It's the first day of camp in this outrageous prequel to the hilarious 2001 cult classic movie. And at Camp Firewood, anything can happen.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Love
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Rebellious Mickey and good-natured Gus navigate the thrills and agonies of modern relationships.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Zoo
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Set amidst a wave of violent animal attacks sweeping across the planet, a young renegade scientist is thrust into a race to unlock the mystery behind this pandemic before time runs out for animals and humans alike.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Steve Jobs
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Set backstage at three iconic product launches and ending in 1998 with the unveiling of the iMac, Steve Jobs takes us behind the scenes of the digital revolution to paint an intimate portrait of the brilliant man at its epicenter.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Conjuring 2
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: New Line Cinema's supernatural thriller The Conjuring 2, with James Wan (Furious 7) once again at the helm following the record-breaking success of The Conjuring, brings to the screen another real case from the files of renowned demonologists Ed and Lorraine Warren. Reprising their roles, Oscar nominee Vera Farmiga (Up In the Air, TV's Bates Motel) and Patrick Wilson (the Insidious films), star as Lorraine and Ed Warren, who, in one of their most terrifying paranormal investigations, travel to north London to help a single mother raising four children alone in a house plagued by malicious spirits.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Home
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When Earth is taken over by the overly-confident Boov, an alien race in search of a new place to call home, all humans are promptly relocated, while all Boov get busy reorganizing the planet. But when one resourceful girl, Tip, manages to avoid capture, she finds herself the accidental accomplice of a banished Boov named Oh. The two fugitives realize there’s a lot more at stake than intergalactic relations as they embark on the road trip of a lifetime.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Chappie
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Every child comes into the world full of promise, and none more so than Chappie: he is gifted, special, a prodigy. Like any child, Chappie will come under the influence of his surroundings—some good, some bad—and he will rely on his heart and soul to find his way in the world and become his own man. But there's one thing that makes Chappie different from any one else: he is a robot.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: BUNK'D
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Siblings Emma, Ravi, and Zuri Ross leave their extravagant New York City penthouse once again to return to Camp Kikiwaka, a rustic summer camp in Maine where their parents met as teenagers.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: In a Valley of Violence
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The story of a drifter named Paul who arrives in a small town seeking revenge on the thugs who murdered his friend. Sisters Mary Anne and Ellen, who run the town's hotel, help Paul in his quest for vengeance.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: A Monster Calls
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A boy imagines a monster that helps him deal with his difficult life and see the world in a different way.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Van Helsing
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Vanessa Helsing, the daughter of famous vampire hunter and Dracula nemesis Abraham Van Helsing is resurrected five years in the future to find out that vampires have taken over the world and that she possesses unique power over them. She is humanity’s last hope to lead an offensive to take back what has been lost.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Christine
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In the 1970s, a television reporter Christine Chubbuck struggles with depression and professional frustrations as she tries to advance her career.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Quantico
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A diverse group of recruits has arrived at the FBI Quantico Base for training. They are the best, the brightest and the most vetted, so it seems impossible that one of them is suspected of masterminding the biggest attack on New York City since 9/11.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Loving
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The story of Richard and Mildred Loving, an interracial couple, whose challenge of their anti-miscegenation arrest for their marriage in Virginia led to a legal battle that would end at the US Supreme Court.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Danish Girl
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When Gerda Wegener asks her husband Einar to fill in as a portrait model, Einar discovers the person she's meant to be and begins living her life as Lili Elbe. Having realized her true self and with Gerda's love and support, Lili embarks on a groundbreaking journey as a transgender pioneer.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: F is for Family
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Follow the Murphy family back to the 1970s, when kids roamed wild, beer flowed freely and nothing came between a man and his TV.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Master of None
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: 30-year-old New York actor Dev takes on such pillars of maturity as the first big job, a serious relationship, and busting sex offenders on the subway.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Hap and Leonard
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A darkly comic swamp noir story of two best friends set in the late 1980s. Based on the novels by Joe R. Lansdale, the series follows Hap Collins, an East Texas white boy with a weakness for Southern women, and Leonard Pine, a gay, black Vietnam vet with a hot temper.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Easy
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This eclectic, star-studded anthology follows diverse Chicagoans fumbling through the modern maze of love, sex, technology and culture. First dates, friends with benefits, couples with kids. Whatever your relationship status is, it's always complicated.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Ranch
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Being a pro athlete didn't pan out for Colt. Now he's helping his dad and brother keep the ranch afloat, and figuring out how he fits into the family.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The DUFF
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Bianca's universe turns upside down when she learns that her high school refers to her as a ‘DUFF' (Designated Ugly Fat Friend). Hoping to erase that label, she enlists the help of a charming jock and her favorite teacher. Together they'll face the school's mean girl and remind everyone that we are all someone's DUFF… and that's totally fine.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Unfriended
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: While video chatting one night, six high school friends receive a Skype message from a classmate who killed herself exactly one year ago. At first they think it's a prank, but when the girl starts revealing the friends' darkest secrets, they realize they are dealing with something out of this world, something that wants them dead.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Self/less
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An extremely wealthy elderly man dying from cancer undergoes a radical medical procedure that transfers his consciousness to the body of a healthy young man but everything may not be as good as it seems when he starts to uncover the mystery of the body's origins and the secret organization that will kill to keep its secrets.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Making a Murderer
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Filmed over 10 years, this real-life thriller follows a DNA exoneree who, while exposing police corruption, becomes a suspect in a grisly new crime.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Fundamentals of Caring
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Having suffered a tragedy, Ben becomes a caregiver to earn money. His first client, Trevor, is a hilarious 18-year-old with muscular dystrophy. One paralyzed emotionally, one paralyzed physically, Ben and Trevor hit the road on a trip into the western states. The folks they collect along the way will help them test their skills for surviving outside their calculated existence. Together, they come to understand the importance of hope and the necessity of true friendship.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Hello, My Name Is Doris
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A self-help seminar inspires a sixty-something woman to romantically pursue her younger co-worker.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Spectral
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A special-ops team is dispatched to fight supernatural beings that have taken over a European city.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Other People
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: David, a struggling comedy writer fresh off from breaking up with his boyfriend, moves from New York City to Sacramento to help his sick mother. Living with his conservative father and much-younger sisters for the first time in ten years, he feels like a stranger in his childhood home. As his mother’s health declines, David frantically tries to extract meaning from this horrible experience and convince everyone (including himself) that he's "doing okay.”

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Circle
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a massive, mysterious chamber, fifty strangers awaken to find themselves trapped with no memory of how they got there. Organized in an inward-facing circle and unable to move, they quickly learn that every two minutes, one of them must die... executed by a strange device in the center of the room.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Fuller House
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: D.J. Tanner-Fuller is a widow and mother of three. Things become too much to handle, so she asks for help from her sister Stephanie and her best-friend Kimmy.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Batman: The Killing Joke
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: As Batman hunts for the escaped Joker, the Clown Prince of Crime attacks the Gordon family to prove a diabolical point mirroring his own fall into madness.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Chef's Table
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In this Emmy-nominated docuseries, find out what's inside the kitchens and minds of the international culinary stars who are redefining gourmet food.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: He Never Died
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Jack is a solitary man with a mysterious past. His strange habits will soon become stranger when his past catches up with him.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: American Ultra
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Mike is an unmotivated stoner whose small-town life with his live-in girlfriend, Phoebe, is suddenly turned upside down.  Unbeknownst to him, Mike is actually a highly trained, lethal sleeper agent. In the blink of an eye, as his secret past comes back to haunt him, Mike is thrust into the middle of a deadly government operation and is forced to summon his inner action-hero in order to survive.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: 13th
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An in-depth look at the prison system in the United States and how it reveals the nation's history of racial inequality.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Aquarius
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In the late 1960s, a Los Angeles police sergeant with a complicated personal life starts tracking a small-time criminal and budding cult leader seeking out vulnerable women to join his “cause.” The name of that man is Charles Manson.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Frequency
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Detective Raimy Sullivan is stunned when a voice suddenly crackles through her father’s old, long-broken ham radio – it’s Frank Sullivan, somehow transmitting over the airwaves and through the decades from 1996. Separated by twenty years, father and daughter have reunited on a frequency only they can hear, but can they rewrite the story of their lives without risking everyone they love?

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Before I Wake
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In this intense and heart pounding supernatural thriller, Jessie (Kate Bosworth) and Mark (Thomas Jane) decide to take in a sweet and loving 8-year-old boy, Cody. Unbeknownst to them, Cody is terrified of falling asleep. At first, they assume his previous unstable homes caused his aversion to sleep, but soon discover why: Cody's dreams manifest in reality as he sleeps. In one moment they experience the incredible wonder of Cody's imagination, and in the next, the horrific nature of his night terrors. To save their new family, Jessie and Mark embark on a dangerous hunt to uncover the truth behind Cody's nightmares.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Blue Jay
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Meeting by chance when they return to their tiny California hometown, two former high-school sweethearts reflect on their shared past.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Greenleaf
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The unscrupulous world of the Greenleaf family and their sprawling Memphis megachurch, where scandalous secrets and lies are as numerous as the faithful. Born of the church, the Greenleaf family love and care for each other, but beneath the surface lies a den of iniquity—greed, adultery, sibling rivalry and conflicting values—that threatens to tear apart the very core of their faith that holds them together.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Advantageous
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a near-future city where soaring opulence overshadows economic hardship, Gwen and her daughter, Jules, do all they can to hold on to their joy, despite the instability surfacing in their world.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Gilmore Girls: A Year in the Life
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Set nearly a decade after the finale of the original series, this revival follows Lorelai, Rory and Emily Gilmore through four seasons of change.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Collateral Beauty
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Retreating from life after a tragedy, a man questions the universe by writing to Love, Time and Death. Receiving unexpected answers, he begins to see how these things interlock and how even loss can reveal moments of meaning and beauty.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Last Chance U
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a docuseries set at one of NCAA football's most fertile recruiting grounds, guys with red flags seek to prove their worth on the field and in class.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Beasts of No Nation
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Based on the experiences of Agu, a child fighting in the civil war of an unnamed, fictional West African country. Follows Agu's journey as he's forced to join a group of soldiers. While he fears his commander and many of the men around him, his fledgling childhood has been brutally shattered by the war raging through his country, and he is at first torn between conflicting revulsion and fascination.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: ARQ
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Two old friends living in a dystopic future become trapped in a mysterious time loop — one that may have something to do with an ongoing battle between an omnipotent corporation and a ragtag band of rebels.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Forest
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Set in the Aokigahara Forest, a real-life place in Japan where people go to end their lives. Against this backdrop, a young American woman comes in search of her twin sister, who has mysteriously disappeared.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Roman Empire
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This stylish mix of documentary and historical epic chronicles the reign of Commodus, the emperor whose rule marked the beginning of Rome's fall.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Reply 1988
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A nostalgic trip back to the late 1980s through the lives of five families and their five teenage kids living in a small neighborhood in Seoul.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Reply 1988
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A nostalgic trip back to the late 1980s through the lives of five families and their five teenage kids living in a small neighborhood in Seoul.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: What Happened, Miss Simone?
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The film chronicles Nina Simone's journey from child piano prodigy to iconic musician and passionate activist, told in her own words.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Get Down
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In 1977 New York City, the talented and soulful youth of the South Bronx chase dreams and breakneck beats to transform music history.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Bye Bye Man
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When three college students move into an old house off campus, they unwittingly unleash a supernatural entity known as The Bye Bye Man, who comes to prey upon them once they discover his name. The friends must try to save each other, all the while keeping The Bye Bye Man's existence a secret to save others from the same deadly fate.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Trollhunters: Tales of Arcadia
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After uncovering a mysterious amulet, an average teen assumes an unlikely destiny and sets out to save two worlds.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Voltron: Legendary Defender
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Five unlikely teenage heroes and their flying robot lions unite to form the megapowerful Voltron and defend the universe from evil.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Transformers: Robots In Disguise
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Years after the events of Predacons Rising, Bumblebee is summoned back to Earth to battle several of Cybertron's most wanted Decepticons that escaped from a crashed prison ship and assembles a team of young Autobots that includes Sideswipe (a rebel "bad boy bot"), Strongarm (an Elite Guard cadet), Grimlock (a bombastic Dinobot), and Fixit (a hyperactive Mini-Con with faulty wiring).

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Space Between Us
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In this interplanetary adventure, a space shuttle embarks on the first mission to colonize Mars, only to discover after takeoff that one of the astronauts is pregnant. Shortly after landing, she dies from complications while giving birth to the first human born on the red planet – never revealing who the father is. Thus begins the extraordinary life of Gardner Elliot – an inquisitive, highly intelligent boy who reaches the age of 16 having only met 14 people in his very unconventional upbringing.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Demonic
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A police officer and a psychologist investigate the deaths of five people who were killed while trying to summon ghosts.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Winter on Fire: Ukraine's Fight for Freedom
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A documentary on the unrest in Ukraine during 2013 and 2014, as student demonstrations supporting European integration grew into a violent revolution calling for the resignation of President Viktor F. Yanukovich.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mascots
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Eager contestants don big heads and furry suits to vie for the title of World's Best Mascot.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Visaranai
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Pandi and his friends, immigrant workers in Andhra Pradesh, are picked up by cops for a crime they never committed. And thus begins their nightmare, where they become pawns in a vicious game where the voiceless are strangled by those with power.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Lady Dynamite
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A single-camera half-hour comedy based on what Maria Bamford has accepted to be "her life." It's the sometimes surreal story of a woman who loses — and then finds — her s**t.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: By the Sea
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Set in France during the mid-1970s, Vanessa, a former dancer, and her husband Roland, an American writer, travel the country together. They seem to be growing apart, but when they linger in one quiet, seaside town they begin to draw close to some of its more vibrant inhabitants, such as a local bar/café-keeper and a hotel owner.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Team Foxcatcher
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: With never-before seen home video, this film recounts the paranoid downward spiral of John E. du Pont and the murder of Olympic wrestler Dave Schultz.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Signal
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Detectives from the present and a detective from the past communicate via walkie-talkie to solve a long-time unsolved case.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Signal
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Detectives from the present and a detective from the past communicate via walkie-talkie to solve a long-time unsolved case.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Ridiculous 6
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When his long-lost outlaw father returns, Tommy "White Knife" Stockburn goes on an adventure-filled journey across the Old West with his five brothers.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bo Burnham: Make Happy
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Combining his trademark wit and self-deprecating humor with original music, Bo Burnham offers up his unique twist on life in this stand-up special about  life, death, sexuality, hypocrisy, mental illness and Pringles cans.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Do-Over
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The life of a bank manager is turned upside down when a friend from his past manipulates him into faking his own death and taking off on an adventure.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Flaked
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In his funky California beach enclave, Chip's the go-to guy for personal insights. But he isn't quite as enlightened when it comes to his own baggage.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Jem and the Holograms
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: As a small-town girl catapults from underground video sensation to global superstar, she and her three sisters begin a one-in-a-million journey of discovering that some talents are too special to keep hidden. Four aspiring musicians will take the world by storm when they see that the key to creating your own destiny lies in finding your own voice.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sleight
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A young street magician is left to take care of his little sister after his mother's passing and turns to drug dealing in the Los Angeles party scene to keep a roof over their heads. When he gets into trouble with his supplier, his sister is kidnapped and he is forced to rely on both his sleight of hand and brilliant mind to save her.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Hot Girls Wanted
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A first-ever look at the realities of the professional “amateur” porn world and the steady stream of 18-to-19-year old girls entering into it.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: White Rabbit Project
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Kari Byron, Tory Belleci and Grant Imahara rank history's greatest inventions, heists and more.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Cinderella and Four Knights
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Eun Ha-Won is a college student. She is a bright girl who wants to be a veterinarian, but at home she is lonely. She is isolated from her family members. Eun Ha-Won lives with father, step-mother and step-sister after her mother died in a car accident. One day, she helps a mysterious old man. The old man suggests to her to live in a mansion and pursue her dream of becoming a veterinarian. Since than, she moves into the mansion and lives with three cousins Kang Ji-Woon, Kang Hyun-Min, Kang Seo-Woo and their bodyguard Lee Yoon-Sung.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Cinderella and Four Knights
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Eun Ha-Won is a college student. She is a bright girl who wants to be a veterinarian, but at home she is lonely. She is isolated from her family members. Eun Ha-Won lives with father, step-mother and step-sister after her mother died in a car accident. One day, she helps a mysterious old man. The old man suggests to her to live in a mansion and pursue her dream of becoming a veterinarian. Since than, she moves into the mansion and lives with three cousins Kang Ji-Woon, Kang Hyun-Min, Kang Seo-Woo and their bodyguard Lee Yoon-Sung.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: I Am the Pretty Thing That Lives in the House
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A young nurse takes care of elderly author who lives in a haunted house.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Pee-wee's Big Holiday
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A fateful meeting with a mysterious stranger inspires Pee-wee Herman to take his first-ever holiday.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: White Girl
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Summer, New York City. A college girl falls hard for a guy she just met. After a night of partying goes wrong, she goes to wild extremes to get him back.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Haunted House
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: With help from a 102-year-old goblin dwelling beneath their haunted apartment building, two siblings deal with ghosts and take on spooky mysteries.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Haunted House
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: With help from a 102-year-old goblin dwelling beneath their haunted apartment building, two siblings deal with ghosts and take on spooky mysteries.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Frank & Lola
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A talented Las Vegas chef falls in love with an aspiring fashion designer but turns violently jealous when he realizes that she's hiding dark secrets.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dinotrux
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Half dinosaur, half construction truck, full-on fun! Watch giant Ty Rux, his little buddy Revvit and the crew come face-to-face with evil D-Structs.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Barry
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A biopic of Barack Obama set during his time as a college student in New York City.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dawn of the Croods
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The world's first family is back for more laughs as they discover sports, sleepovers and other wonders in a world of exotic creatures and adventures. This 2D animated cartoon is based on the 3D animated feature film, "The Croods".

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The world's greatest feline fighter, lover and milk connoisseur is back in this original series filled with daring adventures, great boots, and laugh-out-loud fun! The entire family will be entranced by Puss' fantastical CG world filled with new characters, exotic locations and mystical tales that make up the stuff of legends. There's nothing that can get in this celebrated swashbuckling kitty's way...except maybe a hairball.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Front Cover
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: One man does all he can to veil his Asian heritage; the other takes great pains to hide his sexual orientation. Both of these things begin to change when Ryan is hired to prepare film star Ning for a fashion shoot, and the men develop a bond.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: T@gged
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: T@gged is a modern day thriller that explores the terrifying risks of social media in a world of anonymity.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ratchet & Clank
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When the galaxy comes under the threat of a nefarious space captain, a mechanic and his newfound robot ally join an elite squad of combatants to save the universe.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Darkness
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A family returns from a Grand Canyon vacation with a supernatural presence in tow.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The K2
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A patriotic bodyguard who was abandoned by his country and colleagues, a hidden daughter of leading Presidential candidate who regards love as a tool for revenge, and the First Lady contender who hides her ambition and charisma behind a kind and friendly personality.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The K2
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A patriotic bodyguard who was abandoned by his country and colleagues, a hidden daughter of leading Presidential candidate who regards love as a tool for revenge, and the First Lady contender who hides her ambition and charisma behind a kind and friendly personality.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Marco Polo: One Hundred Eyes
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Before he lost his sight. Before he pledged his service to Kublai Khan. Hundred Eyes saw what made him into the deadly assassin who trains Marco Polo.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Netflix Presents: The Characters
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: No rules. No expectations. A half hour to make their mark. Eight different comedians each get an episode to show their skills in comedy.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: W/ Bob & David
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After being dishonorably discharged from the Navy Seals, Bob and David are back serving our country the way they do best, making sketch comedy. Four half-hours of brand new comedy featuring all new characters, all new scenes, and most importantly, all new wigs.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Mr. Peabody & Sherman Show
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The world's smartest dog and his boy host a zany late-night comedy show from a swanky penthouse, with time-traveling historical figures and a live audience.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Care Bears and Cousins
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Care Bears and Cousins

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Tramps
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A young man and woman find love in an unlikely place while carrying out a shady deal.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dragons: Race to the Edge
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Unlock the secrets of the Dragon Eye and come face to face with more dragons than anyone has ever imagined as Hiccup, Toothless and the Dragon Riders soar to the edge of adventure.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: LEGO Marvel Super Heroes: Avengers Reassembled!
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The Avengers are forced to “party” with Ultron when he seeks to disassemble the team by taking control of Iron Man’s armor and enact a nefarious scheme to take over the world.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Special Correspondents
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A radio journalist and his technician get in over their heads when they hatch a scheme to fake their own kidnapping during a rebel uprising in South America and hide out in New York instead.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Baaghi
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Ronny is a rebellious man, who falls in love with Sia but circumstances separate them. Years later, Ronny learns that Sia is abducted by a martial arts champion, Raghav.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Tallulah
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Desperate to be rid of her toddler, a dissatisfied Beverly Hills housewife hires a stranger to babysit and ends up getting much more than she bargained for.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bert Kreischer: The Machine
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Storyteller Bert Kreischer expounds on a series of incredible and hilarious tales - from an unforgettable run-in with a grizzly bear to his legendary travels in Russia.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Amanda Knox
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This gripping, atmospheric documentary recounts the infamous trial, conviction and eventual acquittal of Seattle native Amanda Knox for the 2007 murder of a British exchange student in Italy.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sniper: Ghost Shooter
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Elite snipers Brandon Beckett and Richard Miller are tasked with protecting a gas pipeline from terrorists looking to make a statement. When battles with the enemy lead to snipers being killed by a ghost shooter who knows their exact location, tensions boil as a security breach is suspected. Is there someone working with the enemy on the inside? Is the mission a front for other activity? Is the Colonel pulling the strings?

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bella and the Bulldogs
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A head cheerleader's life takes an unexpected twist when her rifle-like throwing arm takes her from the sidelines to becoming her middle school’s starting quarterback. Bella Dawson is a confident, caring and talented teenager, who suddenly finds herself fulfilling a lifelong dream but also having to navigate the world of her teammates Troy, Sawyer and Newt, without losing her two best friends, Pepper and Sophie from the cheer squad.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Results
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Two mismatched personal trainers' lives are upended by the actions of a new, wealthy client.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sebastian Maniscalco: Why Would You Do That?
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Comedian Sebastian Maniscalco performs his third Showtime special at the Beacon Theatre in Manhattan.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Chelsea Does
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Comedienne and writer Chelsea Handler discusses the topics of marriage, racism, Silicon Valley, and drugs. Filmed in four parts.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Young Messiah
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Tells the story of Jesus Christ at age seven as he and his family depart Egypt to return home to Nazareth. Told from his childhood perspective, it follows young Jesus as he grows into his religious identity.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ask the Storybots
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Based on the award-winning educational apps, the StoryBots are curious little creatures who live in the world beneath our screens and go on fun adventures to help answer kids' questions, like how night happens or why we need to brush our teeth.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Term Life
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: If Nick Barrow can stay alive for 21 days, he'll die happy. Everyone Nick knows wants him dead; Mob bosses, contract killers, and dirty cops. Performing the last act of a desperate man, Nick takes out a million dollar insurance policy on himself, payable to his estranged daughter. The problem? The policy doesn't take effect for 21 days. Nick knows they'll be lucky to be alive for twenty-one hours.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: For the Love of Spock
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The life of Star Trek's Mr. Spock — as well as that of Leonard Nimoy, the actor who played Mr. Spock for almost fifty years —written and directed by his son, Adam.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: John Mulaney: The Comeback Kid
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Armed with boyish charm and a sharp wit, the former "SNL" writer offers sly takes on marriage, his beef with babies and the time he met Bill Clinton.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Incarnate
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An exorcist comes up against an evil from his past when he uses his skills to enter the mind of a nine year old boy.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Cooked
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Explored through the lenses of the four natural elements – fire, water, air and earth – COOKED is an enlightening and compelling look at the evolution of what food means to us through the history of food preparation and its universal ability to connect us. Highlighting our primal human need to cook, the series urges a return to the kitchen to reclaim our lost traditions and to forge a deeper, more meaningful connection to the ingredients and cooking techniques that we use to nourish ourselves.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Kung Fu Panda: Secrets of the Scroll
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: As Po looks for his lost action figures, the story of how the panda inadvertently helped create the Furious Five is told.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: World of Winx
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The Winx travel all over the world searching for talent for WOW. and preventing the mysterious talent thief from kidnapping them.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Inspector Gadget
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When Dr. Claw returns, Inspector Gadget is brought out of retirement to defeat him again, now with Penny and Brain's open participation.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Anthony Jeselnik: Thoughts and Prayers
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: There's no subject too dark as the comedian skewers taboos and riffs on national tragedies before pulling back the curtain on his provocative style.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: LEGO Jurassic World: The Indominus Escape
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The scientists of Jurassic World create a captivating and terrifying new creature that loves hot dogs. But what happens when the hot dogs run out?

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Kong: King of the Apes
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Set in 2050, Kong becomes a wanted fugitive after wrecking havoc at Alcatraz Island’s Natural History and Marine Preserve. What most humans on the hunt for the formidable animal don’t realize, though, is that Kong was framed by an evil genius who plans to terrorize the world with an army of enormous robotic dinosaurs. As the only beast strong enough to save humanity from the mechanical dinos, Kong must rely on the help of three kids who know the truth about him.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Real Rob
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Centers around comedian Rob Schneider's real life while living in Hollywood.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Tokyo Trial
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In the wake of World War II, 11 Allied judges are tasked with weighing the fates of Japanese war criminals in a tense international trial.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Tig
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An intimate documentary that follows Tig Notaro, a Los Angeles based comedian, who just days after being diagnosed with invasive stage II breast cancer changed the course of her career with a poignant stand-up set that became legendary overnight. It explores Tig's extraordinary journey as her career ignites and as her life unfolds in grand and unexpected ways, all the while continuing to battle a life-threatening illness and falling in love.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Lego Bionicle: The Journey to One
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Six legendary heroes find themselves on an epic quest as they harness the power of nature's elements to defeat the forces of evil.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: No Tomorrow
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When a risk-averse, straight-arrowed, female procurement manager at an Amazon-like distribution center falls in love with a free-spirited man who lives life to the fullest because he believes the apocalypse is imminent, they embark on a quest together to fulfill their individual bucket lists, with comedic and poignant results.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Drishyam
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A simple, street-smart man tries to protect his family from a tough cop looking for his missing son.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Skylanders Academy
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Follow the heroic adventures of the Skylanders team, a group of heroes with unique elemental skills and personalities who travel the vast Skylands universe, protecting it from evil-doers and showing the next wave of Academy cadets how to do things the “Skylander way.”

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Lavender
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A photographer struggling with memory loss discovers her pictures may indicate something sinister is hitting close to home.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ali Wong: Baby Cobra
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Ali Wong might be seven-months pregnant, but there’s not a fetus in the world that can stop this acerbic and savage train of comedy from delivering a masterful hour of stand-up.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Septembers of Shiraz
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In this adaptation of the critically acclaimed debut novel by Iranian American author Dalia Sofer, a secular Jewish family is caught up in the maelstrom of the 1979 Iranian Revolution.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: A Very Murray Christmas
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Bill Murray worries no one will show up to his TV show due to a massive snowstorm in New York City. Through luck and perseverance, guests arrive at Gotham’s Carlyle Hotel to help him — dancing and singing in holiday spirit.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Audrie & Daisy
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A documentary film about three cases of rape, that includes the stories of two American high school students, Audrie Pott and Daisy Coleman. At the time of the sexual assaults, Pott was 15 and Coleman was 14 years old. After the assaults, the victims and their families were subjected to abuse and cyberbullying.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Chef's Table: France
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Sample the bold new flavors of France with chefs who are pushing the boundaries of fine dining and reinventing a rich culinary tradition.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Project Mc²
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: McKeyla, Adrienne, Bryden, and Camryn are four super smart and science-skilled girls recruited to join the spy organization, NOV8.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Pandora
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When an earthquake hits a Korean village housing a run-down nuclear power plant, a man risks his life to save the country from imminent disaster.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Pandora
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When an earthquake hits a Korean village housing a run-down nuclear power plant, a man risks his life to save the country from imminent disaster.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Nightmare Teacher
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A homeroom teacher of Yosan Private High School has an accident, and thus a substitute comes to fill in. Han Bong-Gu  is a mysterious man, and after strange occurrences the class president Ye-Rim tries to get to the bottom of this mystery.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Nightmare Teacher
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A homeroom teacher of Yosan Private High School has an accident, and thus a substitute comes to fill in. Han Bong-Gu  is a mysterious man, and after strange occurrences the class president Ye-Rim tries to get to the bottom of this mystery.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Keith Richards: Under the Influence
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A portrait of Keith Richards that takes us on a journey to discover the genesis of his sound as a songwriter, guitarist and performer.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Surviving Compton: Dre, Suge and Michel'le
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Discovered at a young age, the shy, squeaky-voiced Michel'le was plucked straight from South Central, Los Angeles and catapulted into the spotlight while riding N.W.A.'s rocket ride of early success. Surrounded by industry visionaries from Eazy-E to Tupack Skaur, Michel'le quickly climbed the charts, but her musical successes were soon overshadowed by betrayal and corruption. A nearly decade-long romance with the infamous Dr. Dre pushed her into a life tarnished by alcohol, drugs and violence until her savior came in the unlikely form of Suge Knight, co-founder of Death Row Records and Dre's business partner. Friendship would turn into a courtly romance, but the union Michel'le thought they had did not end happily ever after. With children from both men and a career to protect, Michel'le's voice became silenced by Compton's biggest power players. Until now.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Colin Quinn: The New York Story
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The "SNL" veteran performs his off-Broadway show about the history of New York and the people who shape its personality.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Hawaizaada
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In 1895, Shivkar Bapuji Talpade constructs and flies India's first unmanned plane, despite having the odds stacked against him.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Riot
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Copper Jack Stone purposefully orchestrates a bank robbery in order to be thrown into prison with the notorious Russian kingpin Balam. Balam is more than just a mob criminal; he's a very cunning and dangerous lord who controls the police force from behind bars. Balam lives in prison as a cover for his real power, which is King of the city. His cell is a lavish private room built specifically for him, inaccessible to most in the depths of the prison structure. Even the warden fears venturing into his area of the prison. However, even surrounded by his loyal henchmen and guards in his sectioned off fortress, Balam doesn't know Jack is coming for him to avenge his family, who Balam murdered in cold blood. Balam is tough... but Jack is tougher.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Richie Rich
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Richie Rich is a boy who turned vegetables into a clean energy source. As a result, Rich now has over a trillion dollars. Rich lives with his family in a mansion filled with toys, contraptions, and his best friends Darcy and Murray are always by his side, along with Irona, Richie's robot maid, his dad Cliff, who loves naps and is a bit dense, and his jealous sister Harper. Also, Darcy loves spending money and Murray doesn't want anything out of budget.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Kevin Hart: What Now?
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In Universal Pictures’ Kevin Hart: What Now?, comedic rock-star Kevin Hart follows up his 2013 hit stand-up concert movie Let Me Explain, which grossed $32 million domestically and became the third-highest live stand-up comedy movie of all time. Hart takes center stage in this groundbreaking, record-setting, sold-out performance of “What Now?”—filmed outdoors in front of 50,000 people at Philadelphia’s Lincoln Financial Field—marking the first time a comedian has ever performed to an at-capacity football stadium.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Legends of the Hidden Temple
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Three siblings who break away from a lackluster temple tour in a jungle finds themselves immersed in a real-life mission comprised of obstacles that they must complete in order to escape alive.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Veteran
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When an old collaborator gets severely injured, a veteran policeman tries to figure out the way to bring to justice the ultimately suspected aggressor, a spoiled young executive, heir to a mega corporation, who believes he is above the law.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Veteran
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When an old collaborator gets severely injured, a veteran policeman tries to figure out the way to bring to justice the ultimately suspected aggressor, a spoiled young executive, heir to a mega corporation, who believes he is above the law.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Opening Night
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A failed Broadway singer who now works as a production manager must save opening night on his new production by wrangling his eccentric cast and crew.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Raman Raghav 2.0
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A corrupt cop and a serial killer obsessed with a psychopath from the '60s get caught up in a ruthless cat-and-mouse game.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Another Miss Oh
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Two women working in the same industry with the exact same name keep getting their lives entangled both professionally and personally.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Another Miss Oh
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Two women working in the same industry with the exact same name keep getting their lives entangled both professionally and personally.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: 6 Years
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A young couple bound by a seemingly ideal love, begins to unravel as unexpected opportunities spin them down a volatile and violent path and threaten the future they had always imagined.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Unnatural Selection
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Three high school students decide to escape the mundane urban environment and embark on a fishing adventure.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ok Kanmani
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Adhi and Tara are in a live-in relationship but they are both unwilling to get married. How do they realize that marriage is just a natural progression of their relationship?

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: True Memoirs of an International Assassin
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After a publisher changes a writer's debut novel about a deadly assassin from fiction to nonfiction, the author finds himself thrust into the world of his lead character, and must take on the role of his character for his own survival.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dear My Friends
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Life is ever-delightful — and ever-challenging — for a group of friends in their twilight years as they rediscover themselves through love and family.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dear My Friends
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Life is ever-delightful — and ever-challenging — for a group of friends in their twilight years as they rediscover themselves through love and family.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Strange Weather
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Years after her son's suicide, a woman longs to confront both the past and a friend of his who took his business idea.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Sound of Your Heart
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Comedy following Cho Seok's ridiculous but hilarious adventures with his girlfriend-turned-wife Ae Bong, their dogs, older brother Jo Joon, and parents. Based on the popular webtoon series of the same name.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Sound of Your Heart
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Comedy following Cho Seok's ridiculous but hilarious adventures with his girlfriend-turned-wife Ae Bong, their dogs, older brother Jo Joon, and parents. Based on the popular webtoon series of the same name.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ordinary World
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Perry is a happily married father of two living a comfortable but sedate life in the suburbs. On the occasion of his 40th birthday, he seeks to revisit his former life as the lead singer in a popular punk band though his middle-aged reality quickly (and hilariously) clashes with the indulgences of his youth.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: El Chema
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Inspired by true events, This is the story of the most notorious drug kingpin the world had ever seen. A man known as El Chapo, the biggest international drug lord in history. The most important and influential man, in the history of Narcos. He changed the game with his spectacular escapes and innovative smuggling techniques.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mohenjo Daro
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: During the Indus valley civilization, an Indigo farmer strives for the justice and protection of the city of Mohenjo-Daro and its civilians from an evil politician.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Captive
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Documentary series reconstructing history's most complex, high-stakes hostage negotiations as kidnapping victims recount their terrifying ordeals.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dil Dhadakne Do
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: On a cruise to celebrate their parents' 30th wedding anniversary, a brother and sister deal with the impact of family considerations on their romantic lives.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Hello, My Twenties!
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: With different personalities, life goals and taste in men, five female college students become housemates in a shared residence called Belle Epoque.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Hello, My Twenties!
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: With different personalities, life goals and taste in men, five female college students become housemates in a shared residence called Belle Epoque.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Haters Back Off
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Delve into the oddball family life of Miranda Sings, an incredibly confident, totally untalented star on the rise, who continues to fail upward by the power of her belief that she was born famous, it's just no one knows it yet.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Gabbar Is Back
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A vigilante network taking out corrupt officials draws the notice of the authorities.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Demetri Martin: Live (At The Time)
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Demetri Martin brings his off-kilter take on acoustic guitar, hairless cats, color schemes, and the word "nope" to Washington in his original special.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: 4K Fireplace
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Enjoy this crackling fireplace during a holiday party or a cozy night in. Shot in stunning 4K Ultra HD, this music-free fireplace video flickers, crackles and adds warmth to any room. Loop video playback for continuous enjoyment.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Talvar
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A hardened cop deals with three conflicting perspectives involving a brutal double murder. The case is complicated as the prime suspects are the parents who supposedly killed their teenage daughter.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Brothers
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: David and Monty, estranged half-brothers, train in mixed martial arts to earn a livelihood. However, things change when the two are forced to compete against each other in the final tournament.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Gabriel Iglesias: I'm Sorry for What I Said When I Was Hungry
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Hawaiian-shirt enthusiast Gabriel "Fluffy" Iglesias finds the laughs in racist gift baskets, Prius-driving cops and all-female taco trucks.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Pyaar Ka Punchnama 2
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After falling in love, three roommates experience changes in their lives.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Word Party
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Meet Bailey, Franny, Kip and Lulu. They're adorable baby animals, and they want you to join the party and help them learn!

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ralphie May: Unruly
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Very little is off-limits in comedian Ralphie May’s very first Netflix original stand-up comedy special, Unruly. Filmed live in front of a raucous, fist-pumping crowd at Cobb Energy Performing Arts Centre in Atlanta, May unleashes his hilariously raunchy, no-holds-barred perspective on everything from airline travel and the news media, to Chick-fil-A and everybody being a little racist when they drive.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Rebirth
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A man's life is turned inside out after a visit from his college friend leads him into the unexpected.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Manson Family Vacation
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The story of two brothers: one who’s devoted to his family, the other who’s obsessed with the Manson Family.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Popples
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The adorable Best Popple Pals love helping their friends and neighbors, but every time they do it seems to backfire in hilarious ways.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: StoryBots Super Songs
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Based on the award-winning educational apps, "StoryBots Super Songs" centers on the StoryBots, the curious little creatures who live in the world beneath our screens and help answer humans' biggest questions.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Aziz Ansari: Live at Madison Square Garden
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Ansari headlines the iconic Madison Square Garden and delivers his most hilarious and insightful stand-up yet. Filmed in front of a sold-out audience, Ansari's latest special is an uproarious document of the comic in top form -- covering topics ranging from the struggle of American immigrants to the food industry to relationships to gender inequality.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Chris Tucker: Live
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Comedian Chris Tucker performs live.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dana Carvey: Straight White Male, 60
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Emmy-winning comedian Dana Carvey blends pitch-perfect tales on big personalities with so-true-it-hurts stories from his life as a dad of millennials.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Justin Timberlake + The Tennessee Kids
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: For Justin Timberlake it's the final two dates of his 20/20 Experience World Tour at the MGM Grand Garden Arena in Las Vegas. Surrounded by the 25 band members of The Tennessee Kids and featuring show-stopping performances from one of the highest-grossing tours of the decade, the film is a culmination of the singer’s 134 shows and 2 years on the road.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Russell Peters: Almost Famous
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The comic comes home to Toronto to sound off on cultural quirks, furniture building and bathroom visits, revelling in all things ridiculously human.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Colin Quinn: Unconstitutional
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Colin Quinn returns to the stage in "Unconstitutional" where he tackles 226 years of American Constitutional calamities in 70 Minutes.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Jim Jefferies: Freedumb
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Returning for a second Netflix comedy special, Jim Jefferies unleashes his famously ferocious black humor to a packed house in Nashville, Tennessee.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Asperger's Are Us
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: For the members of the comedy troupe Asperger’s Are Us, it’s easier to associate with a faceless audience than with their own families. No matter who the crowd, best friends Noah, New Michael, Jack and Ethan have one simple mantra: “We would much rather the audience appreciate us as comedians than people who have overcome adversity.”  In this coming-of-age heartfelt documentary, this band of brothers finds themselves at a crossroad. With real life pulling them apart, they decide to plan one ambitious farewell show before they all go their separate ways. People with Asperger’s don’t deal well with uncertainty, and this is the most uncertain time in their lives.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Tony Robbins: I Am Not Your Guru
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Granted unprecedented access, Berlinger captures renowned life and business strategist Tony Robbins behind the scenes of his mega seminar Date with Destiny, pulling back the curtain on this life-altering and controversial event, the zealous participants and the man himself.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Hunterrr
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An ordinary bachelor pursues girls like a hunter, but not with the intention of settling down in life.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Chelsea
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: It's not her first talk show, but it is a first of its kind. Ideas, people and places that fascinate her, all in her unique style.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Kapoor & Sons
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Returning home to visit their ill grandfather, two estranged brothers must confront their unresolved rivalry while their parents’ marriage frays.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Udta Punjab
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Drug abuse and the darker side of Punjab rear their heads in the intense, interwoven tales of a policeman, a doctor, a migrant worker, and a rockstar.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Tamasha
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Ved and Tara meet accidentally meet in Corsica, France and decide to spend the next 7 days together with secretly revealing their true identity or without any promise to meet later, ever. Tara eventually falls in love with Ved and goes to find Ved after 4 years, and helps him to find his true story where he belongs.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Chronically Metropolitan
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A case of writer's block inspires a young novelist to return home to New York City and reconnect with his engaged ex and his bohemian parents.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Miracle
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: How could twin sisters be such polar opposites? Kwon Shi Ah is the beautiful sister, gorgeous in every way and a member of the popular girl group known as Miracle Girls. Since she was in preschool, Shia has worked as a model and then a teen actress before becoming an idol. Her fraternal twin sister, Shi Yeon, is almost double the body size of Shi Ah and has always been ridiculed and bullied in school for her large frame. Because of this, Shi Yeon has become a recluse, who prefers staying home and producing an Internet broadcast within the safety of her room. The only time Shi Yeon ventures out is to visit a mysterious tarot card reader who gives Shi Yeon a magical tarot card every day. But the twin sisters’ lives are turned upside down when they wake up one day and realize that their souls have switched bodies! What will an idol musician and Shi Yeon’s high school crush think of the women they thought they knew?

But the twin sisters’ lives are turned upside down when they wake up one day and realize that their souls have switched bodies! What will an idol musician and Shi Yeon’s high school crush think of the women they thought they knew?

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: White Nights
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Seo Yi-Kyung ambitiously wants to build her own empire. She is calm and also passionate. She doesn't believe greed is a sin. Park Gun-Woo possesses good looks and comes from a wealthy family that runs a large company. Seo Yi-Kyung is his first love and he is still in love with her. Lee Se-Jin comes from a poor background. She desperately wants to escape from her situation.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: White Nights
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Seo Yi-Kyung ambitiously wants to build her own empire. She is calm and also passionate. She doesn't believe greed is a sin. Park Gun-Woo possesses good looks and comes from a wealthy family that runs a large company. Seo Yi-Kyung is his first love and he is still in love with her. Lee Se-Jin comes from a poor background. She desperately wants to escape from her situation.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Hannibal Buress: Comedy Camisado
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: He's a kamikaze gambler. A one-arm cuddler. And if his fly is down, so be it. A night of sly riffs and slow burns.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Anjelah Johnson: Not Fancy
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Actress and comedian Anjelah Johnson showcases her hilarious impressions to riff on European Gypsies, Vietnamese manicurists, Mexican moms, and more.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Force 2
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: ACP Yashvardhan teams up RAW Agent KK to bring down the master mind terrorist, Shiv.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Fitoor
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A young artist tries to win the heart of his muse, while her mother hatches a scheme to end his quest for true love.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Ivory Game
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Wildlife activists and investigators put their lives on the line to battle the illegal African ivory trade, in this suspenseful on-the-ground documentary.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Home: Adventures with Tip & Oh
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Picking up where the 2015 film left off, this coming-of-age buddy comedy follows fearless Tip and overenthusiastic Oh, as they navigate the crazily combined human and alien culture they live in, finding adventure everywhere they go.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Tom Segura: Mostly Stories
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The bearded, bawdy, and comically bitter Tom Segura gets real about body piercings, the "Area 51" of men's bodies, and the lie he told Mike Tyson.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dhanak
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Orphaned siblings Pari and Chotu embark on a journey to restore Chotu's eyesight.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Chocolate City: Vegas Strip
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The Chocolate City dancers come together to save their club from foreclosure. They decide to enter a national stripper competition, traveling all the way to Las Vegas to try their luck.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: I'll Sleep When I'm Dead
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An energetic and fast-paced bio-doc that examines the story behind one of the most prolific and well-known DJs working today: Steve Aoki.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Project Marathwada
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An indebted old farmer Tukaram wants to get justice for his son who commits suicide. But when Tukaram's pleas fall on deaf ears, he is forced to take a drastic step to ensure that his voice is heard, loud and clear, by the nation.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: ABCD 2
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Childhood friends Suresh and Vinnie want to become successful dancers. To fulfill their dreams, they form a dance group with their friends and compete in a hip-hop contest in Las Vegas.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: My Runway
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An egotistic top male model and a pretty model wannabe are forced to live each other's lives until they figure out a way to undo their body switch.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: My Runway
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An egotistic top male model and a pretty model wannabe are forced to live each other's lives until they figure out a way to undo their body switch.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Te3n
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A grandfather, police officer and a priest join hands to investigate and find a missing child.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Budhia Singh: Born to Run
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Budhia Singh – Born To Run is an upcoming 2016 Indian biographical sports film directed by Soumendra Padhi. It is based on Budhia Singh, who ran 48 marathons — one of which was from Bhubaneshwar to Puri, when he was a five-year-old.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mercy
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Brought together at their childhood home over their dying mother, an estranged family is thrust into a deadly fight for their own survival.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: XOXO
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: XOXO follows six strangers whose lives collide in one frenetic, dream-chasing, hopelessly romantic night.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Open Season: Scared Silly
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The humans and animals believe a werewolf is on the loose, and former hunter Shaw uses the opportunity to re-open the season. Boog, Elliot, and Mr. Weenie have to face their fears and find the werewolf to get the season closed permanently.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Jessica Darling's It List
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Jessica Darling – a smart, witty, opinionated girl heading into 7th grade – was never too concerned about where she'd fit in the middle school hierarchy.
