But before her first day of school, her older sister — the super popular Bethany, now in college—decides to help out by giving her the “It List”—a cheat sheet on how to navigate the middle school maze and rise to the top of the popularity chain. The instructions appear simple enough to follow, but, like life, nothing is as easy as it seems.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Garfunkel and Oates: Trying to be Special
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Garkfunkel and Oates: Trying to Be Special is the first special by the musical comedy duo of Kate Micucci and Riki Lindhome. The pair filmed the special at the Neptune Theatre in Seattle, and it features songs, comedy, and a new Garfunkel and Oates music video.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Shaandaar
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Jagjinder Joginder, a wedding planner, brings together the dysfunctional family of businessman Bipin Arora while making arrangements for Bipin's daughter's destination wedding in London.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Kulipari: An Army of Frogs
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a tale of bravery and heroism, fearless frogs go to war against the sinister scorpions and spiders that have teamed up to conquer the amphibians.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Rainbow Time
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Todd grew up under the strange shadow of his older mentally challenged brother Shonzi. As kids, Shonzi forced Todd to make action movies. As adults he pressures him to share love life details, even showing Shonzi a sex tape he made with an old girlfriend to help him cope when family tragedy hits. When their dad suffers a heart attack, Shonzi (now 40, and still a virgin) moves in with Todd and his new girlfriend Lindsay. Shonzi wants desperately to be included in their relationship like old times. When Shonzi’s begging become threats to reveal secrets from their past, Todd must find the courage to be honest with Lindsay, even if it means the end of their relationship.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Little Things
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A cohabiting couple in their 20s navigate the ups and downs of work, modern-day relationships and finding themselves in contemporary Bengaluru.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: You Are My Sunday
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Five friends struggle to find a place to play football in Mumbai.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Chasing Cameron
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The series stars Dallas and his famous friends embarking on a new tour of Magcon around Europe. Aaron Carpenter, Taylor Caniff, Blake Gray, Trey Schafer and Willie Jones are also starring in the series.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Frank and Cindy
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: G.J. Echternkamp tells the story of his relationship with his parents, his mother Cindy and his step-father, Frank. Frank used to be a member of OXO, a band from the '80s whose one hit wonder scored with the song "Whirly Girl". Cindy was the ultimate groupie who married Frank and thought life would be glamorous and award shows, but it's not how it turned out.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dharam Sankat Mein
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The film revolves around a Hindu man (Paresh Rawal) who goes through an identity crisis when he discovers he was adopted as a son in a Hindu family but was born in a Muslim family. The journey starts with finding his real father.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Coach Snoop
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: See a different side of Snoop Dogg in this unique documentary, which details the famous rapper's efforts to mentor young athletes and create opportunities for them to compete at the highest level of youth football. We'll meet the kids and coaches that form Snoop's squad -- and witness the important life lessons they learn with every game.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Stories by Rabindranath Tagore
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The characters of Tagore’s stories spring into life through the cinematic imagination of acclaimed filmmaker, Anurag Basu in ‘Stories By Rabindranath Tagore’. ‘Stories By Rabindranath Tagore’ shares with us the intricately etched characters created by the master himself and brought onto the small screen by the visionary director of ‘Barfi’ and ‘Life in a Metro.’

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Puerto Ricans in Paris
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: NYPD detectives Luis and Eddie visit Paris to help gorgeous French designer Colette catch the black market thief who's ripped off her new handbag design. While Luis' girlfriend Vanessa and Eddie's wife Gloria remain in New York, the hopelessly unhip odd couple stumble through a glamorous high-fashion world brimming with charming cafes, wild nightclubs and corporate treachery.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Liar, Liar, Vampire
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When ordinary boy Davis suddenly becomes famous at school as people start to believe he's actually a vampire, vampire expert Cameron helps him act like a real vampire.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Patton Oswalt: Talking for Clapping
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Patton Oswalt delivers a fresh hour plus of stand-up, covering everything from misery to defeat to hopelessness. It's his most upbeat special to date.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: LEGO Friends: The Power of Friendship
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Five best friends face adventures side by side in their hometown. Zany antics, love and missteps are better with friends.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Iliza Shlesinger: Confirmed Kills
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The standup sensation tackle's TV's "Shark Tank," what it means to be a woman and how to deal with the lawless party goblin that lives in us all.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Umrika
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When a young village boy discovers that his brother, long believed to be in America, has actually gone missing, he begins to invent letters on his behalf to save their mother from heartbreak, all the while searching for him.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: One More Time
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This fantasy drama follows an indie band singer who repeatedly undergoes unwanted time slips and the girlfriend he must save from an unlucky fate.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: One More Time
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This fantasy drama follows an indie band singer who repeatedly undergoes unwanted time slips and the girlfriend he must save from an unlucky fate.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Michael Che Matters
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: "SNL" star Michael Che takes on hot-button topics like inequality, homophobia and gentrification in this stand-up set filmed live in Brooklyn.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Brent Morin: I'm Brent Morin
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a witty solo show, Brent Morin serves up infectious laughs on the agony of puberty, hot guy problems and the time a girl dumped him for a magician.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Joe Rogan: Triggered
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Unleashing his inquisitive, intense comedic style, Rogan explores everything from raising kids and Santa Claus to pot gummies and talking to dolphins.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Kyaa Kool Hain Hum 3
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In order to impress his girlfriend's conservative father, a porn actor uses his fellow adult movie stars in creating a fake traditional family.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bill Hicks: Reflections
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Comedy Dynamics sits down with Bill Hicks’ brother, Steve, who tells old stories, squashes old rumors and reveals the brother and son behind the late comedian. Told amidst old and rare footage, it’s a must watch for any fan.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Phantom
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Phantom is an action thriller that unfolds across various countries around the world. The plot revolves around protagonist Daniyal, whose journey to seek justice takes him from India to Europe, America and the volatile Middle East. However, he finds out that in a mission like this, there is always a price to pay, in this case, a very personal price.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: David Cross: Making America Great Again
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: With nothing off-limits, David Cross is unapologetic, insightful, and biting in his Netflix original stand-up comedy special, MAKING AMERICA GREAT AGAIN. Filmed live at The Paramount Theatre in Austin, TX, Cross takes aim the current political landscape.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Jeff Dunham: Unhinged in Hollywood
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Previously unseen stand-up comedy by Jeff Dunham. Sketches include popular characters. Brad Paisley performs too! Special appearances by comic Chris Parnell and former UFC champion Chuck Liddell.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dinosaur World
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Scientist Khojwala finds it difficult to nurture a baby dinosaur. He, with the help of Chotta Bheem and his gang, decides to travel back in time to return the animal to its world.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: U Turn
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A journalist who intents to write an article on traffic rule breakers gets dragged into a whirlpool of murder cases and deception.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Fearless
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: On a journey from Brazil to the Las Vegas championships, professional bull riders risk it all to earn money, respect and titles.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bottersnikes & Gumbles
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a far away forgotten valley heaped with long-abandoned junk, a timeless battle rages between good and evil… and also between squishy and scaly, happy and grumpy, clever and wily… handsome and plain old ugly. This is the land of Bottersnikes and Gumbles.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Iliza Shlesinger: Freezing Hot
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Smart and brazen comedian Iliza Shlesinger shares her unflinchingly honest observations on the differences between men and women. Filled with hashtag-able catch phrases, this is a laugh-out-loud revelation exposing some of women’s best kept - and ugliest - secrets, including truths about first date attire, fantasy break-ups and the tireless pursuit of not being cold while still looking hot.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Katti Batti
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A man falls in love with a woman because of her outlook on life. They are in a relationship for five years until a sudden turn of events causes a problem in their relationship.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mike Epps: Don't Take It Personal
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Mike Epps wastes no time bringing his unapologetic and raunchy swagger to a howling live audience at the historic Orpheum Theater in Los Angeles.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bangistan
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Two blundering terrorists with lofty ideologies, but ordinary talent, on a mission to change the world.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ludo
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Needing a secluded place for a late-night tryst, two couples stow away in a mall after hours, but are quickly ensnared in a gruesome and deadly game.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Theo Von: No Offense
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Known for always saying the unexpected and telling it like it is, even at the expense of offending, Louisiana comedian Theo Von returns home to film his first stand-up comedy special for Netflix at the Civic Theater in New Orleans.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: #Rucker50
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The celebratory explosion of basketball history makers, legend shakers and lawbreakers; juxtaposed against important events in Civil & Human Rights. The 50 years of The Rucker's ripples reverberate throughout Basketball, Hip-Hop, Harlem, and life.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Poshter Girl
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Poshter Girl takes you on a mad roller coaster ride of a quaint, little village in Maharashtra - Tekawde, which is ill-famous for female infanticide and as a result there are no girls left within the village. When the question of boys' marriage is on heat, a beautiful and Intelligent girl enters the scenario and changes everything. This is the story of the girl Rupali and her chosen 5 candidates who would do anything to win her heart.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Wazir
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: 'Wazir' is a tale of two unlikely friends, a wheelchair-bound chess grandmaster and a brave ATS officer. Brought together by grief and a strange twist of fate, the two men decide to help each other win the biggest games of their lives. But there's a mysterious, dangerous opponent lurking in the shadows, who is all set to checkmate them.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Motu Patlu: King Of Kings
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Motu and Patlu are your home-grown Laurel and Hardy in an animation avatar. They befriend a circus lion, Guddu and attempt to save the jungle from a greedy poacher.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Jeff Foxworthy & Larry the Cable Guy: We've Been Thinking
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Comedians Jeff Foxworthy and Larry the Cable Guy bring their distinctive brand of humor to a packed crowd in Minneapolis.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Spark
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: 'Spark' is a mini music drama like a night concert in the summertime, centering on a man who leaks a great deal of electricity after a sudden accident and a woman he can't get away from no matter how hard he tries

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Spark
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: 'Spark' is a mini music drama like a night concert in the summertime, centering on a man who leaks a great deal of electricity after a sudden accident and a woman he can't get away from no matter how hard he tries

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Jen Kirkman: I'm Gonna Die Alone (And I Feel Fine)
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Jen Kirkman's Netflix produced stand-up special as performed at the North Door in Austin, Texas.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Pac’s Scary Halloween
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Dr. Pacenstein and Eeghost are plotting to ruin Pac's Halloween dinner plans at Transylpacia Castle and it is up to a scary neighbor to save the night.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Reggie Watts: Spatial
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The comic innovator delivers a surreal set blending experimental songs, jokes about grits, guns and drugs, and other improvised comedy adventures.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Chris D'Elia: Incorrigible
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Comedian and actor Chris D’Elia, known for his dynamic physical comedy, explains why the NFL would be way more entertaining if it were real lions, bears and Vikings battling each other, that babies are the worst prize ever, and that you should never ask a Cuban directions unless you’re ready for the best time of your life.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Santa Pac's Merry Berry Day
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: ﻿As Pacworlders excitedly decorate for Berry Day, Pac is saddened about missing his parents as he receives a picture ornament of them from his Aunt Spheria.  The teens reminisce of their childhood Berry Day as they enjoy Christmas eggnog.  Since Berry Day is one of the happiest days of the year, Betrayus launches a plan to get rid of the day by capturing Santa Pac and his Round Deer and to possess the gifts and Berry Day decorations. All Pac wants for Berry Day is to see his parents Sunny and Zac and is overjoyed when they arrive. But, his parents tell him they want to see the tree of life in the secret location which is forbidden.  Are these Pac’s real parents or are they a trick from Betrayus and Dr. Slimestein?  Let’s hope Berry Day can be merry after all.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Extremis
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A purely observational non-fiction film that takes viewers into the ethically murky world of end-of-life decision making in a public hospital.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Cedric the Entertainer: Live from the Ville
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Donning his signature suit and fedora, the dapper comic offers a unique spin on getting old, the presidential election and "Honky Tonk Badonkadonk."

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: One in a Billion
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a country of 1.2 billion people and in a sport with billions of fans worldwide, there has yet to be a single Indian-born player drafted in the NBA. One in a Billion follows the global journey of Satnam Singh Bhamara from his home of Ballo Ke, a farming village in rural India, to the bright lights of New York City as he attempts to change history. Building up to a climactic draft night after years of hard work, Satnam hopes to finally create the long-awaited connection between India and the NBA.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Brahman Naman
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This homage to 1980s teen sex comedies follows a college quiz bowl champion who knows almost everything -- except how to talk to women.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Virunga: Gorillas in Peril
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A behind-the-scenes documentary about the gorillas featured in the film Virunga.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Santa Banta Pvt Ltd
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Two friends and their sweet and endearing misadventures and one of these misadventures sees them land in the middle of a kidnapping investigation.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Jada
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Jada is 7 years old. Jada lives alone on Venice Beach. By following her through a day in her life, the story of who she is, why she is there, and who the man is that has come looking for her unfolds.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sila Samayangalil
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Seven people from different walks of life give their blood sample for ELISA Test - AIDS Screening. To avoid the tension of waiting, they decide to bribe the technician and know the results earlier. They come to know only one among them has AIDS. Each one hoping it is not him,waits with anxiety. The film takes an unexpected turn from here creating an emotional and shocking end.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sam Kinison: The Scream Continues
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Comedy Dynamics sits down with Sam Kinison's brother, Bill, to set the record straight on the stories surrounding this legendary comedian. Including his classic performances, rare TV appearances and photos, this documentary is not to be missed by any true Sam Kinison fan! Plus, you might be surprised who else you see with Sam. He was one popular guy!

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Creative Indians
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The Creative Indians is a docu-series showcasing, de-mystifying and de-constructing the lives, journeys and processes of the most impactful creative professionals and projects of India across industries like Cinema, Art, Design, Music, Fashion, Dance, Photography, Advertising and more.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Janoskians: Untold and Untrue
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A history of the Australia comedy troupe The Janoskians leading up to their live performance at Wembley Stadium.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Tariqi: My Way
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In the 1970s, Dalila is suffering from oppression and injustice by her aristocratic mother because Dalila is determined to be a famous singer. Along the way she experiences two love stories that will show her who is on her side on the path to glory and fame. insists to be a famous singer.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mind Game
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: With the help of a cop, a psychiatrist and a woman who can foretell the future, a brilliant paralegal works to solve an array of perplexing mysteries.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Snervous Tyler Oakley
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After eight years of sharing snippets of his life online, see the intimate truth of Tyler Oakley's relationship with family, followers and fame on his sold out international tour.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sommore: The Reign Continues
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Self-proclaimed "Queen of Comedy" Sommore storms the stage to deliver a riotous stand-up performance in Charlotte, North Carolina.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Lakeeran
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Upset over his role in the accidental death of a Sikh, a young Punjabi man living abroad returns to India and falls for a widow whose husband died in similar circumstances.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Time Out
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The friendship, laughter and shared love between two brothers is tested when a 14-year-old boy is confronted with the complexities of a simple relationship.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Sinner
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a small New York town, a haunted detective hunts for answers about perplexing crimes while wrestling with his own demons.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Leave No Trace
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A father and daughter live a perfect but mysterious existence in Forest Park, a beautiful nature reserve near Portland, Oregon, rarely making contact with the world. But when a small mistake tips them off to authorities, they are sent on an increasingly erratic journey in search of a place to call their own.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ozark
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A financial adviser drags his family from Chicago to the Missouri Ozarks, where he must launder $500 million in five years to appease a drug boss.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Blade Runner 2049
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Thirty years after the events of the first film, a new blade runner, LAPD Officer K, unearths a long-buried secret that has the potential to plunge what's left of society into chaos. K's discovery leads him on a quest to find Rick Deckard, a former LAPD blade runner who has been missing for 30 years.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: 12 Strong
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A team of special forces head into Afghanistan in the aftermath of the September 11th attacks in an attempt to dismantle the Taliban.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: It
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a small town in Maine, seven children known as The Losers Club come face to face with life problems, bullies and a monster that takes the shape of a clown called Pennywise.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Legacies
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a place where young witches, vampires, and werewolves are nurtured to be their best selves in spite of their worst impulses, Klaus Mikaelson’s daughter, 17-year-old Hope Mikaelson, Alaric Saltzman’s twins, Lizzie and Josie Saltzman, among others, come of age into heroes and villains at The Salvatore School for the Young and Gifted.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Manifest
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After landing from a turbulent but routine flight, the crew and passengers of Montego Air Flight 828 discover five years have passed in what seemed like a few hours. As their new realities become clear, a deeper mystery unfolds and some of the returned passengers soon realize they may be meant for something greater than they ever thought possible.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Riverdale
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Set in the present, the series offers a bold, subversive take on Archie, Betty, Veronica and their friends, exploring the surreality of small-town life, the darkness and weirdness bubbling beneath Riverdale’s wholesome facade.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Wind River
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An FBI agent teams with the town's veteran game tracker to investigate a murder that occurred on a Native American reservation.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sorry to Bother You
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In an alternate present-day version of Oakland, black telemarketer Cassius Green discovers a magical key to professional success – which propels him into a macabre universe.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dunkirk
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The story of the miraculous evacuation of Allied soldiers from Belgium, Britain, Canada and France, who were cut off and surrounded by the German army from the beaches and harbour of Dunkirk between May 26th and June 4th 1940 during World War II.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Cobra Kai
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This Karate Kid sequel series picks up 30 years after the events of the 1984 All Valley Karate Tournament and finds Johnny Lawrence on the hunt for redemption by reopening the infamous Cobra Kai karate dojo. This reignites his old rivalry with the successful Daniel LaRusso, who has been working to maintain the balance in his life without mentor Mr. Miyagi.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Vice
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: George W. Bush picks Dick Cheney, the CEO of Halliburton Co., to be his Republican running mate in the 2000 presidential election. No stranger to politics, Cheney's impressive résumé includes stints as White House chief of staff, House Minority Whip and Defense Secretary. When Bush wins by a narrow margin, Cheney begins to use his newfound power to help reshape the country and the world.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mindhunter
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An agent in the FBI's Elite Serial Crime Unit develops profiling techniques as he pursues notorious serial killers and rapists.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Phantom Thread
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In 1950s London, renowned British dressmaker Reynolds Woodcock comes across Alma, a young, strong-willed woman, who soon becomes ever present in his life as his muse and lover.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: All American
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When a rising high school football player from South Central L.A. is recruited to play for Beverly Hills High, the wins, losses and struggles of two families from vastly different worlds - Compton and Beverly Hills - begin to collide. Inspired by the life of pro football player Spencer Paysinger.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: You
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A dangerously charming, intensely obsessive young man goes to extreme measures to insert himself into the lives of those he is transfixed by.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Molly's Game
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Molly Bloom, a young skier and former Olympic hopeful becomes a successful entrepreneur (and a target of an FBI investigation) when she establishes a high-stakes, international poker game.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Den of Thieves
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A gritty crime saga which follows the lives of an elite unit of the LA County Sheriff's Dept. and the state's most successful bank robbery crew as the outlaws plan a seemingly impossible heist on the Federal Reserve Bank.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Lost in Space
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After crash-landing on an alien planet, the Robinson family fights against all odds to survive and escape. But they're surrounded by hidden dangers.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Rise of the Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Rise up! The Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles get an all-new look, new weapons, and awesome new powers! Join the legendary heroes, Raph, Leo, Donnie and Mikey as these brothers discover a Hidden City beneath New York, learn amazing mystic ninja skills, battle absurd mutants… and always find time for a slice of their favorite pizza! Cowabunga!

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: American Vandal
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A true-crime satire that explores the aftermath of a costly high school prank that left twenty-seven faculty cars vandalized with phallic images.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Godless
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A ruthless outlaw terrorizes the West in search of a former member of his gang, who’s found a new life in a quiet town populated only by women.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Somebody Feed Phil
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: "Everybody Loves Raymond" creator Phil Rosenthal travels the globe to take in the local cuisine and culture of Bangkok, Lisbon, Mexico City and more.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Manhunt
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Inspired by actual events, this true crime anthology series takes a deep dive into the dark, twisted minds of terrorists and follows the brave souls who hunt them down.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Haunting of Hill House
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The Crains, a fractured family, confront haunting memories of their old home and the terrifying events that drove them from it.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: CHiPS
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The adventures of two California Highway Patrol motorcycle officers as they make their rounds on the freeways of Los Angeles.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Ballad of Buster Scruggs
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Vignettes weaving together the stories of six individuals in the old West at the end of the Civil War. Following the tales of a sharp-shooting songster, a wannabe bank robber, two weary traveling performers, a lone gold prospector, a woman traveling the West to an uncertain future, and a motley crew of strangers undertaking a carriage ride.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Altered Carbon
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After 250 years on ice, a prisoner returns to life in a new body with one chance to win his freedom: by solving a mind-bending murder.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Castlevania
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A dark medieval fantasy following the last surviving member of the disgraced Belmont clan, trying to save Eastern Europe from extinction at the hand of Vlad Dracula Tepe himself. Inspired by the classic video game series.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dirty John
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Anthology series in which each season is based on a true crime story featuring an epic tale of love gone wrong.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dynasty
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The reboot follows two of America’s wealthiest families, the Carringtons and the Colbys, as they feud for control over their fortune and their children focusing on Fallon Carrington, the daughter of billionaire Blake Carrington, and her soon-to-be stepmother, Cristal, a Hispanic woman marrying into this WASP family and America’s most powerful class.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Won't You Be My Neighbor?
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: For more than thirty years, and through his television program, Fred Rogers (1928-2003), host, producer, writer and pianist, accompanied by his puppets and his many friends, spoke directly to young children about some of life's most important issues.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Good Girls
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Three "good girl" suburban wives and mothers suddenly find themselves in desperate circumstances and decide to stop playing it safe and risk everything to take their power back.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: HAPPY!
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Corrupt ex-cop turned hitman Nick Sax's life is changed forever by a relentlessly positive, imaginary blue winged horse named Happy.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Wet Hot American Summer: Ten Years Later
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A decade after their wild summer as junior counselors, the gang reunites for a weekend of bonding, hanky-panky and hair-raising adventures.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Maniac
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Two strangers are drawn to a mysterious pharmaceutical trial that will, they're assured, with no complications or side-effects whatsoever, solve all of their problems, permanently. Things do not go as planned.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Wild Wild Country
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When a controversial cult leader builds a utopian city in the Oregon desert, conflict with the locals escalates into a national scandal.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Okja
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A young girl named Mija risks everything to prevent a powerful, multi-national company from kidnapping her best friend - a massive animal named Okja.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Okja
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A young girl named Mija risks everything to prevent a powerful, multi-national company from kidnapping her best friend - a massive animal named Okja.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Okja
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A young girl named Mija risks everything to prevent a powerful, multi-national company from kidnapping her best friend - a massive animal named Okja.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Trolls: The Beat Goes On!
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Queen Poppy tries to keep Troll Village's peace with the Bergens by inviting them to parties, playing their sports and preventing crime.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Atypical
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Sam, an 18-year-old on the autism spectrum, takes a funny, yet painful, journey of self-discovery for love and independence and upends his family.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Final Score
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When a stadium is seized by a group of heavily armed criminals during a major sporting event, an ex-soldier must use all his military skills to save both the daughter of a fallen comrade and the huge crowd unaware of the danger.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: A Series of Unfortunate Events
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The orphaned Baudelaire children face trials, tribulations and the evil Count Olaf, all in their quest to uncover the secret of their parents' death.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Charmed
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Set in the fictional college town of Hilltowne, Charmed follows the lives of three sisters, Macy, Mel and Maggie Vera who, after the tragic death of their mother, discover they are three of the most powerful witches of all time.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Cold Case Files
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Tense new series exploring cold cases from victims death to criminal convictions.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: One Day at a Time
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a reimagining of the TV classic, a newly single Latina mother raises her teen daughter and tween son with the "help" of her old-school mom.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Forgotten
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Seoul, South Korea, 1997. When the young but extremely anxious student Jin-seok, his parents and his successful older brother Yoo-seok move to a new home, mysterious and frightening events begin to happen around them, unexplained events that threaten to ruin their seemingly happy lives. Unable to understand what is happening, Jin-seok wonders if he is losing his mind.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Forgotten
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Seoul, South Korea, 1997. When the young but extremely anxious student Jin-seok, his parents and his successful older brother Yoo-seok move to a new home, mysterious and frightening events begin to happen around them, unexplained events that threaten to ruin their seemingly happy lives. Unable to understand what is happening, Jin-seok wonders if he is losing his mind.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Backtrace
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The lone surviving thief of a violent armored car robbery is sprung from a high security facility and administered an experimental drug.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Santa Clarita Diet
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: They're ordinary husband and wife realtors until she undergoes a dramatic change that sends them down a road of death and destruction. In a good way.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Stranger
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: With the help of a gutsy female detective, a prosecutor who has lost the ability to feel empathy tackles a murder case amid political corruption.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Stranger
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: With the help of a gutsy female detective, a prosecutor who has lost the ability to feel empathy tackles a murder case amid political corruption.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Set It Up
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Two overworked and underpaid assistants come up with a plan to get their bosses off their backs by setting them up with each other.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Cloverfield Paradox
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Orbiting above a planet on the brink of war, scientists test a device to solve an energy crisis and end up face-to-face with a dark alternate reality.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Cocomelon
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In the town of Cocomelon, baby JJ and his siblings go on fun every-day adventures with nursery, play, exploration, and learning - situations that any preschooler could relate to. Fun, relatable stories set to toe-tapping songs.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Gerald's Game
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When her husband's sex game goes wrong, Jessie (who is handcuffed to a bed in a remote lake house) faces warped visions, dark secrets and a dire choice.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Roma
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In 1970s Mexico City, two domestic workers help a mother of four while her husband is away for an extended period of time.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Adrift
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A true story of survival, as a young couple's chance encounter leads them first to love, and then on the adventure of a lifetime as they face one of the most catastrophic hurricanes in recorded history.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Beguiled
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: During the Civil War, at a Southern girls’ boarding school, young women take in an injured enemy soldier. As they provide refuge and tend to his wounds, the house is taken over with sexual tension and dangerous rivalries, and taboos are broken in an unexpected turn of events.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Disenchantment
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Set in a ruined medieval city called Dreamland, Disenchantment follows the grubby adventures of a hard-drinking princess, her feisty elf companion and her personal demon.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Big Mouth
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Teenage friends find their lives upended by the wonders and horrors of puberty in this edgy comedy from real-life pals Nick Kroll and Andrew Goldberg.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Knightfall
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Go deep into the clandestine world of the legendary brotherhood of warrior monks known as The Knights Templar.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: GLOW
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In 1980s LA, a crew of misfits reinvent themselves as the Gorgeous Ladies of Wrestling.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Bad Batch
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a desert wasteland in Texas, a muscled cannibal breaks one important rule: don’t play with your food.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Oats Studios
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A compilation of shorts, diverse experimental content and more weird stuff spread directly from the devious mind of the South African film director Neill Blomkamp.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Tully
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Marlo, a mother of three, including a newborn, is gifted a night nanny by her brother. Hesitant at first, she quickly forms a bond with the thoughtful, surprising, and sometimes challenging nanny named Tully.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Guernsey Literary & Potato Peel Pie Society
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Free-spirited writer Juliet Ashton forms a life-changing bond with the delightful and eccentric Guernsey Literary and Potato Peel Pie Society, when she decides to write about the book club they formed during the occupation of Guernsey in WWII.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Foreigner
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Quan is a humble London businessman whose long-buried past erupts in a revenge-fueled vendetta when the only person left for him to love – his teenage daughter – dies in an Irish Republican Army car bombing. His relentless search to find the terrorists leads to a cat-and-mouse conflict with a British government official whose own past may hold the clues to the identities of the elusive killers.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Foreigner
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Quan is a humble London businessman whose long-buried past erupts in a revenge-fueled vendetta when the only person left for him to love – his teenage daughter – dies in an Irish Republican Army car bombing. His relentless search to find the terrorists leads to a cat-and-mouse conflict with a British government official whose own past may hold the clues to the identities of the elusive killers.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Can't Stop, Won't Stop: A Bad Boy Story
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A behind-the-scenes look at the prolific label's legacy and offer an in-depth look at the two-night anniversary extravaganza that took place last May at Brooklyn's Barclays Center in honor of the late rap great, The Notorious B.I.G.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Outlaw King
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Forced into exile by the English after being crowned King of Scotland, legendary warrior Robert the Bruce fights to reclaim the throne.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Destination Wedding
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Frank and Lindsay—two emotionally-broken strangers—meet on the way to a destination wedding. Over the course of the weekend and against all odds, they find themselves drawn together even though they are initially repulsed by one another.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Kominsky Method
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An aging actor, who long ago enjoyed a brush with fame, makes his living as an acting coach.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Keepers
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This docuseries examines the decades-old murder of Sister Catherine Cesnik and its suspected link to a priest accused of abuse.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: 13 Reasons Why
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After a teenage girl's perplexing suicide, a classmate receives a series of tapes that unravel the mystery of her tragic choice.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bird Box
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Five years after an ominous unseen presence drives most of society to suicide, a survivor and her two children make a desperate bid to reach safety.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Babysitter
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When Cole stays up past his bedtime, he discovers that his hot babysitter is part of a Satanic cult that will stop at nothing to keep him quiet.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Imposters
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Maddie, a persona shifting con-artist who is as beautiful as she is dangerous, leaves her unwitting victims tormented when they realize they have been used and robbed of everything – including their hearts. But things get complicated when her former targets, Ezra, Richard, and Jules team up to track her down.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Narcos: Mexico
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: See the rise of the Guadalajara Cartel as an American DEA agent learns the danger of targeting narcos in 1980s Mexico.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Black Lightning
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Jefferson Pierce is a man wrestling with a secret. As the father of two daughters and principal of a charter high school that also serves as a safe haven for young people in a New Orleans neighborhood overrun by gang violence, he is a hero to his community.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Salt Fat Acid Heat
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Chef and food writer Samin Nosrat travels the world to explore four basic keys to wonderful cooking, serving up feasts and helpful tips along the way.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Package
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When a group of teenagers goes on a spring break camping trip, an unfortunate accident sets off a race to save their friend’s most prized possession.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Replicas
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A scientist becomes obsessed with returning his family to normalcy after a terrible accident.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Cam
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A young camgirl discovers that she’s inexplicably been replaced on her site with an exact replica of herself.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mystery Science Theater 3000
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The cult hit returns! Captured by mad scientists, new host Jonah survives a blitz of cheesy B movies by riffing on them with his funny robot pals.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: My Next Guest Needs No Introduction With David Letterman
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: TV legend David Letterman teams up with fascinating global figures for in-depth interviews and curiosity-fueled excursions in this monthly talk show.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Seven Seconds
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Tensions run high between African American citizens and Caucasian cops in Jersey City when a teenage African American boy is critically injured by a cop.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Queer Eye
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An all-new “Fab Five” advise men on fashion, grooming, food, culture and design in this modern reboot of the Emmy Award-winning reality series.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Abducted in Plain Sight
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In 1974, 12-year-old Jan Broberg is abducted from a small church-going community in Idaho by a trusted neighbour and close family friend.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Meyerowitz Stories (New and Selected)
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An estranged family gathers together in New York for an event celebrating the artistic work of their father.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: I Don't Feel at Home in This World Anymore
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When a depressed woman is burglarized, she finds a new sense of purpose by tracking down the thieves alongside her obnoxious neighbor. But they soon find themselves dangerously out of their depth against a pack of degenerate criminals.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Step Sisters
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Jamilah has her whole life figured out. She's the president of her black sorority, captain of their champion step dance crew, is student liaison to the college dean, and her next move is on to Harvard Law School. She's got it all, right? But when the hard-partying white girls from Sigma Beta Beta embarrass the school, Jamilah is ordered to come to the rescue. Her mission is to not only teach the rhythmically-challenged girls how to step dance, but to win the Steptacular, the most competitive of dance competitions. With the SBBs reputations and charter on the line, and Jamilah's dream of attending Harvard in jeopardy, these outcast screw-ups and their unlikely teacher stumble through one hilarious misstep after another. Cultures clash, romance blossoms, and sisterhood prevails as everyone steps out of their comfort zones.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Shack
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After suffering a family tragedy, Mack Phillips spirals into a deep depression causing him to question his innermost beliefs. Facing a crisis of faith, he receives a mysterious letter urging him to an abandoned shack deep in the Oregon wilderness. Despite his doubts, Mack journeys to the shack and encounters an enigmatic trio of strangers led by a woman named Papa. Through this meeting, Mack finds important truths that will transform his understanding of his tragedy and change his life forever.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Apostle
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In 1905, a man travels to a remote island in search of his missing sister who has been kidnapped by a mysterious religious cult.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Beirut
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In 1980s Beirut, Mason Skiles is a former U.S. diplomat who is called back into service to save a colleague from the group that is possibly responsible for his own family's death. Meanwhile, a CIA field agent who is working under cover at the American embassy is tasked with keeping Mason alive and ensuring that the mission is a success.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: To All the Boys I've Loved Before
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Lara Jean's love life goes from imaginary to out of control when her secret letters to every boy she's ever fallen for are mysteriously mailed out.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: My Little Pony: Equestria Girls
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Full-time students and part-time magical pony-girls, the Equestria Girls are always ready to save the day with the Magic of Friendship!

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Dragon Prince
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An extraordinary discovery inspires two human princes and an elven assassin to team up on an epic quest to bring peace to their warring lands.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bāhubali 2: The Conclusion
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When Mahendra, the son of Bāhubali, learns about his heritage, he begins to look for answers. His story is juxtaposed with past events that unfolded in the Mahishmati Kingdom.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Icarus
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: While investigating the furtive world of illegal doping in sports, director Bryan Fogel connects with renegade Russian scientist Dr. Grigory Rodchenkov—a pillar of his country’s “anti-doping” program. Over dozens of Skype calls, urine samples, and badly administered hormone injections, Fogel and Rodchenkov grow closer despite shocking allegations that place Rodchenkov at the center of Russia’s state-sponsored Olympic doping program.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Five Came Back
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The extraordinary story of how Hollywood changed World War II – and how World War II changed Hollywood, through the interwoven experiences of five legendary filmmakers who went to war to serve their country and bring the truth to the American people: John Ford, William Wyler, John Huston, Frank Capra, and George Stevens. Based on Mark Harris’ best-selling book, “Five Came Back: A Story of Hollywood and the Second World War.”

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: She-Ra and the Princesses of Power
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In this reboot of the '80s series, a magic sword transforms an orphan girl into warrior She-Ra, who unites a rebellion to fight against evil.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Kindergarten Teacher
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Lisa Spinelli is a Staten Island teacher who is unusually devoted to her students. When she discovers one of her five-year-olds is a prodigy, she becomes fascinated with the boy, ultimately risking her family and freedom to nurture his talent.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Chilling Adventures of Sabrina
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: As her 16th birthday nears, Sabrina must choose between the witch world of her family and the human world of her friends. Based on the Archie comic.
A simple yet proud rancher conspires to murder his wife for financial gain, convincing his teenage son to participate.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Little Italy
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Former childhood pals Leo and Nikki are attracted to each other as adults—but will their feuding parents' rival pizzerias put a chill on their sizzling romance?

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Hold the Dark
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In the grim Alaskan winter, a naturalist hunts for wolves blamed for killing a local boy, but he soon finds himself swept into a chilling mystery.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Perfection
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When troubled musical prodigy Charlotte seeks out Elizabeth, the new star pupil of her former school, the encounter sends both musicians down a sinister path with shocking consequences.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bright
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In an alternate present-day where magical creatures live among us, two L.A. cops become embroiled in a prophesied turf battle.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Evil Genius
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This baffling true crime story starts with the grisly death of a pizza man who robs a bank with a bomb around his neck - and gets weirder from there.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Everything Sucks!
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: It's 1996 in a town called Boring, Oregon, where high school misfits in the AV and drama clubs brave the ups and downs of teenage emotions in the VHS era.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Kodachrome
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Matt Ryder is convinced to drive his estranged and dying father Benjamin Ryder cross country to deliver four old rolls of Kodachrome film to the last lab in the world that can develop them before it shuts down for good. Along with Ben's nurse Zooey, the three navigate a world changing from analogue to digital while trying to put the past behind them.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Discovery
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In the near future, due to a breakthrough scientific discovery by Dr. Thomas Harbor, there is now definitive proof of an afterlife. While countless people have chosen suicide to reset their existence, others try to decide what it all means. Among them is Dr. Harbor's son Will, who has arrived at his father's isolated compound with a mysterious young woman named Isla. There, they discover the strange acolytes who help Dr. Harbor with his experiments.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Nightflyers
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In the year 2093, a team of scientists aboard the Nightflyer, the most advanced ship ever built, embarks on a journey to find other life forms. Their mission takes them to the edge of the solar system, and to the edge of insanity, as they realize true horror isn't waiting for them in outer space—it's already on their ship.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Extinction
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A chief mechanic at a factory, haunted by apocalyptic nightmares, becomes a hero when Earth is invaded by a mysterious army bent on destruction.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Book of Henry
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Susan, a single mother of two, works as a waitress in a small town. Her son, Henry, is an 11-year-old genius who not only manages the family finances but acts as emotional support for his mother and younger brother. When Henry discovers that the girl next door has a terrible secret, he implores Susan to take matters into her own hands.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Creep 2
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After finding an ad online for “video work,” Sara, a video artist whose primary focus is creating intimacy with lonely men, thinks she may have found the subject of her dreams. She drives to a remote house in the forest and meets a man claiming to be a serial killer. Unable to resist the chance to create a truly shocking piece of art, she agrees to spend the day with him. However, as the day goes on, she discovers she may have dug herself into a hole from which she can’t escape.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Speed Kills
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Speedboat racing champion and multimillionaire Ben Aronoff leads a double life that lands him in trouble with the law and drug lords.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Black Mirror: Bandersnatch
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In 1984, a young programmer begins to question reality as he adapts a dark fantasy novel into a video game. A mind-bending tale with multiple endings.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: When We First Met
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Noah spends the perfect first night with the girl of his dreams Avery but gets relegated to the friend zone. He spends the next three years wondering what went wrong - until he gets the unexpected chance to travel back in time and alter that night, and his fate, over and over again.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dear White People
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: At a predominantly white Ivy League college, a diverse group of students navigate various forms of racial and other types of discrimination.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mudbound
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In the post–World War II South, two families are pitted against a barbaric social hierarchy and an unrelenting landscape as they simultaneously fight the battle at home and the battle abroad.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Anon
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Set in a near-future world where there is no privacy, ignorance or anonymity, our private memories are recorded and crime almost ceases to exist. In trying to solve a series of unsolved murders, Sal Frieland stumbles onto a young woman who appears to have subverted the system and disappeared. She has no identity, no history and no record. Sal realizes it may not be the end of crime but the beginning. Known only as 'The Girl', Sal must find her before he becomes the next victim.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Jim & Andy: The Great Beyond - Featuring a Very Special, Contractually Obligated Mention of Tony Clifton
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Offbeat documentarian Chris Smith provides a behind-the-scenes look at how Jim Carrey adopted the persona of idiosyncratic comedian Andy Kaufman on the set of Man on the Moon.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: A-X-L
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The life of a teenage boy is forever altered by a chance encounter with cutting edge military technology.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Hell Fest
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: On Halloween night at a horror theme park, a costumed killer begins slaying innocent patrons who believe that it's all part of the festivities.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Two Sentence Horror Stories
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This anthology series of terror features diverse characters facing primal fears in spine-chilling situations that stretch past daily routine.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dirty Money
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: From crippling payday loans to cars that cheat emissions tests, this investigative series exposes brazen acts of corporate greed and corruption.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Nailed It!
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Home bakers who have a poor track record in the kitchen seek redemption -- and cash -- on this series. In each episode, three contestants try their hand at re-creating edible masterpieces. The projects don't always turn out great, but whichever amateur baker comes closest to a successful dessert by the end of the episode takes home the $10,000 prize, which they might want to use on baking lessons. Comic Nicole Byer and renowned pastry chef Jacques Torres host. It's part reality contest, part hot mess.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: My Mister
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a world that is less than kind, a young woman and a middle-aged man develop a sense of kinship as they find warmth and comfort in one another.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: My Mister
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a world that is less than kind, a young woman and a middle-aged man develop a sense of kinship as they find warmth and comfort in one another.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dave Chappelle
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Comedy icon Dave Chappelle makes his triumphant return to the screen with a pair of blistering, fresh stand-up specials.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Damnation
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Seth Davenport is masquerading as a small town Iowa preacher in the hopes of starting a full-blown insurrection against the status quo, unaware that an industrialist tycoon has hired a professional strikebreaker to stop the uprising by any means necessary. An epic saga of the secret history of the 1930’s American heartland, chronicling the mythic conflict and bloody struggle between big money and the downtrodden, God and greed, charlatans, and prophets.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Great News
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A New Jersey mom puts her relationship with her daughter to the test when she lands an internship at the same TV station where her daughter works.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: 22 July
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In Norway on 22 July 2011, neo-Nazi terrorist Anders Behring Breivik murdered 77 young people attending a Labour Party Youth Camp on Utöya Island outside of Oslo. This three-part story will focus on the survivors of the attacks, the political leadership of Norway, and the lawyers involved.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Insatiable
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A bullied teenager turns to beauty pageants as a way to exact her revenge, with the help of a disgraced coach who soon realizes he's in over his head.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Explained
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This documentary series, made in partnership with Vox, explain some of the world's current trends, from politics, to science to pop culture.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Buster's Mal Heart
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An eccentric mountain man on the run from the local sheriff recalls the mysterious events that brought him to his present fugitive state.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Toys That Made Us
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The minds behind history's most iconic toy franchises discuss the rise -- and sometimes fall -- of their billion-dollar creations.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ben Is Back
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: 19-year-old Ben Burns unexpectedly returns home to his family's suburban home on Christmas Eve morning. Ben's mother, Holly, is relieved and welcoming but wary of her son staying clean. Over a turbulent 24 hours, new truths are revealed, and a mother's undying love for her son is tested as she does everything in her power to keep him safe.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mr. Sunshine
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Set in the early 1900s, this drama tells the story of a young man from Korea who grows up in the United States. When he returns to Korea as a US Marine Corps officer, he meets and falls in love with a noblewoman who is fighting for Korean independence. Their romance is complicated by social class and political ideology.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mr. Sunshine
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Set in the early 1900s, this drama tells the story of a young man from Korea who grows up in the United States. When he returns to Korea as a US Marine Corps officer, he meets and falls in love with a noblewoman who is fighting for Korean independence. Their romance is complicated by social class and political ideology.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Private Life
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Richard and Rachel, a couple in the throes of infertility, try to maintain their marriage as they descend deeper and deeper into the insular world of assisted reproduction and domestic adoption.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: RBG
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Justice Ruth Bader Ginsburg now 84, and still inspired by the lawyers who defended free speech during the Red Scare, Ginsburg refuses to relinquish her passionate duty, steadily fighting for equal rights for all citizens under the law. Through intimate interviews and unprecedented access to Ginsburg’s life outside the court, RBG tells the electric story of Ginsburg’s consuming love affairs with both the Constitution and her beloved husband Marty—and of a life’s work that led her to become an icon of justice in the highest court in the land.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: An Evening with Beverly Luff Linn
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Lulu Danger's unsatisfying marriage takes a turn for the worse when a mysterious man from her past comes to town to perform an event called "An Evening with Beverly Luff Linn: For One Magical Night Only."

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Friends from College
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Twenty years after graduation, a tight-knit group of college friends reconnects and discovers that love hasn't gotten easier with age.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mary Magdalene
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In the first century, free-spirited Mary Magdalene flees the marriage her family has arranged for her, finding refuge and a sense of purpose in a radical new movement led by the charismatic, rabble-rousing preacher named Jesus.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Disjointed
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Pot activist Ruth Whitefeather Feldman runs a medical marijuana dispensary while encouraging her loyal patients to chill out and enjoy the high life.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dumplin'
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: To prove a point about measuring up and fitting in, Texas teen Willowdean “Dumplin’” Dickson enters a local pageant run by her ex-beauty queen mom.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Tau
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Held captive in a futuristic smart house, a woman hopes to escape by befriending the A.I. program that controls the house.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Wormwood
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In this genre-bending tale, Errol Morris explores the mysterious death of a U.S. scientist entangled in a secret Cold War program known as MK-Ultra.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Duck Butter
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Dissatisfied with the dishonesty they see in dating, strangers Naima and Sergio make a pact to spend 24 straight hours together in an attempt to fast forward their relationship.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Never Stop Dreaming: The Life and Legacy of Shimon Peres
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A look back on the life of Nobel Peace Prize winner, Shimon Peres, who served as prime minister of Israel twice and negotiated the 1994 Israel-Jordan peace treaty.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Zookeeper's Wife
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The account of keepers of the Warsaw Zoo, Jan and Antonina Zabinski, who helped save hundreds of people and animals during the Nazi invasion.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Game Over, Man!
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Three friends are on the verge of getting their video game financed when their benefactor is taken hostage by terrorists.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Polly Pocket
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The series, based on the doll of the same name, will feature a young girl called Polly who has a magical locket that allows her and her friends to shrink down to a tiny size.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Steve Martin and Martin Short: An Evening You Will Forget for the Rest of Your Life
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Comedians and writers Steve Martin and Martin Short perform a live comedy set with music by The Steep Canyon Rangers and jazz pianist, Jeff Babko, at the Peace Center in Greenville, South Carolina.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Victoria & Abdul
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Queen Victoria strikes up an unlikely friendship with a young Indian clerk named Abdul Karim.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: War Machine
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A rock star general bent on winning the “impossible” war in Afghanistan takes us inside the complex machinery of modern war. Inspired by the true story of General Stanley McChrystal.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Norm Macdonald Has a Show
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Based on his podcast, comedianNorm Macdonald and his sidekick Adam Egret sit down and chat with celebrity guests about their life, career and views in a somewhat unconventional and often irreverent way.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Gypsy
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The journey of Jean Holloway – a therapist who begins to develop dangerous and intimate relationships with the people in her patients' lives.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Minecraft: Story Mode
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: MInecraft: Story Mode is an interactive, animated TV series from Netflix and Telltale Games. Viewers input decisions that affect the course of the story, using a remote control or computer keyboard.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Titan
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: On a bleak future Earth, a soldier endures a radical genetic transformation to save humanity. But his wife fears he's becoming more creature than man.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Security
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An ex-special services veteran, down on his luck and desperate for work, takes a job as a security guard at a run-down mall in a rough area of town. On his first night on the job, he opens the door to a distraught and desperate young girl who has fled the hijacking of a Police motorcade that was transporting her to testify as a witness in a trial. Hot on her heels is the psychopathic hijacker and his team of henchmen, who will stop at nothing to extract and eliminate the witness.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Transformers: Cyberverse
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When Bumblebee begins to suffer amnesia, his partner, Windblade, comes to the rescue, and repairs his memory chips, enabling him to rediscover his past adventures on Cybertron. Once his memories are repaired, Bumblebee gets a clue that will lead both him and Windblade to complete their current mission and save their friends, unaware that Megatron sent his Decepticon assassins to hunt them down.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mowgli: Legend of the Jungle
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A human child raised by wolves, must face off against a menacing tiger named Shere Khan, as well as his own origins.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Abstract: The Art of Design
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Step inside the minds of the most innovative designers in a variety of disciplines and learn how design impacts every aspect of life.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: A Futile and Stupid Gesture
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The National Lampoon name became globally recognized after the monumental success of Animal House—but before the glory days, it was a scrappy yet divinely subversive magazine and radio show that introduced the world to comedic geniuses like Bill Murray, Chevy Chase, John Belushi, and Gilda Radner. The driving force behind National Lampoon was Doug Kenney, and his truly wild and crazy story unfolds in A Futile and Stupid Gesture from Harvard to Hollywood to Caddyshack and beyond.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: How It Ends
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A desperate father tries to return home to his pregnant wife after a mysterious apocalyptic event turns everything to chaos.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Death Note
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A young man comes to possess a supernatural notebook, the Death Note, that grants him the power to kill any person simply by writing down their name on the pages. He then decides to use the notebook to kill criminals and change the world, but an enigmatic detective attempts to track him down and end his reign of terror.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Boss Baby: Back in Business
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: With a little help from his brother and accomplice, Tim, Boss Baby tries to balance family life with his job at Baby Corp headquarters.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The After Party
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When an aspiring rapper goes viral for the wrong reasons, he thinks his career is sunk. But a wild party gives him one more chance to make it right.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Other Side of the Wind
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Surrounded by fans and skeptics, grizzled director J.J. "Jake" Hannaford returns from years abroad in Europe to a changed Hollywood, where he attempts to make his innovative comeback film.  This film was started in 1970 but never completed during Welles lifetime.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: To the Bone
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A young woman dealing with anorexia meets an unconventional doctor who challenges her to face her condition and embrace life.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Innocent Man
