data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a story that gained national attention with John Grisham’s best-selling non-fiction book, The Innocent Man: Murder and Injustice in a Small Town, the six-part documentary series The Innocent Man focuses on two murders that shook the small town of Ada, Oklahoma, in the 1980s — and the controversial chain of events that followed.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Hot Girls Wanted: Turned On
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Porn has gone mainstream; the question is, can we handle it? This exploration of the intersection of sex and technology is told through the stories of the people whose lives are defined by the current explosion of internet porn-whether they're creating it, consuming it, or both.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: We the Animals
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Manny, Joel and Jonah tear their way through childhood and push against the volatile love of their parents. As Manny and Joel grow into versions of their father and Ma dreams of escape, Jonah, the youngest, embraces an imagined world all his own.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Reversing Roe
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Documentary that delves deep into the history of abortion law, revealing the contradictory ways in which women's bodies have been used to further political and ideological agendas.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Beyond Skyline
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Detective Mark Corley storms his way onto an alien spaceship to rescue his estranged son. When the ship crashes in Southeast Asia, he forges an alliance with a band of survivors to take back the planet once and for all.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: VeggieTales in the City
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: With exciting trips to the big city, the ski slopes and beyond, the Veggie friends expand their horizons and learn valuable faith-based lessons.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Valor
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The boundaries between military discipline and human desire are tested on a U.S. Army base that houses an elite unit of helicopter pilots trained to perform clandestine international and domestic missions. The drama unfolds in the present as well as in flashbacks to a failed mission involving one of the first female pilots in the unit, ultimately uncovering layers of personal and government/military secrets and leading to a season-long plan to rescue a group of MIA soldiers.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Illang: The Wolf Brigade
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In 2029, the elite police squad Illang combats a terrorist group opposing reunification of the two Koreas. But another enemy may be lurking nearby.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Illang: The Wolf Brigade
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In 2029, the elite police squad Illang combats a terrorist group opposing reunification of the two Koreas. But another enemy may be lurking nearby.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Shirkers
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In 1992, teenager Sandi Tan shot Singapore's first indie road movie with her enigmatic American mentor Georges – who then vanished with all the footage. Twenty years later, the 16mm film is recovered, sending Tan, now a novelist in Los Angeles, on a personal odyssey in search of Georges' vanishing footprints.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: A Bad Moms Christmas
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Amy, Kiki and Carla – three under-appreciated and over-burdened women – rebel against the challenges and expectations of the Super Bowl for mothers: Christmas. And if creating a more perfect holiday for their families wasn’t hard enough, they have to do all of that while hosting and entertaining their own mothers.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Hotel Transylvania: The Series
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Mavis navigates life without her dad, Dracula, around and discovers one of the few common human and monster truths: being a teenager bites.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Welcome Home
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A couple try to repair their damaged union in an Italian vacation paradise. Then they discover the owner's intentions.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Piercing
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After kissing his wife and baby goodbye for a seemingly normal business trip, Reed checks himself into a hotel room to accomplish something he’s always dreamed of: the perfect murder. As his sinister plans unfold, he soon realizes he might be in over his head with a mysteriously unhinged call girl named Jackie.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Outsider
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A former American G.I. joins a yakuza family after his release from prison in post-World War II Osaka.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Car Masters: Rust to Riches
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The colorful crew at Gotham Garage overhauls an eclectic collection of cars and trucks, trading up to a showstopper they can sell for big bucks.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: On My Block
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A coming of age comedy following a diverse group of teenage friends as they confront the challenges of growing up in gritty inner-city Los Angeles.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Spy Kids: Mission Critical
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In this animated spinoff series, Juni and Carmen Cortez must battle the evil organization S.W.A.M.P. -- without the help of their super-spy parents.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Andhadhun
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A series of mysterious events changes the life of a blind pianist who now must report a crime that was actually never witnessed by him.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Unicorn Store
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A woman named Kit moves back to her parent's house, where she receives a mysterious invitation that would fulfill her childhood dreams.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Hot Date
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A sketch-comedy series that chronicles the social waters of dating, sex, marriage and diving into the ritual of romance. Based on the CollegeHumor webseries of the same name.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Paradise PD
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An eager young rookie joins the ragtag small-town police force led by his dad as they bumble, squabble and snort their way through a big drug case.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Newness
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In contemporary Los Angeles, two millennials navigating a social media–driven hookup culture begin a relationship that pushes both emotional and physical boundaries.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Monster High: Electrified
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When Clawdeen dreams of opening a salon made for monsters and normies, Frankie has the perfect place - an abandoned power station outside town. But the idea sparks negative voltage when Moanica plots to ruin the whole thing, and replace the celebration with something a little more... shocking! Luckily the ghouls have a secret weapon on their side...Twyla, the daughter of the Boogey Man, and the perfect ghoul to unearth any mystery. Along with the most voltageous salon ever! So catch every twist, turn, zap and blast...because the Monster High ghouls are about to get ELECTRIC!

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: No Escape Room
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A father and daughter check out a small town escape room and discover there is something sinister about the place.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Somewhere Between
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Laura Price, a local news producer in San Francisco, is helping the police to hunt down a serial killer. After the killer strikes close to home, a twist of fate allows a “Groundhog Day”-type reset, and Laura relives the week prior to the string of murders. Can she change fate and stop the killer?

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Haunted
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Real people sit down with friends and family to share terrifying true stories from their past, re-created through chilling re-enactments.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: If I Leave Here Tomorrow: A Film About Lynyrd Skynyrd
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The story of Lynyrd Skynyrd; The Greatest American Rock Band Ever. We fly beyond Free Bird to celebrate the life & times of leader Ronnie Van Zant, from boogie-woogie beginnings in Jacksonville’s Shantytown to a tragic end in a Mississippi swamp.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Week Of
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The parents of a soon-to-be married couple make the final preparations for the wedding ceremony.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Standups
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Comedy's freshest voices take the stage in LA for six half-hour specials packed with sly jokes, hilarious anecdotes and awkward confessions.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Bride of Habaek
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Yoon So Ah is a pragmatic neuropsychiatrist who carries a tremendous financial burden to run her own practice. Her family has been tasked with serving Ha Baek, a reincarnated water god, for many generations, and So Ah is forced to do the same. Ha Baek starts to develop feelings for So Ah, but he has competition for her heart from Hoo Ye, the CEO of a resort company, who clashes with So Ah over a piece of land but then falls in love with her. Can a relationship between a mortal female and a god have a future?

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Bride of Habaek
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Yoon So Ah is a pragmatic neuropsychiatrist who carries a tremendous financial burden to run her own practice. Her family has been tasked with serving Ha Baek, a reincarnated water god, for many generations, and So Ah is forced to do the same. Ha Baek starts to develop feelings for So Ah, but he has competition for her heart from Hoo Ye, the CEO of a resort company, who clashes with So Ah over a piece of land but then falls in love with her. Can a relationship between a mortal female and a god have a future?

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: El Chapo
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A look at the life of notorious drug kingpin, El Chapo, from his early days in the 1980s working for the Guadalajara Cartel, to his rise to power of during the '90s and his ultimate downfall in 2016.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: What the Health
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Filmmaker Kip Andersen uncovers the secret to preventing and even reversing chronic diseases, and he investigates why the nation's leading health organizations doesn't want people to know about it.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Long Dumb Road
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Two guys serendipitously meet at a time when they both find themselves at personal crossroads and decide to embark on an unplanned road trip across the American Southwest.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Long Shot
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When Juan Catalan is arrested for a murder he insists he didn't commit, he builds his case for innocence around unexpected raw footage.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dude
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Four best friends negotiate loss and major life changes during the last two weeks of high school.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Debt Collector
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A classically-trained martial artist goes to work as a debt collector for the mob. The job seems easy enough, until one “client” pulls him into a situation deeper than could ever be expected.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sugar Rush
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A relentlessly fast-paced baking competition that challenges brilliant bakers to create sweet treats that look and taste amazing – all against the clock. Who will race to the finish and win $10,000?

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Win It All
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A gambling addict faces a conflict when entrusted with keeping a bunch of money that isn't his.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Tottaa Pataaka Item Maal
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Four women from Delhi, NCR and Gurgaon, tired of dealing with the incessant fear or rape, decide to teach one man how it feels to be afraid of being raped, on a daily basis.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Joan Didion: The Center Will Not Hold
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Griffin Dunne’s years-in-the-making documentary portrait of his aunt Joan Didion moves with the spirit of her uncannily lucid writing: the film simultaneously expands and zeroes in, covering a vast stretch of turbulent cultural history with elegance and candor.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Guest
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The story of a psychic, a priest, and a detective who fight unusual crimes committed by strange powers.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Guest
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The story of a psychic, a priest, and a detective who fight unusual crimes committed by strange powers.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Incredible Jessica James
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Burned by a bad breakup, a struggling New York City playwright makes an unlikely connection with a divorced app designer she meets on a blind date.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Siberia
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Lucas, a diamond trader who travels to Saint Petersburg to arrange a sale, discovers that his Russian business partner has left his hotel and gone to a small Siberian village, so Lucas also heads there to try find him.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ugly Delicious
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Star chef David Chang leads friends on a mouthwatering, cross-cultural hunt for the world's most satisfying grub. All the flavor. None of the BS.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: John Mulaney: Kid Gorgeous at Radio City
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: John Mulaney relays stories from his childhood and "SNL," eviscerates the value of college and laments getting older in this electric comedy special.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Girlboss
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Sophia is a rebellious, broke anarchist who refuses to grow up. She stumbles upon her passion of selling vintage clothes online and becomes an unlikely businesswoman. As she builds her retail fashion empire, she realizes the value and the difficulty of being the boss of her own life.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Because This Is My First Life
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Nam Se-Hee is a single man in his early 30s. He has chosen to not marry. He owns his home, but he owes a lot on his mortgage. Yoon Ji-Ho is a single woman in her early 30s. She does not own a home and envies those that do. She has given up on dating due to her financial struggles. Yoon Ji-Ho begins to live at Nam Se-Hee’s house. They become housemates.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Because This Is My First Life
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Nam Se-Hee is a single man in his early 30s. He has chosen to not marry. He owns his home, but he owes a lot on his mortgage. Yoon Ji-Ho is a single woman in her early 30s. She does not own a home and envies those that do. She has given up on dating due to her financial struggles. Yoon Ji-Ho begins to live at Nam Se-Hee’s house. They become housemates.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Just Between Lovers
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Two survivors of a building collapse discover support and love in each other as they overcome the pain of loss and reconstruct a hopeful future.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Just Between Lovers
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Two survivors of a building collapse discover support and love in each other as they overcome the pain of loss and reconstruct a hopeful future.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Saint
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: International master thief, Simon Templar, also known as The Saint, is asked by a desperate rich man to find his kidnapped daughter. However, in addition to evading the authorities, Simon must face a dangerous adversary from his past.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: In Darkness
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A blind musician hears a murder committed in the apartment upstairs from hers that sends her down a dark path into London's gritty criminal underworld.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bill Nye Saves the World
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Bill Nye explores science and its impact on politics, society and pop culture. Each episode tackles a topic from a scientific point of view, dispelling myths, and refuting anti-scientific claims that may be espoused by politicians, religious leaders or titans of industry.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sierra Burgess Is a Loser
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A case of mistaken identity results in unexpected romance when the most popular girl in high school and the biggest loser must come together to win over their crushes.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ibiza
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: She could do the responsible thing. Or she could go to Ibiza with her best friends to chase down a hot DJ. Easy choice.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Shimmer Lake
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Shot in reverse day-by-day through a week—a local sheriff embarks on a quest to unlock the mystery of three small-town criminals and a bank heist gone wrong.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Hey Arnold! The Jungle Movie
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When their trip to San Lorenzo takes a turn for the worst, Arnold and his classmate’s only hope of getting home is retracing the dangerous path that led to Arnold's parents' disappearance.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Spirit: Riding Free
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a small Western town, spunky ex-city girl Lucky forms a tight bond with wild horse Spirit while having adventures with best pals Pru and Abigail.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Good Cop
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Honest cop Tony Jr. gets advice from his unscrupulous father, retired NYPD officer Tony Sr., about everything from his job to his love life.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Wheelman
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A getaway driver for a bank robbery realizes he has been double crossed and races to find out who betrayed him.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Voice
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: It's 3 minutes for hearers, but a life for the callers. A crime thriller chasing even the slightest sounds to rescue people's lives calling for urgent help.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Voice
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: It's 3 minutes for hearers, but a life for the callers. A crime thriller chasing even the slightest sounds to rescue people's lives calling for urgent help.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Cristela Alonzo: Lower Classy
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The irrepressible Alonzo skewers Latino stereotypes, pricey luxuries and her mother's tough-love parenting in a night of sly and infectious comedy.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Patriot Act with Hasan Minhaj
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Every Sunday, Hasan Minhaj brings an incisive and nuanced perspective to global news, politics and culture in his unique comedy series.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Fourth-grade friends George and Harold have a shared love of pranks and comic books -- and turning their principal into an undies-wearing superhero.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: You Get Me
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After arguing with his girlfriend, Ali, Tyler lands in the arms of sexy new girl, Holly. The next morning, he finds that not only does Ali agree to take him back, but Holly is a new student at their school and is dead set on her new man.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Rotten
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This docuseries travels deep into the heart of the food supply chain to reveal unsavory truths and expose hidden forces that shape what we eat.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Murder Mountain
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In Humboldt County, California, the big business of legal marijuana brings in visitors from around the world. Some are never seen again.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: My Teacher, My Obsession
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Riley is struggling to make friends after transferring to a new high school where her father, Chris, is an English teacher. When she meets Kyla, they quickly becomes close friends. However, the friendship takes a strange turn when Riley learns that Kyla is obsessed with her dad. Will Kyla successfully seduce Chris and start a twisted new life with him by removing everyone in her path, or will Riley be able to save her father from Kyla’s treacherous plot before it’s too late?

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Voyeur
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Journalism icon Gay Talese reports on Gerald Foos, the Colorado motel owner who allegedly secretly watched his guests with the aid of specially designed ceiling vents, peering down from an "observation platform" he built in the motel's attic.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bathtubs Over Broadway
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When he started as a comedy writer for the Late Show with David Letterman, Steve Young had few interests and not many friends outside of his day job. But while gathering material for a segment on the show, Steve stumbled onto a few vintage record albums that would change his life forever.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Psychokinesis
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An ordinary guy suddenly finds he has superpowers he can use to help his spirited daughter and the people around them, but he also runs into trouble in the process.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Psychokinesis
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An ordinary guy suddenly finds he has superpowers he can use to help his spirited daughter and the people around them, but he also runs into trouble in the process.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Alexa & Katie
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Lifelong best friends Alexa and Katie are eagerly anticipating the start of their freshman year of high school. The pals confront a crisis that leaves them feeling like outsiders at a time when what seems to matter most is fitting in.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Chip and Potato
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Lovable pug Chip starts kindergarten, makes new friends and tries new things -- with a little help from Potato, her secret mouse pal.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Adam Sandler: 100% Fresh
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Adam Sandler takes his comical musical musings back out on the road, from comedy clubs to concert halls to one very unsuspecting subway station.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Polka King
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Local Pennsylvania polka legend Jan Lewan develops a plan to get rich that shocks his fans and lands him in jail.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: First They Killed My Father
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A 5-year-old girl embarks on a harrowing quest for survival amid the sudden rise and terrifying reign of the Khmer Rouge in Cambodia.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Magic School Bus Rides Again
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Ms. Frizzle's sister takes her class on a slew of wild science adventures in this update of the beloved animated show.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dogs
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: These six intimate stories explore the abiding emotional bonds that form between dogs and their caregivers, no matter the circumstances.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Magic for Humans
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: From baffling people on the street to orchestrating elaborate tricks, Justin Willman blends good-natured magic with grown-up laughs.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: QB1: Beyond the Lights
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A 10-part docuseries following high-school quarterbacks, on and off the field, throughout their unforgettable senior seasons.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Show Dogs
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Starring Will Arnett, Chris "Ludacris" Bridges, Natasha Lyonne, Jordin Sparks, Gabriel Iglesias, Shaquille O'Neal, Alan Cumming, and Stanley Tucci, SHOW DOGS is a family comedy about the unlikely pairing of a human detective (Arnett) and his canine partner (voice of Chris "Ludacris" Bridges), who has to go undercover at the world's most exclusive dog show to solve his biggest case yet.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: 7 Days Out
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Witness the excitement and drama behind the scenes in the seven days leading up to major live events in the worlds of sports, fashion, space and food.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Girlfriend's Day
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When he's caught up in a deadly conspiracy, an unemployed greeting card writer must create the perfect card for a new holiday to save his skin.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Resurrection of Gavin Stone
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Gavin Stone, a washed-up former child star, is forced to do community service at a local megachurch and pretends to be Christian so he can land the part of Jesus in their annual Passion Play, only to discover that the most important role of his life is far from Hollywood.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: 3Below: Tales of Arcadia
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After crash-landing on Earth, two royal teen aliens on the run struggle to blend in with humans as they evade intergalactic bounty hunters.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: One of Us
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Penetrating the insular world of New York's Hasidic community, focusing on three individuals driven to break away despite threats of retaliation.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Taylor Swift: Reputation Stadium Tour
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Taylor Swift takes the stage in Dallas for the Reputation Stadium Tour and celebrates a monumental night of music, memories and visual magic.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Like Father
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When a workaholic young executive, is left at the altar, she ends up on her Caribbean honeymoon cruise with the last person she ever expected: her estranged and equally workaholic father. The two depart as strangers, but over the course of a few hilarious adventures, a couple of umbrella-clad cocktails and a whole lot of soul-searching, they return with a renewed appreciation for family and life.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Black
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A Grim Reaper, a detective and a woman who foresees death get ensnared in matters of life and death -- and dark mysteries of twenty years past.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Black
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A Grim Reaper, a detective and a woman who foresees death get ensnared in matters of life and death -- and dark mysteries of twenty years past.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: She's Gotta Have It
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Nola Darling struggles to define herself and divide her time among her friends, job and three lovers. A new take on Spike Lee's film, in 10 episodes.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Amar
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Laura and Carlos love each other as if every day was the last, and perhaps that first love intensity is what will tear them apart a year later.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Birth of the Dragon
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Set against the backdrop of San Francisco’s Chinatown, this cross-cultural biopic chronicles Bruce Lee’s emergence as a martial-arts superstar after his legendary secret showdown with fellow martial artist Wong Jack Man.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Outside In
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An ex-con struggling to readjust to life in his small town forms an intense bond with his former high-school teacher.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Memories of the Alhambra
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: While looking for the cryptic creator of an innovative augmented-reality game, an investment firm executive meets a woman who runs a hostel in Spain.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Memories of the Alhambra
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: While looking for the cryptic creator of an innovative augmented-reality game, an investment firm executive meets a woman who runs a hostel in Spain.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Irreplaceable You
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A couple who have known each other since 8 are destined to be together until death do them apart.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Confession Tapes
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This true crime documentary series investigates cases where people convicted of murder claim their confessions were coerced, involuntary or false.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sandy Wexler
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When a hapless but dedicated talent manager signs his first client who actually has talent, his career finally starts to take off.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Alex Strangelove
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Alex Truelove is on a quest to lose his virginity, an event eagerly awaited by his patient girlfriend and cheered on with welcome advice by his rowdy friends. But Alex, a super gregarious dude, is oddly unmotivated. A magical house party throws Alex into the presence of Elliot, a hunky college guy, who pegs Alex as gay and flirts hard. Alex is taken aback but after a series of setbacks on the girlfriend front he takes the plunge and learns some interesting new facts about himself.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Gaga: Five Foot Two
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Go behind the scenes with pop provocateur Lady Gaga as she releases a bold new album and prepares for her Super Bowl halftime show.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Free Rein
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A 15-year-old from LA spends the summer at her mom's childhood home on an island off the coast of England, where she bonds with a mysterious horse.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sacred Games
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A link in their pasts leads an honest cop to a fugitive gang boss, whose cryptic warning spurs the officer on a quest to save Mumbai from cataclysm.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Get Me Roger Stone
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: From his days of testifying at the Watergate hearings to advising recent presidential candidate Donald Trump, Roger Stone has long offended people on both sides of the political fence as a force in conservative America. Outspoken author, pundit, ahead of his time election strategist, this is his story.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Animal Crackers
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A family must use a magical box of Animal Crackers to save a rundown circus from being taken over by their evil uncle Horatio P. Huntington.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Shot in the Dark
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Three rival freelance stringers scour the streets at night to film crime scenes, fires, accidents -- and anything else they can sell to news outlets.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Rainbow Rangers
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Inspired by the colors of the rainbow, seven magical girls from Kaleidoscopia are guardians of both nature and the Earth.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Unsolved: The Murders of Tupac and The Notorious B.I.G.
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A chronicle of the two major police investigations by LAPD Detective Greg Kading into the deaths of Tupac and The Notorious B.I.G.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Daniel Sloss: Live Shows
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Comedian Daniel Sloss is ready to find the funny in some very dark topics, from the deeply personal to the truly irreverent.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Beauty Inside
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: It is a love story of Han Se-gye who is an A-list actress. She is known as a troublemaker and the object of many rumors. Her life is a mystery, but, in reality, she suffers from an unusual phenomenon. At a certain point every month, her appearance changes to a different person. She lives one week out of every month with a different appearance, and Seo Do-jae who is an executive director of an airline company. He seems perfect with an attractive appearance and intelligence but, he suffers from prosopagnosia. He hides this disability and tries hard to memorize people by their habits and mannerisms. The only face that he is able to recognize is Han Se-gye’s.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Beauty Inside

The only face that he is able to recognize is Han Se-gye’s.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Love Daily
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Romantic anthology web series revolving around 12 stories of 12 months of young people on their paths to love.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mr. Roosevelt
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A young woman returns home and must confront her ex-boyfriend when an unexpected tragedy occurs.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Clive Davis: The Soundtrack of Our Lives
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The life and successes of iconic music executive Clive Davis, from his miraculous start at Columbia Records through his trailblazing work at Arista Records and J Records, with a heavy dose of outstanding music sprinkled in between.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Christmas Chronicles
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Siblings Kate and Teddy try to prove Santa Claus is real, but when they accidentally cause his sleigh to crash, they have to save Christmas.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bill Nye: Science Guy
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Bill Nye is retiring his kid show act in a bid to become more like his late professor, astronomer Carl Sagan. Sagan dreamed of launching a spacecraft that could revolutionize interplanetary exploration. Bill sets out to accomplish Sagan's mission, but he is pulled away when he is challenged by evolution and climate change contrarians to defend the scientific consensus. Can Bill show the world why science matters in a culture increasingly indifferent to evidence?

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Welcome to Waikiki
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description:
Kang Dong-Goo dreams of becoming a movie director, but he is cynical due to bad luck. Cheon Joon-Ki wanted to follow in his father's footsteps and become an actor, but he is now just a minor actor. Bong-Doo-Sik came to Seoul to become a scenario writer, but things have not been easy for him.

These 3 men run the guest house Waikiki in Itaewon, South Korea. Their guest house is facing bankruptcy and then a mysterious baby and single mother appear at Waikiki.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Welcome to Waikiki
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description:
Kang Dong-Goo dreams of becoming a movie director, but he is cynical due to bad luck. Cheon Joon-Ki wanted to follow in his father's footsteps and become an actor, but he is now just a minor actor. Bong-Doo-Sik came to Seoul to become a scenario writer, but things have not been easy for him.

These 3 men run the guest house Waikiki in Itaewon, South Korea. Their guest house is facing bankruptcy and then a mysterious baby and single mother appear at Waikiki.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Quincy
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An intimate look into the life of icon Quincy Jones. A unique force in music and popular culture for 70 years, Jones has transcended racial and cultural boundaries; his story is inextricably woven into the fabric of America.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Cuba and the Cameraman
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This revealing portrait of Cuba follows the lives of Fidel Castro and three Cuban families affected by his policies over the last four decades.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Greenhouse Academy
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When teen siblings Hayley and Alex enter an elite boarding school, they find rivalry, romance and a mystery related to the recent loss of their mom.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Champions
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Vince, a charismatic gym owner with no ambition lives with his younger brother Michael, a gorgeous idiot. Their simple life of women and working out is put on hold when the teenage son of Vince is dropped off on their doorstep by Priya, one of his old high school flings.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Acts of Vengeance
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A fast-talking lawyer transforms his body and takes a vow of silence, not to be broken until he finds out who killed his wife and daughter and has his revenge.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Carrie Pilby
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Awkward, isolated and disapproving of most of the people around her, a precocious 19-year-old genius is challenged to put her convictions to the test by venturing out on to the NYC dating scene.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Clapper
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: 15 minutes of fame destroys the life of a man who works as a clapper in television.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Fun Mom Dinner
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Four women, whose kids attend the same preschool class, get together for a "fun mom dinner". When the night takes an unexpected turn, these unlikely new friends realize they have more in common than just marriage and motherhood.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Land of Steady Habits
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After leaving his wife and his job to find happiness, Anders begins a clumsy, heartbreaking quest to reassemble the pieces of his fractured life.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: SKY Castle
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The drama revolves around the lives of housewives living in a luxurious residential area called SKY Castle in suburban Seoul, where wealthy doctors and professors live. The wives are determined to make their husbands more successful and to raise their children like princes and princesses and to be top students.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: SKY Castle
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The drama revolves around the lives of housewives living in a luxurious residential area called SKY Castle in suburban Seoul, where wealthy doctors and professors live. The wives are determined to make their husbands more successful and to raise their children like princes and princesses and to be top students.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Our Souls at Night
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Addie Moore and Louis Waters, a widow and widower, have lived next to each other for years. The pair have almost no relationship, but that all changes when Addie tries to make a connection with her neighbour.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Escape from Mr. Lemoncello's Library
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Can twelve 12-year-olds escape from the most ridiculously brilliant library ever created? Escape from Mr. Lemoncello's Library plunks a dozen sixth-graders into the middle of a futuristic library for a night of nonstop fun and adventure.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Life Sentence
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When Stella finds out her terminal cancer is cured, she's going to have to learn to live with all the choices she's made when she decided to "live like she was dying".

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Springsteen On Broadway
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Springsteen on Broadway is a solo acoustic performance written and performed by Tony Award, Academy Award, and 20-time Grammy Award winner Bruce Springsteen. Based on his worldwide best-selling autobiography 'Born to Run,' Springsteen on Broadway is a unique evening with Bruce, his guitar, a piano, and his very personal stories. In addition, it features a special appearance by Patti Scialfa. Netflix will allow global audiences to see the show critics have been raving about from anywhere they are.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bullet Head
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A group of career criminals finds itself trapped in a warehouse with the law – and an Attack Dog named DeNiro closing in.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Small Crimes
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A disgraced former cop, fresh off a six-year prison sentence for attempted murder, returns home looking for redemption but winds up trapped in the mess he left behind.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Unrest
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When Harvard PhD student Jennifer Brea is struck down at 28 by a fever that leaves her bedridden, doctors tell her it’s "all in her head." Determined to live, she sets out on a virtual journey to document her story—and four other families' stories—fighting a disease medicine forgot.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Lawless Lawyer
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Driven by the desire to avenge his mother, a former gangster turned lawyer uses both his fists and the loopholes in law to fight against those with absolute power.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Lawless Lawyer
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Driven by the desire to avenge his mother, a former gangster turned lawyer uses both his fists and the loopholes in law to fight against those with absolute power.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Reprisal
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Jacob, a bank manager haunted by a violent heist that took the life of a coworker, teams up with his ex-cop neighbor, James, to bring down the assailant. When Gabriel kidnaps Jacob’s wife and daughter, Jacob barrels down a path of bloodshed that initiates an explosive counterattack and brings all three men to the breaking point.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Something in the Rain

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: With his major league baseball debut right around the corner, a star pitcher lands in prison and must learn to navigate his new world.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Angel
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: True story of Ashraf Marwan, who was President Nasser's son-in-law and special adviser and confidant to his successor Anwar Sadat - while simultaneously Israeli Intelligence's most precious asset of the 20th century. Based on NYT bestselling book 'The Angel: The Egyptian Spy Who Saved Israel' by Uri Bar-Joseph.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Brainchild
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: From germs and emotions to social media and more, it's the science of your world explained in a way that's refreshingly relatable.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Father of the Year
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Two college grads return to their hometown, where a hypothetical question -- whose dad would win in a fight? -- leads to mass mayhem.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The B-Side: Elsa Dorfman's Portrait Photography
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Portrait photographer Elsa Dorfman found her medium in 1980: the larger-than-life Polaroid Land 20x24 camera. For the next thirty-five years, she captured the “surfaces” of those who visited her studio: families, Beat poets, rock stars, and Harvard notables. As pictures begin to fade and her retirement looms, Dorfman gives Errol Morris an inside tour of her backyard archive.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Puss in Book: Trapped in an Epic Tale
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After tumbling into a magic storybook, Puss in Boots must fight, dance and romance his way through wild adventures as he searches for an escape.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Demetri Martin: The Overthinker
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: With his signature one-liners and drawings, Demetri Martin muses on doughnut holes, dogs, sports bars, the alphabet's most aggressive letters and more.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Death and Life of Marsha P. Johnson
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Describing herself as a 'street queen,' Johnson was a legendary fixture in New York City’s gay ghetto and a tireless voice for LGBT pride since the days of Stonewall, who along with fellow trans icon Sylvia Rivera, founded Street Transvestites Action Revolutionaries (S.T.A.R.), a trans activist group based in the heart of NYC’s Greenwich Village. Her death in 1992 was declared a suicide by the NYPD, but friends never accepted that version of events. Structured as a whodunit, with activist Victoria Cruz cast as detective and audience surrogate, The Death and Life of Marsha P. Johnson celebrates the lasting political legacy of Johnson, while seeking to finally solve the mystery of her unexplained death.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Revolutionary Love
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Byun Hyuk is the younger son of a rich conglomerate family who was born with a silver spoon in his mouth. The lack of difficulties in life contributed to the carefree and hopelessly positive mindset of his. One day, he meets a girl who is everything that he is not. This drama is a depiction of youth where they learn about love and friendship.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Marlon
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A loving (but immature) father is committed to co-parenting his two kids with his very-together ex-wife. While his misguided fatherly advice, unstoppable larger-than-life personality and unpredictable Internet superstardom might get in the way sometimes, for Marlon, family really always does come first - even if he's the biggest kid of all.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When Jeff Ross and Dave Attell take the stage, no one is safe. With the help of special guests, they're packing a lot of laughs into one epic weekend.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Comedians Jimmy Carr, D.L. Hughley and Katherine Ryan tackle the world's woes with help from a rotating crew of funny guests and an actual expert.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Historic footage and leading voices of the era examine the "Bobby Phenomenon" of the 1960s and the legacy of the man who helped redefine the country.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Legacy of a Whitetail Deer Hunter

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A psychiatrist tries to put her life back together after a violent attack by seeking to repair the life of a new patient, but he has his own terrifying history.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After receiving a bizarre chance to go back in time, a man wakes up to find that his whole life — including the person he married — is different.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Honoring service members whose courage merited the awarding of a Medal of Honor, this docudrama series re-creates their inspiring true stories.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Llama, his family and his good friends have heart-warming adventures in a safe, friendly town. An animated show based on the award-winning books.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ronnie Coleman: The King
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Ronnie Coleman is known as "The King" and for good reason. He is the 8x Mr. Olympia champion in the world of bodybuilding - sharing the world record for most Olympia wins. Now retired, he has undergone over 6 surgeries leaving him unable to walk without crutches but his desire to train like a pro bodybuilder has not dissipated. Exploring the history of his career as a bodybuilding legend and following his journey to recovery; for the first time ever discover the true man behind The King.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Hasan Minhaj: Homecoming King
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Comic Hasan Minhaj of "The Daily Show" shares personal stories about racism, immigrant parents, prom night horrors and more in this stand-up special.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Insia Malik is a talented 15-year-old school girl from Baroda whose spirit is ripped because her mother is in a troubled and violent marriage. Of course she still dares to pursue her dream of becoming a singer and she also valiantly attempts to free her mother from her conservative, cold father.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In this intense obstacle course series, elite athletes from the U.S. and other countries compete for cash prizes, individual glory and national pride.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a locked down train station, a homicide detective conducts an interview with a tormented monkey  who is suspected of murder.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Jenni Rivera: Mariposa de Barrio
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This drama reveals the difficult rise to fame of the Mexican-American singer Jenni Rivera, from her past of abuse to success as a band leader.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Iliza Shlesinger: Elder Millennial
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Filmed February 23, 2018, aboard the USS Hornet, comedian Iliza Shlesinger brings an ‘elder millennial’ perspective to her audience. Recently engaged, she dives into undeniable truths about life at age 35. Looking back at the insanity of the road traveled and what’s to come, Iliza talks first apartments, a woman's inner she dragon, peacock mating calls, and her newfound urge to squeeze a chubby baby leg.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: During the Japanese colonial era, roughly 400 Korean people, who were forced onto Battleship Island (‘Hashima Island’) to mine for coal, attempt to escape.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: During the Japanese colonial era, roughly 400 Korean people, who were forced onto Battleship Island (‘Hashima Island’) to mine for coal, attempt to escape.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Sanju explores some of the most crucial chapters from movie star Sanjay Dutt’s dramatic and controversial real life. It gives a lowdown on his tryst with drugs and his trials and tribulations in the Arms Acts case and the 1993 Mumbai blasts.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Cheeky comic Craig Ferguson keeps it casual as he discusses '70s porn, Japanese toilets and his mildly crime-filled days as a talk show host.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: NRI corporate Sundar Ramasamy comes to India to vote, only to learn that his vote has already been cast. While he reclaims his right legally, it also sets in motion a chain of events that eventually lead to him entering the political fray, trying to change the system.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Twenty years after the modern world's most notorious child murder, the legacy of the crime and its impact are explored.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: As his life comes to its end, famous Hollywood director Orson Welles puts it all on the line at the chance for renewed success with the film The Other Side of the Wind.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Strong Island
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Examining the violent death of the filmmaker’s brother and the judicial system that allowed his killer to go free, this documentary interrogates murderous fear and racialized perception, and re-imagines the wreckage in catastrophe’s wake, challenging us to change.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Final Table
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Team of chefs vie to impress some of the world's toughest palates as they whip up iconic dishes from different nations in this fast-paced competition.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Time: The Kalief Browder Story
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The story of a teenager wrongfully charged with theft and jailed at Riker's Island prison for over 1,000 days.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Spyder
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A surveillance expert who wants to help people comes across a foe who is the very definition of evil. Can he stop the man before he destroys everything?

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Lust Stories
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An anthology of four stories that sheds light on modern relationships from the viewpoint of the Indian woman.

Featuring our 5 train heroes, with special powers: Kay, Alf, Duck, Selly and Victor - and their exciting adventures. Can the Robot Trains save the village from the evil dark forces that be?

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Most Unknown
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An epic documentary film that sends nine scientists to extraordinary parts of the world to uncover unexpected answers to some of humanity’s biggest questions. How did life begin? What is time? What is consciousness? How much do we really know?  By introducing researchers from diverse backgrounds for the first time, then dropping them into new, immersive field work they previously hadn’t tackled, the film pushes the boundaries of how science storytelling is approached. What emerges is a deeply human trip to the foundations of discovery and a powerful reminder that the unanswered questions are the most crucial ones to pose.  Directed by Emmy-nominated and Peabody Award-winning filmmaker Ian Cheney and advised by world-renowned filmmaker Werner Herzog, The Most Unknown is an ambitious look at a side of science never before shown on screen.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Flint Town
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Over a two-year period, filmmakers embedded with cops in Flint, Michigan, reveal a department grappling with volatile issues in untenable conditions.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Death by Magic
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Magician Drummond Money-Coutts travels the globe, sharing his infectious love of his craft and attempting feats that proved fatal to other magicians.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Benji
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Two school kids strike up a friendship with an orphaned puppy named Benji. When danger befalls them and they end up kidnapped by robbers who are in over their heads, Benji and his scruffy sidekick come to the rescue.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: My Sassy Girl
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Set in the Joseon Dynasty period, a romance takes place between cold-hearted Gyun-Woo and Princess Hyemyung who causes troubles.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: My Sassy Girl
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Set in the Joseon Dynasty period, a romance takes place between cold-hearted Gyun-Woo and Princess Hyemyung who causes troubles.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Lego Jurassic World: The Secret Exhibit
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: How the characters from Lego Jurassic World: The Indominus Escape (2016) and Jurassic World (2015) got involved with the Park.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Beyond Stranger Things
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Secrets from the "Stranger Things 2" universe are revealed as cast and guests discuss the latest episodes with host Jim Rash. Caution: spoilers ahead!

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Alaska Is a Drag
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Tough, but diva fabulous, Leo, an aspiring drag superstar, is stuck working in a fish cannery in Alaska. He and his twin sister are trapped in the monotony of fist fights and fish guts. Out of necessity, Leo learned to fight back, which catches the attention of the local boxing coach. When a new boy moves to town and wants to be his sparring partner, Leo has to face the real reason he's stuck in Alaska.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Parmanu: The Story of Pokhran
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A look at India's second confidential nuclear test series at Pokhran lead by Dr. APJ Abdul Kalam, during the time of PM Atal Bihari Vajpayee's tenure.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Zero
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Short in stature but big on love, a bachelor meets two very different women who broaden his horizons and help him find purpose in life.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Amateur
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: 14-year-old basketball phenom Terron Forte has to navigate the under-the-table world of amateur athletics when he is recruited to an elite NCAA prep school.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Pottersville
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Maynard, a beloved local businessman is mistaken for the legendary Bigfoot during an inebriated romp through town in a makeshift gorilla costume. The sightings set off an international Bigfoot media spectacle and a windfall of tourism dollars for a simple American town hit by hard times. When Brock Masterson, reality TV’s “Monster Hunter,” arrives to hunt the beast, Maynard agonizes over whether to come clean, destroying the rebirth of his beloved town, or perpetuate the inadvertent hoax.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: A Christmas Prince: The Royal Wedding
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A year after Amber helped Richard secure the crown. The two are set to tie the knot in a royal Christmas wedding — but their plans are jeopardized when Amber finds herself second-guessing whether or not she's cut out to be queen, and Richard is faced with a political crisis that threatens to tarnish not only the holiday season but the future of the kingdom.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Bleeding Edge
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Each year in the United States, unparalleled innovations in medical diagnostics, treatment, and technology hit the market. But when the same devices designed to save patients end up harming them, who is accountable?

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Lowriders
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A young street artist in East Los Angeles is caught between his father's obsession with lowrider car culture, his ex-felon brother and his need for self-expression.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Becoming Champions
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This series looks at the stories behind the athletes and countries that have achieved World Cup champion status.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: NY Prison Break: The Seduction of Joyce Mitchell
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Convicted killers David Sweat and Richard Matt seduce bored, restless, small town mom Joyce Mitchell who aids and abets their audacious jailbreak.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: S.W.A.T.: Under Siege
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When a D.E.A. and S.W.A.T. cartel takedown ends in a shootout, S.W.A.T. Agent Travis Hall seizes a mysterious prisoner taking him into custody. Before long, the S.W.A.T. compound is under siege by wave-after-wave of assault teams attempting to recover the prisoner known as “The Scorpion” for the tattoo blazed across his back. When Travis discovers that his prisoner is a Secret Ops double agent planted within the cartel, it’s up to him and his expert S.W.A.T. team to keep “The Scorpion” and his billion dollar secrets safe.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Live
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The police officers at South Korea's busiest patrol division toil day and night as keepers of law and peace -- but the reality is far from orderly.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Live
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The police officers at South Korea's busiest patrol division toil day and night as keepers of law and peace -- but the reality is far from orderly.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Selection Day
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Two teen cricket prodigies struggle against their overbearing father and a system stacked against them to realize their own ambitions and identities.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: 6 Balloons
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Over the course of one night, a woman drives across LA with her heroin addict brother in search of a detox center, with his two-year-old daughter in tow.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Chasing Coral
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Coral reefs are the nursery for all life in the oceans, a remarkable ecosystem that sustains us. Yet with carbon emissions warming the seas, a phenomenon called “coral bleaching”—a sign of mass coral death—has been accelerating around the world, and the public has no idea of the scale or implication of the catastrophe silently raging underwater.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ram Dass, Going Home
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Ram Dass is one of the most important cultural figures from the 1960s and 70s. A pyschedelic pioneer, author of Be Here Now, beloved spiritual teacher, and outspoken advocate for death-and-dying awareness, Ram Dass is now himself approaching the end of life.  Since suffering a life-changing stroke twenty years ago, he has been living at his home on Maui and deepening his spiritual practice — which is centered on love and his idea of merging with his surroundings and all living things.  Shot in a nuanced cinematic style, the film is an intimate summary of his life learning and awareness, and is ultimately a poetic meditation on life, death, and the soul’s journey home.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Edgar Rice Burroughs' Tarzan and Jane
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Saved from a plane crash and given supernatural powers, teen Tarzan joins forces with brave city girl Jane to protect his jungle home from threats.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: First Match
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Hardened by years in foster care, a teenage girl from Brooklyn’s Brownsville neighborhood decides that wrestling boys is the only way back to her estranged father.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Justice
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A U.S. Marshal seeking justice for his brother's murder defends a small town from a corrupt Mayor and his henchmen with intents to revive the civil war.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Charming
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Charming Cursed to be TOO charming, Prince Charming, the most famous prince the world has ever known, has found himself engaged to three iconic princesses (Snow White, Cinderella and Sleeping Beauty)… all at the same time! In order to break his curse and free his kingdom from its ravages, Prince Charming must embark on an epic quest and wind his way through a series of seemingly impossible tasks to learn which of these three (3) princesses is his true love. Determined to make things right, the Prince is accompanied on this madcap journey by a clever and cunning hooligan named Lenore (who becomes his teacher and confidant). Along the way, the Prince realizes that Lenore is both his best friend and his true love and that life’s journey is not defined by whom you run the gauntlet for, but rather whom you run it with.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Falsa identidad
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Isabel and Diego, two complete strangers, must assume the identity of a married couple in order to flee the state of Sonora.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: All I Wish
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A woman struggles to escape the clutches of her overbearing, co-dependent mother, while gradually falling for a sexy, sophisticated attorney.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Strongest Deliveryman
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Two gutsy food delivery workers strive to overcome their socioeconomic disadvantages to achieve big goals -- and bump into love along the way.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Strongest Deliveryman
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Two gutsy food delivery workers strive to overcome their socioeconomic disadvantages to achieve big goals -- and bump into love along the way.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Angamaly Diaries
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Six young friends in the small town of Angamaly tries their luck by starting a pork business lead by Vincent Pepe. They initially strike a business deal with Rajan and Ravi despite the duo having killed a close friend of theirs in a gang fight. Vincent is in love with Sakhi and plan to immigrate abroad with her. But their plans hit a road bump as the deal with the gangsters hits some road bumps.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: ReMastered: Tricky Dick & The Man in Black
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This documentary chronicles Johnny Cash's 1970 visit to the White House, where Cash's emerging liberal ideals clashed with Richard Nixon's policies.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Live Up To Your Name
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description:
Heo Im is an oriental doctor, acknowledged as the best in acupuncture and moxibustion in Joseon. His success is blocked due to his low status.

One day, Heo Im travels though time and finds himself in present day Seoul. He meets Choi Yeon-Kyung. She is doctor firmly believing in only modern medicine.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Fred Armisen: Standup for Drummers
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: For an audience of drummers, comedian Fred Armisen shares and demonstrates his thoughts on musical genres, drummer quirks, regional accents and more.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Fastest Car
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The drivers of exotic supercars put their street cred on the line against deceptively fast sleeper cars built and modified by true gearheads.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bad Guys: Vile City
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Ordered to take down a villainous business leader who controls the city, a prosecutor gathers a team of men who may not be so clean themselves.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Former Secretary of Labor Robert Reich meets with Americans from all walks of life as he chronicles a seismic shift in the nation's economy.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Degenerates
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Six stand-ups explore the coarse and salacious side of comedy in this series of half-hour specials. For mature audiences.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mom
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After her stepdaughter is sexually assaulted at a party, a furious mother sets out to destroy the lives of the four perpetrators who walked free.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Christmas Inheritance
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: To inherit her father's company, socialite Ellen must first visit his small hometown, where she learns the value of hard work and helping others.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: An Imperfect Murder
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Successful actress Vera Lockman thrashes during a nightmare in which she struggles with, shoots and kills her drug-dealer ex-boyfriend. Jolted awake, she reveals in her journal that the killing actually occurred the day before and that Sal, dead, lies in a trunk in her living room.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: LEGO Marvel Super Heroes: Guardians of the Galaxy - The Thanos Threat
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The Guardians are on a mission to deliver the Build Stone to the Avengers before the Ravagers, Thanos and his underlings steal it from them.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Killing Hasselhoff
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A man in a high stakes celebrity death pool quickly loses everything - his business, his bank account, his home, his fiancé. He snaps, then realizes the only way to get his life back on track. He'll have to murder his own celebrity. He'll have to kill Hasselhoff.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Shepherds and Butchers
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A lawyer takes on a case of a prison guard in South Africa who is traumatized by the executions he's witnessed.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Holiday Calendar
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A talented photographer stuck in a dead-end job inherits an antique Advent calendar that may be predicting the future -- and pointing her toward love.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Zac & Mia
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: "Zac and Mia", based on the novel by A.J. Betts, about 2 teens battling cancer in the same hospital. In the real world, Zac and Mia would have pretty much nothing in common, but in the hospital, where they're the only 2 teens on the ward, they develop an unbreakable bond. If cancer is the variable that changed everything, the only constant is their ever-deepening need for one another.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Deidra & Laney Rob a Train
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After their mother ends up in jail, two sisters turn to train robbery in order to support their family.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Take Your Pills
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a hypercompetitive world, drugs like Adderall offer students, athletes, coders and others a way to do more -- faster and better. But at what cost?

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Abby Hatcher
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Abby Hatcher is part girl, part superhero; living in a world full of fuzzlies. When a fuzzly friend needs help, Abby takes action – going on a mission to make things right.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: My Only Love Song
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Song Soo-Jung is an arrogant pop star who believes not only that status and money can get you anywhere, but that it defines your worth. She accidentally falls into a time-slip portal and travels back in time to the Joseon era where she meets On-Dal, a man who loves money yet is generous to those without.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Naked
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Following a wild night out with his Best Man, Rob Anderson wakes up to find himself naked in an elevator on the morning of his wedding day and is forced to relive the morning over and over again.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Witness the stories of history's most notorious kingpins, their terrifying enforcers, and the men and women who've sworn to bring them down.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The gleefully irreverent Jefferies skewers “grabby” celebrities, political hypocrisy and his own ill-advised career moves in a brash stand-up special.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Cities of Last Things
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This is a story about a common man who has extraordinary events in his mundane life. The film depicts the protagonist's turns of events in three eras, three seasons, three nights, in the same city, as told with reverse chronology.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Busted!
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Suspense, surprises and fun abound in this Korean variety game show featuring big personalities and even bigger mysteries in every episode.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Suspense, surprises and fun abound in this Korean variety game show featuring big personalities and even bigger mysteries in every episode.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: LA homicide detective Gene Handsome's knack for solving mysteries is matched only by his inability to make sense of his own problems.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dinotrux: Supercharged
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Amped up with powers that make them faster, stronger and more agile than ever, the Dinotrux are back to face new challenges and meet new friends.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Inside the Criminal Mind
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Explore the psychological machinations and immoral behavior that define the most nefarious types of criminals.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Roxanne, Roxanne
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The most feared battle emcee in early-'80s NYC was a fierce teenager from the Queensbridge projects with the weight of the world on her shoulders. At age 14, hustling the streets to provide for her family, Roxanne Shanté was well on her way to becoming a hip-hop legend.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Lucid Dream
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Dae-ho, an investigative journalist, seeks to track down the whereabouts of his son who was abducted three years ago. With the help of a detective and a psychiatrist friend, he will retrace his memory of the incident through the use of lucid dreaming techniques.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The isolated life of an extreme introvert is thrown out of order when his company hires a new employee: a cheery extrovert who's not all she seems.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: No-nonsense comic Bill Burr takes the stage in Nashville and riffs on fast food, overpopulation, dictators and gorilla sign language.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Snatching trophies. Getting gorgeous. Turning it up. Alyssa Edwards rules the dance studio by day -- and the drag world by night.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A family man with no drug running experience searches the Caribbean for a lost stash of cocaine said to be worth at least $2 million.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Amid a coup, a North Korean agent escapes south with the country's injured leader in an attempt to keep him alive and prevent a Korean war.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: A Miraculous Christmas Special: Tales of Ladybug and Cat Noir
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: It's Christmas in Paris, a time for generosity, giving and spending time with family. At least not for everyone, Adrien has to celebrate his first Christmas without his mom, and he thinks that his father is not interested in celebrating the holiday with him this year, which inspires him the idea to run away from home as Cat Noir to sing out his anger in the cold and snow. When the news of his disappearance spreads all over Paris, Adrien's friends go out searching for him while Marinette transforms as Ladybug to search the cold and snow for the boy she secretly loves. But things get worse when she accidentally causes a man dressed as Santa to get akumatized on Christmas Eve, now Ladybug and Cat Noir have to stop him before he destroys the holiday for everyone.
