But things get worse when she accidentally causes a man dressed as Santa to get akumatized on Christmas Eve, now Ladybug and Cat Noir have to stop him before he destroys the holiday for everyone.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Catfight
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The rivalry between two former college friends comes to a head when they both attend the same glamorous event.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Toilet: A Love Story
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A woman threatens to leave her husband unless he installs a toilet in their home. To win back her love and respect, he heads out on a journey to fight against the backward society.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: 72 Dangerous Animals: Asia
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: From fangs to claws to venomous stings, they all wield deadly weapons. But which creature will be crowned the fiercest of all?

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: My Dead Ex
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A classic, will-they-won't they romance story. Charley is living your typical teenage girl’s life. Ben, Charley’s not so secret admirer, isn’t living at all. But a little thing like death can’t stop these two teens from falling in love. Or maybe it can.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Misty
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When a popular anchorwoman for a prime time news show becomes the suspect in a murder case, her estranged husband - who has worked as a prosecutor in the past but now works as a public defender - decides to defend his wife.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Misty
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When a popular anchorwoman for a prime time news show becomes the suspect in a murder case, her estranged husband - who has worked as a prosecutor in the past but now works as a public defender - decides to defend his wife.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Terrorism Close Calls
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The war on terror is everywhere and anywhere. In this series, we learn about the deadly terrorist attacks that almost happened or were not as deadly as planned. Each episodes explores a recently declassified terrorist scheme intended to cause mass casualties.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Edge of Fear
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After being stabbed in the heart by ruthless home invaders, a man is left for dead. Now weak, outnumbered, and knife sticking from his chest, he attempts to do the impossible: save his wife from these murderers before he bleeds to death.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: My ID is Gangnam Beauty
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This romantic comedy chronicles the life of Mirae, who has always believed that her life would be better if she were born more beautiful. After she goes under the knife, she comes out looking like the beautiful woman she has always dreamed of becoming. She feels ready to take on the world for the first time, and she falls madly in love with Seok, the perfect man. Except Seok hates people who get plastic surgery.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: My ID is Gangnam Beauty
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This romantic comedy chronicles the life of Mirae, who has always believed that her life would be better if she were born more beautiful. After she goes under the knife, she comes out looking like the beautiful woman she has always dreamed of becoming. She feels ready to take on the world for the first time, and she falls madly in love with Seok, the perfect man. Except Seok hates people who get plastic surgery.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ryan Hamilton: Happy Face
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Small-town import Ryan Hamilton charms New York with folksy comic observations on big-city life, hot-air ballooning and going to Disney World alone.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: End Game
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Filmed and edited in intimate vérité style, this movie follows visionary medical practitioners who are working on the cutting edge of life and death and are dedicated to changing our thinking about both.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mike Birbiglia: Thank God for Jokes
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Mike Birbiglia declares that a joke should never end with "I’m joking." In his all-new comedy, Birbiglia tiptoes hilariously through the minefield that is modern-day joke-telling. Join Mike as he learns that the same jokes that elicit laughter have the power to produce tears, rage, and a whole lot of getting yelled at. Ultimately it's a show that asks, “How far should we go for the laugh?”

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Pad Man
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Upon realizing the extent to which women are affected by their menses, a man sets out to create a sanitary pad machine and to provide inexpensive sanitary pads to the women of rural India.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sun Dogs
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A man eager to serve his country but rejected by the Marines pairs up with a young runaway to form an unlikely team on a misguided adventure.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Manto
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In Bombay's seedy-shiny film world, Manto and his stories are widely read and accepted. But as sectarian violence engulfs the nation, Manto makes the difficult choice of leaving his beloved Bombay. In Lahore, he finds himself bereft of friends and unable to find takers for his writings.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Little Boxes
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: It's the summer before 6th grade, and Clark is the new-in-town biracial kid in a sea of white. Discovering that to be cool he needs to act 'more black,' he fumbles to meet expectations, while his urban intellectual parents Mack and Gina also strive to adjust to small-town living. Equipped for the many inherent challenges of New York, the tight-knit family are ill prepared for the drastically different set of obstacles that their new community presents, and soon find themselves struggling to understand themselves and each other in this new suburban context.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Move
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The series is called MOVE and each episode brings us inside the life of a Canadian living with mental illness who has found a positive way to "self-medicate" through the discovery of exercise and human movement.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Hymn of Death
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Based on a true story, the drama tells the tragic love story of Kim Woo Jin, a married stage drama writer, and Yun Shim Duk, Korea's first professional soprano, who meet while studying at Tokyo University in the 1920s. Yun Shim Duk's recording of "Death Song" became the first Korean pop song in 1926.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Hymn of Death
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Based on a true story, the drama tells the tragic love story of Kim Woo Jin, a married stage drama writer, and Yun Shim Duk, Korea's first professional soprano, who meet while studying at Tokyo University in the 1920s. Yun Shim Duk's recording of "Death Song" became the first Korean pop song in 1926.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Baazaar
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After moving to Mumbai, an ambitious young man becomes the stock trader for a notorious businessman.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ittefaq
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Police officer Dev investigates a double murder case that has only two witnesses - an acclaimed writer Vikram and a young homemaker Maya, who also happen to be the prime suspects in the case. He finds himself being torn between their own version's of what happened on the fateful night, and takes it upon himself to figure out the real story and capture the real murderer.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Chris Rock: Tamborine
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Chris Rock takes the stage for his first comedy special in 10 years, filled with searing observations on fatherhood, infidelity and American politics.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: 72 Dangerous Animals: Latin America
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Powerful cats, indestructible arachnids and flesh-melting pit vipers are just the beginning in this series about Latin America's deadliest creatures.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Take Me
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Ray is a fledgling entrepreneur who specializes in high-end simulated abductions. He jumps at the chance when a mysterious client contracts him for a weekend kidnapping with a handsome payday at the end. But the job isn't all that it seems.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ee Nagaraniki Emaindi
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Four friends, with a bittersweet history, get drunk and embark on a journey to Goa. On the trip, they lose an expensive ring which threatens to derail one of their engagement. They end up confronting one another and their own fears, as they enroll in a short film making competition in Goa to try and win the prize money for the ring.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Patton Oswalt: Annihilation
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Patton Oswalt, despite a personal tragedy, produces his best standup yet. Focusing on the tribulations of the Trump era and life after the loss of a loved one, Oswalt continues his journey to contribute joy to the world.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: LEGO Marvel Super Heroes: Black Panther - Trouble in Wakanda
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After speaking at the Wakanda Embassy, Black Panther fights Thanos and fends him off with the help of fellow Avengers Captain America, Thor, Iron Man, Hulk, and Black Widow. After regaining conscious, Thanos is approached by Erik Killmonger and Ulysses Klaue in a plot where they will obtain the Vibranium in Wakanda to empower Thanos. When Black Panther discovers this plot, he must work with Shuri, Okoye, and the Avengers to defeat them.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Rory Scovel Tries Stand-Up for the First Time
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Comedian Rory Scovel storms the stage in Atlanta, where he shares unfocused thoughts about things that mystify him, relationships and the "Thong Song."

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Revenger
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Hell-bent on avenging the murder of his family, a former detective infiltrates a remote island that serves as a prison for vicious death row criminals.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Revenger
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Hell-bent on avenging the murder of his family, a former detective infiltrates a remote island that serves as a prison for vicious death row criminals.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Coin Heist
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When a crisis threatens to destroy their high school, four teens hatch a daring plan to raise $10 million. Step one? Breaking into the U.S. Mint.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: LEGO Friends: Girls on a Mission
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Meet Andrea, Mia, Emma, Olivia and Stephanie. They're five best friends. And they're on a heroic mission: to save Heartlake City from wily swindlers.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Jagga Jasoos
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A gifted teenage detective searches for his missing father with his ladylove assistant.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Joel McHale Show with Joel McHale
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Trending news, pop culture, social media, original videos and more come together in host Joel McHale's weekly comedy commentary show.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Drug King
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Busan, South Korea, 1970s. Lee Doo-sam is a small-time smuggler. After helping a drug gang to smuggle meth, he falls into the dark crime world. Quick-witted and full of ambition, he eventually takes over the drug underworld and starts to lead a double life: a good community leader during the day but an infamous drug lord during the night.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Drug King
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Busan, South Korea, 1970s. Lee Doo-sam is a small-time smuggler. After helping a drug gang to smuggle meth, he falls into the dark crime world. Quick-witted and full of ambition, he eventually takes over the drug underworld and starts to lead a double life: a good community leader during the day but an infamous drug lord during the night.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Jab Harry Met Sejal
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Haunted by the memories of home he once knew, a middle-aged tour guide unconsciously embarks on a journey to find self.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Katt Williams: Great America
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The king of underground comedy takes the stage in Jacksonville with unflinching riffs on American politics and the raunchy perils of getting old.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Derren Brown: Sacrifice
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Illusionist Derren Brown concocts a psychological experiment in which he tries to manipulate an ordinary person into taking a bullet for a stranger.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Struggle: The Life and Lost Art of Szukalski
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The remarkable life story of the pre-war Polish artist Stanislav Szukalski, documented by the American friends he made late in life.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sky Ladder: The Art of Cai Guo-Qiang
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Known for his spectacular pyrotechnic displays, Chinese artist Cai Guo-Qiang creates his most ambitious project yet: Sky Ladder, a visionary, explosive event that he pulls off in his hometown in China after 20 years of failed attempts.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Fortress
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Ancient Korea, 17th century. The powerful Khan of the Jurchen tribe of Manchuria, who fights the Ming dinasty to gain China, becomes the first ruler of the Qing dinasty and demands from King In-jo of Joseon to bow before him; but he refuses, being loyal to the Mings. On December 14th, 1636, the Qing horde invades Joseon, so King In-jo and his court shelter in the mountain fortress of Namhan and prepare to defend the kingdom.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Fortress
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Ancient Korea, 17th century. The powerful Khan of the Jurchen tribe of Manchuria, who fights the Ming dinasty to gain China, becomes the first ruler of the Qing dinasty and demands from King In-jo of Joseon to bow before him; but he refuses, being loyal to the Mings. On December 14th, 1636, the Qing horde invades Joseon, so King In-jo and his court shelter in the mountain fortress of Namhan and prepare to defend the kingdom.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Qarib Qarib Singlle
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Yogi and Jaya, who have polar opposite personalities and sensibilities, meet via an online dating app. This encounter turns into so much more when the two travel to Rishikesh.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: My Secret Romance
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After sharing a night with Jin Wook, Yoo Mi departs, never to see him again. Three years later, she achieves her goal of becoming a nutritionist.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: My Secret Romance
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After sharing a night with Jin Wook, Yoo Mi departs, never to see him again. Three years later, she achieves her goal of becoming a nutritionist.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Feminists: What Were They Thinking?
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In 1977, a book of photographs captured an awakening - women shedding the cultural restrictions of their childhoods and embracing their full humanity. This documentary revisits those photos, those women and those times and takes aim at our culture today that alarmingly shows the need for continued change.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: A Christmas Prince
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When a reporter goes undercover as a nanny to get the inside scoop on a playboy prince, she gets tangled in some royal intrigue and ends up finding love - but will she be able to keep up her lie?

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: All About the Washingtons
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The wife of a legendary rapper launches her own career, which puts his life into a tailspin.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: All Hail King Julien: Exiled
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Julien's been dethroned, but loyal friends and some very unlikely allies will propel the lovable lemur on a colorful journey to take back his kingdom.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Aiyaary
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An Indian Army officer is compelled to chase down his protege when the latter turns rogue and threatens to disrupt the country’s government and army.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: SPF-18
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: 18-year-old Penny Cooper spent years pining for Johnny Sanders Jr., but when a mysterious musician shows up on the beach, Penny is torn.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Kulipari: Dream Walker
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Now the Blue Sky King, Darel must lead a rescue mission to save a Dream Walker -- leaving the village under the protection of the Kulipari youth.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Hari Kondabolu: Warn Your Relatives
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Hari Kondabolu breaks down identity politics, celebrity encounters, his mango obsession and more in an unpredictable stand-up comedy special.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Seeing Allred
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Gloria Allred overcame trauma and personal setbacks to become one of the nation’s most famous women’s rights attorneys. Now the feminist firebrand takes on two of the biggest adversaries of her career, Bill Cosby and Donald Trump, as sexual violence allegations grip the nation and keep her in the spotlight.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Resurface
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A suicidal war veteran finds like-minded souls in a surf therapy program that helps traumatized soldiers heal while riding the waves.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Heroin(e)
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This documentary follows three women -- a fire chief, a judge and a street missionary -- as they battle West Virginia's devastating opioid epidemic.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sudani from Nigeria
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When a soccer club manager brings one of his injured foreign players home to recuperate, they form an unlikely bond despite their cultural differences.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Candy Jar
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Dueling high school debate champs who are at odds on just about everything forge ahead with ambitious plans to get into the colleges of their dreams.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Neal Brennan: 3 Mics
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Wicked one-liners and soul-baring confessions converge in this uniquely intimate stand-up special from "Chappelle's Show" co-creator Neal Brennan.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: FIGHTWORLD
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Actor and fight enthusiast Frank Grillo travels the world, immersing himself in different fight cultures to understand their traditions and motivations.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mersal
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A few individuals in the medical profession are murdered or kidnapped, and the cop investigating the case suspects a doctor and arrests him. But is he the one who is behind these crimes? And why are they being committed?

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Jerry Before Seinfeld
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Jerry Seinfeld returns to the club that gave him his start in the 1970s, mixing iconic jokes with stories from his childhood and early days in comedy.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Last Shaman
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: James, giving himself 12 months before he has "a license to kill himself," sets off to the Amazon rainforest with hopes of finding a shaman who can save his life.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bareilly Ki Barfi
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Bitti Mishra is a bohemian Bareilly girl who falls deeply in love with Pritam Vidrohi, an author because she admires his progressive way of thinking. Finding him though proves to be as hard as looking for a needle in the haystack. So Bitti seeks the help of the local printing press-owner, Chirag Dubey on her journey of love.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Baadshaho
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Emergency has been declared in India. Maharani Gitanjali from one of Rajasthan's princely states has already lost her privy purse. Now, she fears that she will lose the last treasure chest of gold which has been forcibly taken away from her. So she asks her trusted lieutenant, Bhawani to step in and plan a heist.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Rapture
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Groundbreaking artists share their life stories in this vibrant documentary series that captures hip-hop's impact on global culture.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: C/o Kancharapalem
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: From a schoolboy’s crush to a middle-aged bachelor’s office romance, four love stories spanning age, religion and status unfold in a small Indian town.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Battlefish
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Over the course of a fishing season, tough men and women pursue lucrative albacore tuna in the competitive waters off the Oregon coast.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Rachel Divide
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Rachel Dolezal became infamous when she was unmasked as a white woman passing for black so thoroughly that she had become the head of her local N.A.A.C.P. chapter. This portrait cuts through the very public controversy to reveal Dolezal’s motivations.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Trevor Noah: Afraid of the Dark
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Trevor Noah stars in his first Netflix special.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Larva Island
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Stranded on a tropical island, two silly larva buddies find slapstick fun in everything from discovering food to meeting new animal friends.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Larva Island
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Stranded on a tropical island, two silly larva buddies find slapstick fun in everything from discovering food to meeting new animal friends.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Larva Island
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Stranded on a tropical island, two silly larva buddies find slapstick fun in everything from discovering food to meeting new animal friends.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Spivak
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A self-loathing, failed Eastside novelist living in the ‘hipster’ neighborhood of Echo Park in Los Angeles is shocked to find himself falling in love with everything he hates, including a simple All-American blonde girl from the Westside.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Christmas in the Heartland
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Kara and Jessie are two teenage girls from very different worlds, but with a little Christmas magic, they find they have much more in common than they ever imagined.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sir
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A young widow is hired as the domestic helper for a wealthy architect, but social divides come to the fore as an unlikely attraction grows between them.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Break with Michelle Wolf
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Nobody's safe as Michelle Wolf unapologetically takes aim in this weekly topical show that blends sketches with live comedy and in-studio guests.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Jim Gaffigan: Cinco
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: America's king of clean comedy delivers wickedly funny jokes in his fifth hour-long special.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Half Girlfriend
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A boy meets a girl named Riya and falls in love. After struggling to convince her to be his girlfriend, she half-heartedly agrees to be his `half-girlfriend'.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Daughters of Destiny
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Five girls from India's most impoverished families attend a boarding school designed to create opportunities as they strive for a brighter future.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The American Meme
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Paris Hilton, the Fat Jew, and Brittany Furlan have all used social media to achieve massive internet fame. But, American Meme explores, is it worth it?

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Amazing Interiors
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Meet eccentric homeowners whose seemingly ordinary spaces are full of surprises, from a backyard roller coaster to an indoor aquarium.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Titipo Titipo

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Titipo the train is out to prove that he's got what it takes to help the folks of Train Village ride the rails safely and reliably.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Stretch Armstrong & the Flex Fighters
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When overscheduled teenager Jake Armstrong and his two best friends are accidentally exposed to an experimental chemical, they become Stretch Armstrong and the Flex Fighters, a team of unlikely superheroes who expand beyond the confines of their lives and embark on a series of adventures.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Weed the People
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The uplifting and heart-wrenching struggles of families who treat their cancer-stricken children with marijuana, some with astonishing results.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Love per Square Foot
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Individually, bank employees Sanjay and Karina don't earn enough to be able to buy a home, so they decide to enter into a marriage of convenience.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Harvey Street Kids
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Kids rule in a place called Harvey Street, where a trio of girls right wrongs, ice cream is always an option, and every day feels like Saturday.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Stay Here
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Designer Genevieve Gorder and real estate expert Peter Lorimer show property owners how to turn their short-term rentals into moneymaking showstoppers.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mubarakan
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Singleton Kartar Singh is left with the responsibility of raising his two orphaned nephews. He asks his brother in Punjab to raise Charan and his sister in London to raise Karan. When the twins cross continents, they leave behind a trail of confusion.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Argon
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a world filled with provocative (and often misleading) news, a passionate team of investigative TV reporters strives to bring truths to light.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Argon
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a world filled with provocative (and often misleading) news, a passionate team of investigative TV reporters strives to bring truths to light.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Qismat
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Shiva is just looking to sow some wild oats before settling down, until he falls in love with his beautiful neighbor.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Fire Chasers
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: As California's 2016 fire season rages, brave backcountry firefighters race to put out the flames, protect homes and save lives in this docuseries.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ali Wong: Hard Knock Wife
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Pregnant again, Ali Wong returns to Netflix in her second original stand-up comedy special and gets real on why having kids is not all it's cracked up to be.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Tom Segura: Disgraceful
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Tom Segura gives voice to the sordid thoughts you'd never say out loud, with blunt musings on porn, parking lot power struggles, parenthood and more.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Limitless
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This documentary follows eight women in India who struggle with self-confidence and society's expectations but rediscover themselves through running

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Soorma
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Soorma, a comeback story of the hockey legend Sandeep Singh is a biopic that chronicles the life and times of the famed hockey player.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Mars Generation
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Aspiring teenage astronauts reveal that a journey to Mars is closer than you think.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Family Blood
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Ellie, a recovering drug addict, has just moved to a new city with her two teenage children. She has struggled to stay sober in the past and is determined to make it work this time, finding a stable job and regularly attending her meetings. Unfortunately, new friends, a new job, and the chance of a new life, can’t keep Ellie from slipping once again. Her life changes when she meets Christopher – a different kind of addict – which forces her daughter and son to accept a new version of Ellie.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Pihu
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The social thriller starring a two year-old baby girl. She is living in a home where the adults are going through a complicated phase. Being a toddler, she is occasionally trapped in the accidental situations.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Judd Apatow: The Return
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Renowned producer, director and writer Judd Apatow makes his long-awaited return to stand-up comedy with this new special shot in Montreal.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sarah Silverman: A Speck of Dust
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In her first comedy special post-health scare, Sarah Silverman shares a mix of fun facts, sad truths and yeah-she-just-went-there moments.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Pa Paandi
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: ‘Power’ Paandi, once a legendary stunt master who ruled the world of film stunts in his prime years is now content in living a peaceful life with his son and grandchildren. But he soon realizes that his acts that he thinks is normal and righteous, constantly irks his son who seems to taking their relationship for granted. One such overblown tiff with his son drives him to go do some soul searching, the outcome of which has many unexpected experiences.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Nobody Speak: Trials of the Free Press
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The courtroom and publicity battles between the superstar wrestler and the notorious website explode in a sensational trial all about the limits of the First Amendment and the new no holds barred nature of celebrity life in an internet dominated society.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Aapla Manus
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Sr Inspector Maruti Nagargoje is investigating a murder case which took place in the house of a couple.Who claim that they weren't in the house when the incident happened.Maruti has a different way of working as he doesn't consider statement given to police on crime scene as valuable and conducts his own interrogation with suspects.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Love Beats Rhymes
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A young woman dreams of making it big in the world of hip hop, but her parents demand that she finish her university degree. She dutifully agrees to complete her education, but her spoken word proves to have a powerful impact in the classroom.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Naam Shabana
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Shabana Khan is the special agent who is entrusted the task of assassinating a deadly arms dealer by the Indian Intelligence Agencies.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Brian Regan: Nunchucks and Flamethrowers
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Brian Regan takes relatable family humor to new heights as he talks board games, underwear elastic and looking for hot dogs in all the wrong places.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: #realityhigh
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When nerdy high schooler Dani finally attracts the interest of her longtime crush, she lands in the cross hairs of his ex, a social media celebrity.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: We Speak Dance
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Trained dancer Vandana Hart travels the world to learn traditional and urban dance styles from the local experts who know them best.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: DeRay Davis: How to Act Black
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Dynamic comic DeRay Davis hits the stage like a ball of fire, nailing the finer points of living, dating and handling show business as a black man.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Def Comedy Jam 25
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In this special live event, giants of stand-up come together to commemorate the 25th anniversary of Russell Simmons's groundbreaking "Def Comedy Jam."

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: LEGO Elves: Secrets of Elvendale
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Armed with a powerful amulet, a teenage guardian is tasked with protecting her little sister -- and all of Elvendale. Based on the popular web series.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Motown Magic
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Imaginative boy Ben transforms his city by bringing colorful street art to life, armed with a magic paintbrush -- and the classic sounds of Motown.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dave Chappelle: Equanimity & The Bird Revelation
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Comedy titan Dave Chappelle caps a wild year with two stand-up specials packed with scorching new material, self-reflection and tough love.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Amy Schumer: The Leather Special
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Comic sensation Amy Schumer riffs on sex, dating and the absurdities of fame in a bold and uncensored stand-up set at Denver's Bellco Theater.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: A Very Country Christmas
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Jeanette Williams is a busy single parent, trying to make the best life for her and her daughter. With no time to follow current celebrity gossip, Jeanette is unaware of when a Country superstar returns to their small town to escape the intrusive paparazzi and the chaos of fame. A chance meeting between the two have them both letting their guards down and opening their hearts to the possibility of romance.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Paprika
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Stan and Olivia - the amazingly different Paprika twins - use their boundless enthusiasm to turn everyday life into an extraordinary adventure.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Pup Star: Better 2Gether
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Pup Star is back for an all-new adventure! After winning the canine competition show Pup Star and becoming an international pup sensation, Tiny, the adorable Yorkie, has her world turned upside down when an evil rival switches her out in competition with a street pup named Scrappy. The two pups find themselves living the others' very different life and an incredible journey through iconic cities ensues in this fun and hilarious dog-out-of-water adventure! As they prepare for the Pup Star competition to reach its finale, each experiences life through a very different collar and discover the importance of family and being true to yourself. At the finale, both Yorkies claim to be Tiny leaving everyone, including the judges, wondering – who is the real Pup Star? A huge, fun musical adventure, ‘Pup Star: Better 2gether’ is filled with incredible singing pups, fantastic new paw-tapping songs, and an action packed heart-warming story that will have audiences of all ages howling for more!

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Barbra: The Music ... The Mem'ries ... The Magic!
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Iconic songstress Barbra Streisand culminates her 13-city tour in Miami with dazzling ballads, Broadway standards and stories from behind the scenes.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Maz Jobrani: Immigrant
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Iranian American comic Maz Jobrani lights up the Kennedy Center with riffs on immigrant life in the Trump era, modern parenting pitfalls and more.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Nailed It! Holiday!
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: It's the "Nailed It!" holiday special you've been waiting for, with missing ingredients, impossible asks and desserts that look delightfully sad.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Part-Time Idol
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This drama takes place in fictional entertainment company where a producer who has produced many famous idols suddenly has an existential crisis and disappears. Years later he appears and starts to put together a co-ed idol group, which is when the story begins.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Part-Time Idol

Years later he appears and starts to put together a co-ed idol group, which is when the story begins.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ascharya Fuck It
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Desire and greed intertwines the lives of a Bollywood star, his chauffeur, a prostitute and her pimp in an unlikely love story.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Nappily Ever After
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After an accident at the hair salon, Violet realizes she's not living life to the fullest. A soulful barber helps her put the pieces back together.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Judwaa 2
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Separated at birth and peculiarly connected via their reflexes, twins Prem and Raja are reunited with each other as they set out to take down the underground smuggling world.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Christina P: Mother Inferior
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Christina Pazsitzky hits Seattle with a biting dose of reality, telling truths about her childhood, getting older and the horrors of giving birth.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ari Shaffir: Double Negative
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Wry yet thoughtful, comedian Ari Shaffir brings his edgy humor to two fast-paced stand-up specials about children and adulthood.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Milada
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The story of communist show-trial victim Milada Horáková. Horáková was one of the first victims of the communist regime in Czechoslovakia. She opposed the communist coup in 1948 but did not leave the country. She was arrested and tried for treason on fabricated charges in a show trial that was broadcast on the radio and shown in film clips. The film focuses on the time from 1945 to 1950 when the communists took over, but also goes back a little further in Horáková's life into the late 1930s

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: First and Last
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Take an intimate look at the emotionally charged first and last days of new and soon-to-be released inmates at Georgia's Gwinnett County Jail.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Buddy Thunderstruck
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Follow the outrageous, high-octane adventures of Buddy Thunderstruck, a truck-racing dog who brings guts and good times to the town of Greasepit.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Monkart
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Jin and his dragon monster Draka set out on a racing adventure and try to save the kingdom from evil forces.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Monkart
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Jin and his dragon monster Draka set out on a racing adventure and try to save the kingdom from evil forces.
