data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After his girlfriend dumps him at a New Year's Eve party, Bill and his friends drive to an off-season beach town to win her back.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Cycle
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Keshav, an astrologer, deeply values his cycle as it is his most prized possession. However, problems arise when a couple of thieves steal his bicycle.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Westside
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Nine struggling musicians share the spotlight in this deeply personal reality series about the challenges and thrills of staging a Hollywood showcase.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Paradox
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A loud poem. A whimsical western tale of music and love.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Chase
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After people in his town start turning up dead, a grumpy landlord is visited by a man who recounts an unsolved serial murder case from 30 years ago that may hold the clue to what is happening now.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Chase
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After people in his town start turning up dead, a grumpy landlord is visited by a man who recounts an unsolved serial murder case from 30 years ago that may hold the clue to what is happening now.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Tiffany Haddish: She Ready! From the Hood to Hollywood!
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In her first stand-up special filmed at the Nate Holden Performing Arts Center, Los Angeles native and rising star Tiffany Haddish tackles subjects ranging from her early days in foster care and being bullied on the playground to getting revenge on ex-boyfriends and introducing Will and Jada Pinkett Smith to Groupon.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Party Monster: Scratching the Surface
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In the probing documentary "Party Monster," DJ Fingablast investigates what became of his childhood hero, DJ Slizzard.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ani... Dr. Kashinath Ghanekar
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The true story of the first Marathi superstar Kashinath Ghanekar, chronicling his struggles and hardships in marriage and life to pursue his passion for acting and attain the unmatched heights of stardom in Marathi theatre and cinema.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Stree
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Set in the town of Chanderi, Stree is based on the urban legend of Nale Ba that went viral in Karnataka in the 1990s, and features Shraddha Kapoor and Rajkummar Rao in pivotal roles.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: A Champion Heart
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A troubled girl finds faith, hope, and healing through a relationship with a wounded horse.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Burning Sands
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Deep into Hell Week, a favored pledgee is torn between honoring his code of silence or standing up against the intensifying violence of underground hazing.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Judah Friedlander: America Is the Greatest Country in the United States
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Deadpan comic and self-proclaimed world champion Judah Friedlander performs over several nights in New York, explaining why America is No. 1.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Take the 10
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A day in the life of two best friends, a drug dealer, and a store manager collide at a hip-hop concert in the Inland Empire.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Bros
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Reunited in their hometown for their father's funeral, two self-interested brothers meet a peculiar woman who shares a huge secret about their family.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Bros
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Reunited in their hometown for their father's funeral, two self-interested brothers meet a peculiar woman who shares a huge secret about their family.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Jim Norton: Mouthful of Shame
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Fedoras, mom's underpants, and puppy love all make Jim Norton's s**t list in 'Mouthful of Shame'.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Merku Thodarchi Malai
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Living on the borders of Kerala and Tamil Nadu, Rangasamy, a laborer just like his fellow sons of soils toils, hard-working at the spice plantations owned by landlords. He lives a happy life and wishes to own a piece of land and earn a living through farming. After years of struggle, his dream finally comes true when Chaako, a local politician helps him buy the land, however, he soon faces tougher challenges as he has to deal with corrupt and wealthy politicians.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ponysitters Club
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A young horse enthusiast teams up with her best friends to rescue and rehabilitate animals on her family's beloved ranch.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Being Napoleon
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: As over 6,000 immaculately dressed military re-enactors, men and women, gather for the 200th anniversary of the epic Battle of Waterloo, some of them representing real individuals from the time, whether ‘humble foot-soldiers’, ‘officers’ or the great ‘Marshal Ney.’ who is unfortunately less adapt at horsemanship than the original, the real battle is taking place elsewhere: American Mark Schneider, considered the best Napoleon in the business, vs. Frenchman Frank Samson, uniform-maker extraordinaire, as to who will be Emperor on the day. There was only one Napoleon, there can be only one Napoleon, but the Belgians are in charge, unrest is growing in the ranks, there is an outstanding prison sentence to be served, an unpaid bill for parking to which the ‘Empress Josephine’ also has something to say, and as to who meets their Waterloo first, you’ll just have to watch.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dhh
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Convinced only a miracle can save them from failing school exams, a trio of friends seek help from a magician. To their surprise, he gamely complies.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mauli
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Mauli is a tough cop whose in control when in uniform.But a big terror to criminals without uniform he gets transferred to Kapur village which has no respect for cops and it's temple is closed since last 15 years due to terror of Nana Londhe.Mauli beats his men black and blue where he finds admire in Renuka.Its soon reveled that Mauli is a simple man but the actual terror cop is his twin brother with the same name.Mauli's brother dies while trying to save Mauli from Nana leaving Mauli helpless in the village and face humiliation in front of Nana's terror.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: CIA: Comrade In America
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A young Aji Mathew is a communist who goes the whole nine yards for the ideologies he believes in. When the girl he loves leaves to the US out of the blue and her parents fix her wedding, Aji is left with just a fortnight to reach the country albeit with no passport or visa. How far he is willing to go for love forms the plot.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Sound of Your Heart: Reboot
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Based on the longest-running web-based comic series "Ma Eum Ui Sori" in Korea, "Sound of your heart" is a story about Cho Seok, an aspiring comic writer, and his strange family.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Sound of Your Heart: Reboot
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Based on the longest-running web-based comic series "Ma Eum Ui Sori" in Korea, "Sound of your heart" is a story about Cho Seok, an aspiring comic writer, and his strange family.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bert Kreischer: Secret Time
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Comedian Bert Kreischer is ready to take his shirt off and "party hardy" with his debut Netflix Original stand-up special, Bert Kreischer: Secret Time. Considered one of the best storytellers of his generation, Bert regales the audience at the Trocadero Theatre in Philadelphia with stories about zip-lining with his family, his daughter practicing softball with an imaginary ball, and upstaging ex-NBA player Ralph Sampson at a childhood basketball camp.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Counterpunch
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: As boxing's popularity wanes, three fighters at different stages of their career make sacrifices to pursue their dreams of becoming champions.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Rajma Chawal
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A father attempts to reconnect with his estranged son through social media, a new world for him.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Marlon Wayans: Woke-ish
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An American stand-up comedy special starring Marlon Wayans who jokes about racism, hip-hop, gay rights, and raising kids.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Monster Island
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Young Lucas finds out he's not really a human after he surprisingly transforms into a monster in front of the most popular kids at school. His search for Monster Island and his real roots takes him on a fabulously scary journey that puts him face to face with more tentacles, fangs and far-out situations than he can shake one of his new wings at.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Best.Worst.Weekend.Ever.
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Teenage friends plan an epic trip to Comic-Con to meet their idol, only to get caught in one hilariously awkward predicament after another.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Liberated: The New Sexual Revolution
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A documentary about today's young adult hookup culture and the stories in pop-culture that influence it.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Prince of Peoria
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A prankster prince who wants to experience life as an ordinary teen leaves his kingdom to live incognito with a single mom and her studious son.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Njan Prakashan
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Pining for a lavish life abroad, a lazy but lovable guy next door crafts a scam to avoid a career in nursing and find a wealthy spouse to secure a visa.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Maria Bamford: Old Baby
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: She's savagely upbeat. Lovably awkward. And full of surprises. A wildly funny trip through a one-of-a-kind comic mind.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Gad Elmaleh: American Dream
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In his first English-language special, comedian Gad Elmaleh gleefully digs into America's food obsessions, dating culture, slang, and more.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Rodney King
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: 25 years ago, four LAPD officers were acquitted in a state court for beating King, sparking three days of rioting that left 53 people dead. Now, around the anniversary, this Spike Lee-produced one-man show (Roger Guenver Smith) will be streaming on Netflix. A complex, semi-tragic figure, King drowned in 2012. His life was rarely smooth, or simple – its telling makes for a sober, moving watch.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Made in Mexico
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: These Mexico City socialites may lead opulent lives, but a peek behind the curtain reveals a tangled web of intrigue, envy and personal struggles.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Te Ata
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The extraordinary life of Chickasaw Nation citizen Mary Thompson Fisher is given a heartfelt tribute in this moving look at a culture in transition, and the way one woman used her voice to keep Native traditions and stories alive. Raised in Indian Territory, Fisher left home to pursue her dream of becoming an actress, only to find that her true calling was at home all along. From Chautauquas to Broadway and even the White House, Fisher traveled the world performing Native American songs and stories for heads of state, American presidents, and European royalty. Featuring Chickasaw citizens both in front of and be-hind the camera, this touching portrait starring Q’orianka Kilcher (“The New World”) and Graham Greene honors a woman whose own story was the most inspiring one she never told. -TCFF database

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Loudon Wainwright III: Surviving Twin
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Grammy-winning singer Loudon Wainwright III reflects upon his unique relationship with his father in an evening of original songs and heartfelt stories.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Michael Bolton's Big, Sexy Valentine's Day Special
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After Santa tells Michael Bolton that he needs 75,000 new babies by Christmas to meet toy supply, Michael Bolton hosts a sexy telethon to get the world to start making love.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Buddy Thunderstruck: The Maybe Pile
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Champion truck-racing dog Buddy and his best friend, ferret mechanic Darnell, paw through the "maybe pile" and test out a bunch of crazy stunts.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Awe!
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: ‘Awe’ charts the journey of a motley of characters that have nothing to do with each other but are yet connected by a single, fragile string. Who are these people and what about their lives connect them to each other is what the film is all about.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Notes from Dunblane: Lessons from a School Shooting
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In the wake of the 2012 Sandy Hook Elementary School massacre that took the lives of 20 first graders and their teachers, local clergymen Father Bob Weiss receives a letter from a fellow priest in Dunblane, Scotland, whose community suffered an eerily similar fate in 1996. From across the Atlantic, the two priests forge a poignant bond through the shared experience of trauma and healing.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: ReMastered: Who Shot the Sheriff
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In 1976, reggae icon Bob Marley survived an assassination attempt as rival political groups battled in Jamaica. But who exactly was responsible?

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Period. End of Sentence.
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In an effort to improve feminine hygiene, a machine that creates low-cost biodegradable sanitary pads is installed in a rural village in Northern India. Using the machine, a group of local women is employed to produce and sell pads, offering them newfound independence and helping to destigmatize menstruation for all.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Love Jacked
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Maya, a headstrong 28-year-old with artistic ambitions – a strong contrast to what her father Ed wants: a dutiful daughter to run the family store. Ed is shocked when Maya takes her assertions of independence a step further and decides to travel to Africa for inspiration and returns with a fiancé who is not quite what he seems.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bigger Than Africa
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When the slave boats docked in the Americas, Cuba and the Caribbean, hundreds of cultures and religions came with the Africans but only one survived the plantations. To date, the most pronounced African Culture of the Diasporas remains the culture of the Yoruba. From Brazil to Trinidad, the United States to Cuba, Haiti and the entire Caribbean, this West African culture dominates all other Cultures of Africa and could be said to have survived the plantations for hundreds of years. Bigger Than Africa follows the trans-Atlantic slave trade route from West Africa to six different countries-- USA, Nigeria, Brazil, Republic of Benin, Trinidad and Tobago and Cuba-- to explore and find reasons for the survival of this particular West African Culture.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Most Assassinated Woman in the World
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Set against the backdrop of the infamous Theatre Grand Guignol the story revolves around iconic actress Paula Maxa - the most famous of the Grand Guignol's leading ladies and the titular Most Assassinated Woman, who was graphically slain on stage multiple times a day.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Stars in the Sky: A Hunting Story
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This documentary focuses on the lives of American hunters, presented as an honest exploration of the controversies, emotions, and traditions inherent to this most primal human activity.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Kevin James: Never Don't Give Up
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Kevin James makes his long-awaited return to stand-up in this family-friendly special, dishing on fatherhood, fans, his disdain for allergies and more.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: My Birthday Song
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Rajiv Kaul, a successful ad-filmmaker, is celebrating his 40th birthday. Everything is as always: friends, food, wine, music. The only thing different is the absence of his wife and kids and the presence of a beautiful stranger, Sandy. Who is she? Why does she stare at him? Do they know each other from before?  A dangerous liaison ensues and throws Rajiv’s life upside down. Nothing is what it seems and there is no one who Rajiv can trust. Neither his wife nor his best friend, but most dangerously, not even himself.  Can Rajiv undo the past and save himself from the impending doom?  A series of twisted events blurs the fine line between past, present and future. Between what’s real and what may not be…

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Taramani
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An orthodox youngster and a free-spirited lady fall in love, only to understand that they are different in all aspects of life. How do they realise their complex requirements and mistakes?

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Manu
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The relationship between a painter and his admirer unfolds as an abstract, twist-filled hide-and-seek game against the backdrop of murder and revenge.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Nigerian Prince
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After being sent to Nigeria against his will, a stubborn Nigerian-American teenager joins forces with an internet scammer in order to return to the United States.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Weapon of Choice
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: "They never fail." The Glock pistol has been fetishised in films and the arts, and is a regular topseller in the international arms market. For the first time, the filmmaking duo Fritz Ofner and Eva Hausberger tell the story of the rise of the Glock: An Austrian design that became the most sought-after service and murder weapon worldwide. Tracing the web of power, money, violence and politics, the film masterfully portrays the dark sides of globalisation and not least an Austrian tale of willful ignorance.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Lucas Brothers: On Drugs
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Deadpan twin comics Keith and Kenny Lucas take the stage in Brooklyn with a set that touches on drugs, race, Deion Sanders, teachers and O.J. Simpson.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: A StoryBots Christmas
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When Bo mistakenly thinks that her friends don't like her gifts, she heads to the North Pole to ask Santa for help making better presents. She learns along the way that Christmas is about far more than just the toys.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: YG Future Strategy Office
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Kpop star Seungri, BIGBANG youngest member, tries to lead a team of blumbing staff at YG's Future Strategy Office in this mockumentary sitcom.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: YG Future Strategy Office
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Kpop star Seungri, BIGBANG youngest member, tries to lead a team of blumbing staff at YG's Future Strategy Office in this mockumentary sitcom.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Free Rein: The Twelve Neighs of Christmas
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: As Bright Fields preps for its Mistletoe Ball, a broken ornament leads Zoe to a family secret, while Gaby finds herself at the mercy of new boss Mia.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: For Here or to Go?
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An aspiring Indian tech entrepreneur in the Silicon Valley finds himself unexpectedly battling the bizarre American immigration system to keep his dream alive or prepare to return home forever.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Genius
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Pressured by his dad since childhood and by his boss at work, a man has a breakdown, but finds his rehabilitation at the unlikeliest of places.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Marc Maron: Too Real
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Battle-scarred stand-up comedian Marc Maron unleashes a storm of ideas about meditation, mortality, documentary films and our weird modern world.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Joe Rogan: Strange Times
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Outspoken as ever, comedian Joe Rogan takes on politics, pro wrestling, pot laws, cats, vegans and much more in a stand-up special shot in Boston.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Lynne Koplitz: Hormonal Beast
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Unabashed comedian Lynne Koplitz offers a woman's take on being crazy, the benefits of childlessness and the three things all men really want.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Vir Das: Abroad Understanding
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Comedian Vir Das tackles nationalism, globalism, good food and bad politics in two cleverly crosscut performances in New York and New Delhi.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Vir Das: Abroad Understanding
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Comedian Vir Das tackles nationalism, globalism, good food and bad politics in two cleverly crosscut performances in New York and New Delhi.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Super Monsters and the Wish Star
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Christmas wishes come true for Lobo, whose favorite cousin arrives for a surprise visit, and for Glorb, who wishes he could be everywhere at once!

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Running Man
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The fruit of the Soul Tree was the source of energy for civilization. However, many were blinded by its ultimate power which led to never-ending battles amongst the tribes. Desperate to put an end to these catastrophic wars, the leaders of each tribe finally reached a peace agreement that resulted in a competition. One player from each tribe, equipped with special watches and shields, compete against one another for a chance to win the Materion, the sacred fruit of the Soul Tree. And those brave contestants who strive to succeed in the competition are known as the Running man. There are seven representatives from each tribe in the competition. In different games, they either play against each other, split into teams or work together as one.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Running Man
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The fruit of the Soul Tree was the source of energy for civilization. However, many were blinded by its ultimate power which led to never-ending battles amongst the tribes. Desperate to put an end to these catastrophic wars, the leaders of each tribe finally reached a peace agreement that resulted in a competition. One player from each tribe, equipped with special watches and shields, compete against one another for a chance to win the Materion, the sacred fruit of the Soul Tree. And those brave contestants who strive to succeed in the competition are known as the Running man. There are seven representatives from each tribe in the competition. In different games, they either play against each other, split into teams or work together as one.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: W. Kamau Bell: Private School Negro
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Comedian W. Kamau Bell muses on parenting in the Trump era, "free speech" dustups, woke children's TV and his fear of going off the grid.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Poster Boys
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Life of three men comes in trouble when their photos appear on advertisement for sterilization.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Zion
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A portrait of Zion Clark, a young wrestler who was born without legs and grew up in foster care.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Out of Many, One
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The U.S. has long offered a promise of opportunity to immigrants, but currently immigration has become a divisive issue. This documentary illustrates how an understanding of our history and democracy is essential to constructive debate, informed civic participation and shaping a new class of citizens.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Loo Loo Kids Johny & Friends Musical Adventure
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Music-loving baby Johny goes on dance-filled adventures with his family, friends and adorable critters in this colorful, animated preschooler series. Watch all you want.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Chris D'Elia: Man on Fire
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Unbridled comic Chris D'Elia reconsiders his approach to major life events like marriage, not having kids and buying pants for your friends.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Reservoir Game
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An investigative reporter seeks to expose the whereabouts of a slush fund belonging to the former president of South Korea, Lee Myung-bak.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Reservoir Game
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An investigative reporter seeks to expose the whereabouts of a slush fund belonging to the former president of South Korea, Lee Myung-bak.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Justice: Qalb Al Adala
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The show follows an ambitious young Arab female lawyer who got her law degree in the US and instead of joining her father's law firm back at home (UAE) she decides to go out on her own as a defense attorney, pushing the legal and cultural envelope in the process.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Meghnadbodh Rohoshyo
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A professor mysteriously vanishes, leaving behind a host of suspects, a shadowy history and a clue: the anonymous birthday gift of a Bengali classic.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mahi NRI
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Set primarily in the UK's second largest city Birmingham, Mera Mahi NRI (My Beloved Non-Resident Indian) is a realistic multi- cultural comedy drama that follows the life of a student 'freshie' (a term used to describe somebody who is from the sub-continent who has recently arrived in the UK and who has very little experience of the British way of life).

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Hollywood Masters
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Personal. Provocative. Hollywood's greatest successes reveal the secrets behind their careers.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Vir Das: Losing It
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The world's got a lot of problems, but Vir Das has a lot of answers as he discusses travel, religion, his childhood and more in this stand-up special.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Vanjagar Ulagam
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A woman is murdered and her neighbour is picked up as a suspect. Meanwhile, a journalist believes he can use this murder to lure an elusive gangster, with help from the guy’s former accomplice.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Brad Paisley's Comedy Rodeo
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Country music star Brad Paisley hosts a night of music and laughs with comics Nate Bargatze, John Heffron, Jon Reep, Sarah Tiana and Mike E. Winfield.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Garbage
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Taxi driver Phanishwar is living with a mysterious girl, Nanaam, who he keeps in chains. When a medical student, Rami, a victim of revenge porn leaked online by an ex-boyfriend, seeks refuge in Goa, she stumbles into the strange but placid lives of Phanishwar and Nanaam.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Follow This
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Follow the reporters at BuzzFeed as they probe topics ranging from quirky internet crazes to safe injection spaces for opioid users.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Gurgaon
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A real estate baron Kehri Singh manages 'Preet Real Estate' which he runs in his daughter's name whom he consider's to be his lucky mascot. A sidelined and insulted Nikki Singh is ignored by his father and is considered to be insolent, useless and unlucky. In order to pay off a huge debt to a local criminal, Nikki sets off a chilling event that forces his father to revisit his dark past and confront a brutal truth.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Todo lo que sería Lucas Lauriente
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In his stand-up set, Argentine comic Lucas Lauriente animatedly rattles off reflections on different generations and begs kids to stop saying "goals."

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Todd Barry: Spicy Honey
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: With bone-dry wit, stand-up comic Todd Barry dissects texting emergencies, Hitler's taste in wine, pricey soap, cheap pizza and much more.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mo Amer: The Vagabond
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Arab-American comedian Mo Amer recounts his life as a refugee comic, from traveling with the name Mohammed to his long path to citizenship.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Puppy Star Christmas
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The Pup Star family just got bigger! And the new pups: Cindy, Rosie, Charlie, and Brody will have to learn the true meaning of Christmas. When Pup Star’s mean team, scheme to ruin Christmas, the pups end up in the North Pole to save Santa and the holiday spirit. Their adventure is filled with great pup-tastic songs to spread holiday cheer all year round.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Noblemen
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A 15 year old boy, struggling with his adolescent years, is terrorized by a gang of bullies in a posh boarding school. This sets forth a chain of events that leads to a loss of life and innocence.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ladies First
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An inspirational survival story of Deepika Kumari who, as a girl born on the roadside to abject poverty in rural India, went in search of food, stumbled upon archery, and within 4 years became the Number One archer in the World.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Recovery Boys
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In the heart of America's opioid epidemic, four men try to reinvent their lives and mend their broken relationships after years of drug abuse.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Late Life: The Chien-Ming Wang Story
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The first and only Taiwanese player for the New York Yankees, Chien-Ming Wang held many titles: American League Wins Leader, World Series Champion, Olympian, Time 100 Most Influential, and The Pride of Taiwan. He had it all - until a 2008 injury forever altered the course of his career. Late Life: The Chien-Ming Wang Story - named after the late sinking action on his signature pitch - follows the rise and fall of the international icon as he fights his way back into the Major Leagues through endless rehab programs and lengthy stints away from home, carrying the weight of the world on his battered shoulder. A poignant and intimate account of Wang’s steadfast quest, Late Life tells the story of a man who is unwilling to give up and unable to let go.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Pandigai
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A low-level hotel worker gets involved in a street fighting racket on the advice of a compulsive gambler. When the duo realise they have been duped by the gangster controlling the racket, they decided to rob him…

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Brij Mohan Amar Rahe!
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Faking his death to escape the realities of his uneventful life worked out well for Brij Mohan -- until he was sentenced to death for his own murder.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Pahuna: The Little Visitors
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Three Nepalese children rely on each other for survival after they become separated from their parents while entering India.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Adhugo
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Bunty, the little pink piglet is the apple of Chanti’s (Sathwik) eye. But what happens when this innocent little creature is embroiled with people who each have their own agenda to seek?

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Jindua
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An existing relationship is threatened when a new girl catches a man's eye.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Frat Star
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: "Frat Star" explores the alluring, superficial, manipulative, and dark world of Ivy League fraternity culture. An insecure, poor, and broken-hearted Nick enters freshman year with no interest in fraternities. This all changes when his old money roommate Billy convinces him to pledge.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: King of Peking
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When home entertainment enters the market in 90s Beijing, a former projectionist ropes his young son into starting their own pirate movie company, but easy money comes with its own price tag.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Jonaki
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: While Jonaki, an 80-year-old woman, searches for love in a strange world of decaying memories, her lover, now old and grey, returns to a world she is leaving behind.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Joshua: Teenager vs. Superpower
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When the Chinese Communist Party backtracks on its promise of autonomy to Hong Kong, teenager Joshua Wong decides to save his city. Rallying thousands of kids to skip school and occupy the streets, Joshua becomes an unlikely leader in Hong Kong and one of China’s most notorious dissidents.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Aditi Mittal: Things They Wouldn't Let Me Say
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Trailblazing comic Aditi Mittal mixes topical stand-up with frank talk about being single, wearing thongs and the awkwardness of Indian movie ratings.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sei
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A wannabe actor lands himself in trouble when he disguises as an ambulance driver to help his bed-ridden father

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Pup Star: World Tour

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After winning a local talent show, the Beat Bugs journey to compete on "The Bug Factor," a televised singing contest held in faraway Rocket Ship Park.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: It's Halloween in Pitchfork Pines, but the neighbors don't seem to be in the mood. Can the Super Monsters save their favorite holiday?

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Music Teacher
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Despite his ambitions to make it big, Beni is still stuck in the hills, bitter and hurt, struggling to make ends meet by teaching music and singing in clubs. Jyotsna, his estranged student and now a Bollywood singer, left the hills 8 years ago. The town is abuzz with the news of Jyotsna's return to perform at a music concert. Beni has to come to terms with the pains of the past and the delusions of the present to deal with both, Jyotsna's presence in the hills and in his life.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: B. A. Pass 2 is the story of a young girl, who, in order to achieve her goals and to avoid marriage, makes a few wrong decisions and adopts ill habits that eventually ruin her life.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Love and Shukla
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A sexually inexperienced rickshaw driver struggles to build intimacy with his shy new wife in their tiny, overcrowded quarters.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: True: Wonderful Wishes
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Do-gooding True and Bartleby will go anywhere to make wishes come true -- from the bottom of the Living Sea to the tip of Mount Tippy Tippy Top!

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Yoo Byung Jae: Discomfort Zone
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Daring comedian Yoo Byung-jae connects criticism he's received from the general public to some of the most touchy issues in current Korean society.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Yoo Byung Jae: Discomfort Zone
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Daring comedian Yoo Byung-jae connects criticism he's received from the general public to some of the most touchy issues in current Korean society.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Salam - The First ****** Nobel Laureate
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: "Salam" is a feature length documentary about the Nobel prize winning Pakistani physicist, Abdus Salam. The film reveals the extraordinary life of the charismatic Abdus Salam, in all its color, vitality and tragedy. It is the story of a man who traversed two worlds with ease: one of science and religion, modernity and tradition, war and peace and obscurity and celebrity. When he won the Nobel prize in 1979, he became the very first Pakistani to achieve this distinction, and only the fourth from the subcontinent. Born in 1926 in a remote village in Punjab, British India, Salam was a child prodigy. He came from humble beginnings, growing up in a small brick house with a large family of eleven. While Salam's legacy looms large in the world of physics, he is largely forgotten in Pakistan because of his faith. Children do not read about him and he is still vilified and maligned by right wing clerics for being a "Qadiani"-a derogatory term for someone belonging to the Ahmadiyya community. By telling this complex story of a man who due to extremism could not strengthen his people as he so deeply desired, the film draws attention to the state of affairs in the world today, where knowledge is sacrificed at the altar of ignorance and intolerance, depriving the coming generation of all that is precious.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Shubh Aarambh
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In the midst of her wedding, a young girl tries to save a 28 year old love marriage, of her future in-laws, which is falling apart.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mr. Chandramouli
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Raghav, a professional boxer, finds himself in a fix when an unexpected turn of events gets him tangled in a battle between his passion, family and the love of his life.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Jani Dueñas: Grandes fracasos de ayer y hoy
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Radio broadcaster, actress and comedian Jani Dueñas brings her acid sense of humor to this stand-up special as she pours out her feelings on issues that are all too universal, from aging to dieting to sex.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Nathicharami
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A widow struggles with the dilemma of her own growing sexual needs, and her desire to remain faithful to the memory of her late husband.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: True: Magical Friends
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The power of friendship can solve any problem -- and the Rainbow Kingdom's got plenty to go around. Cue Bartleby and True for the rescue!

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Todd Glass: Act Happy
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Try to keep up as comedian Todd Glass delivers rapid-fire stand-up that bounces from his heart attack to his coming out to how to eat a Kit Kat.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Yoo Byung Jae: Too Much Information
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: "Saturday Night Live Korea" writer-turned-comedian Yoo Byung-jae lays bare his childhood memories and philosophy on sex in his first stand-up venture.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Yoo Byung Jae: Too Much Information
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: "Saturday Night Live Korea" writer-turned-comedian Yoo Byung-jae lays bare his childhood memories and philosophy on sex in his first stand-up venture.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Elf Pets: Santa's St. Bernards Save Christmas
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: What happens when an entire town forgets the true spirit of the Christmas season? It’s up to Santa and a delightful cast of North Pole characters to help them remember! In this festive Elf Pets® animated special, Santa discovers there is not enough Christmas spirit for him to make Christmas magical. Thankfully, The Elf on the Shelf® Scout Elves, Santa’s special Elf Pets® St. Bernard pups and a big-hearted family join forces to help others remember the true meaning of Christmas and ensure another successful holiday season for Santa!

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Little Singham
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This animated series showcases the fun and thrilling adventures of Little Singham, a brave kid super-cop with lion powers, as he defends his town and the world from evil villains, scary mutants and even aliens .

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Harith Iskander: I Told You So

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Luna Petunia returns to magical Amazia, adding memories to her scrapbook with old friends -- and a new pal from the Animal Empire.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Enissa Amani: Ehrenwort
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Live from Hamburg, Iranian-German comedian Enissa Amani shares her take on German engineering, tax deductions and online fan-mail etiquette.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Puriyaatha Puthir

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Villains are rampaging through Charter City and the Flex Fighters -- Jake, Ricardo and Nathan -- need your help to halt the chaos.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Two men kidnap the daughter of a rich man, and the latter approaches a retired cop to track the missing woman.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Abducted and confined in a room by a gang of sadistic men, a pregnant woman tries to escape, against insurmountable odds.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Highland: Thailand's Marijuana Awakening
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Thailand's complicated history with marijuana continues to play a role in its policies and laws, as well as the health and security of its citizens.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: D.L. Hughley: Contrarian
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Comedian D.L. Hughley riffs on politics, "Black Panther," his upbringing and more in a rapid-fire stand-up show at Philadelphia's Merriam Theater.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Joe Mande's Award-Winning Comedy Special
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Stand-up comic Joe Mande aims for critical adulation with this special that covers dating shows, "Shark Tank," Jewish summer camp and much more.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Jen Kirkman: Just Keep Livin'?
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Incisive comic Jen Kirkman gets real about women's bodies, the value of alone time and an Italian private tour guide who may have been a ghost.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Umbrella Academy
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A family of former child heroes, now grown apart, must reunite to continue to protect the world.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Secret of Skinwalker Ranch
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A team of experts and scientists undertakes exhaustive research at Skinwalker Ranch, an infamous location for paranormal activity and UFO sightings.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Virgin River
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After seeing an ad for a midwife, a recently divorced big-city nurse moves to the redwood forests of California, where she meets an intriguing man.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Gentlemen
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: American expat Mickey Pearson has built a highly profitable marijuana empire in London. When word gets out that he’s looking to cash out of the business forever it triggers plots, schemes, bribery and blackmail in an attempt to steal his domain out from under him.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Love, Death & Robots
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Terrifying creatures, wicked surprises and dark comedy converge in this NSFW anthology of animated stories presented by Tim Miller and David Fincher.
