data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Murphy is a flawed and irreverent woman who just happens to be blind and is the only “witness” to the murder of her drug-dealing friend, Tyson. When the police dismiss her story, she sets out with her dog, Pretzel, to find the killer while also managing her colorful dating life and the job she hates at Breaking Blind — the guide-dog school owned by her overprotective parents.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Tuca & Bertie
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Free-spirited toucan Tuca and self-doubting song thrush Bertie are best friends -- and birds -- who guide each other through life's ups and downs.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Russian Doll
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Nadia keeps dying and reliving her 36th birthday party. She's trapped in a surreal time loop -- and staring down the barrel of her own mortality.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Jurassic World: Camp Cretaceous
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Six teens attending an adventure camp on the opposite side of Isla Nublar must band together to survive when dinosaurs wreak havoc on the island.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Witcher
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Geralt of Rivia, a mutated monster-hunter for hire, journeys toward his destiny in a turbulent world where people often prove more wicked than beasts.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bridgerton
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Wealth, lust, and betrayal set in the backdrop of Regency era England, seen through the eyes of the powerful Bridgerton family.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: A Call to Spy
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In the beginning of WWII, with Britain becoming desperate, Churchill orders his new spy agency - SOE - to recruit and train women as spies.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Surviving R. Kelly
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Celebrated as one of the greatest R&B singers of all time, R. Kelly’s genre defining career and playboy lifestyle has been riddled with rumors of abuse, predatory behavior, and pedophilia. Despite damning evidence and multiple witnesses, to date, none of these accusations have seemingly affected him. For the first time ever, survivors and people from R. Kelly’s inner circle, are coming forward with new allegations about his sexual, mental, and physical abuse. They are now finally ready to share their full story and shed light on the secret life the public has never seen.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Are You Afraid of the Dark?
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Each season of this horror anthology series follows a different group of kids, members of the Midnight Society, as they discover terrifying curses and creatures.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The UnXplained
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The show will explore the facts behind the world's most fascinating, strange and inexplicable mysteries.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Queen's Gambit
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a Kentucky orphanage in the 1950s, a young girl discovers an astonishing talent for chess while struggling with addiction.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Roswell, New Mexico
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After reluctantly returning to her tourist-trap hometown of Roswell, New Mexico, the daughter of undocumented immigrants discovers a shocking truth about her teenage crush who is now a police officer—he’s an alien who has kept his unearthly abilities hidden his entire life. She protects his secret as the two reconnect and begin to investigate his origins, but when a violent attack and long-standing government cover-up point to a greater alien presence on Earth, the politics of fear and hatred threaten to expose him and destroy their deepening romance.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dead to Me
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A hotheaded widow searching for the hit-and-run driver who mowed down her husband befriends an eccentric optimist who isn't quite what she seems.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: I Think You Should Leave with Tim Robinson
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: There is no such thing as an ordinary interaction in this offbeat sketch comedy series that features a deep roster of guest stars.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Last Dance
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A 10-part documentary chronicling the untold story of Michael Jordan and the Chicago Bulls dynasty with rare, never-before-seen footage and sound from the 1997-98 championship season – plus over 100 interviews with famous figures and basketball’s biggest names.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Locke & Key
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Three siblings who move into their ancestral estate after their father's gruesome murder discover their new home's magical keys, which must be used in their stand against an evil creature who wants the keys and their powers.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Outer Banks
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A tight-knit group of teens unearths a long-buried secret, setting off a chain of illicit events that takes them on an adventure they'll never forget.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Emily in Paris
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When ambitious Chicago marketing exec Emily unexpectedly lands her dream job in Paris, she embraces a new life as she juggles work, friends and romance.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Rental
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Two couples rent a vacation home for what should be a celebratory weekend get-away.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Unbelievable
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A teenager is charged with lying about her rape allegation, but two determined investigative female detectives discover a far more sinister truth.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Kingdom
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In this zombie thriller set in Korea's medieval Joseon dynasty which has been defeated by corruption and famine, a mysterious rumor of the king’s death spreads, as does a strange plague that renders the infected immune to death and hungry for flesh. The crown prince, fallen victim to a conspiracy, sets out on a journey to unveil the evil scheme and save his people.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Kingdom
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In this zombie thriller set in Korea's medieval Joseon dynasty which has been defeated by corruption and famine, a mysterious rumor of the king’s death spreads, as does a strange plague that renders the infected immune to death and hungry for flesh. The crown prince, fallen victim to a conspiracy, sets out on a journey to unveil the evil scheme and save his people.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: I'm Thinking of Ending Things
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Nothing is as it seems when a woman experiencing misgivings about her new boyfriend joins him on a road trip to meet his parents at their remote farm.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Irishman
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Pennsylvania, 1956. Frank Sheeran, a war veteran of Irish origin who works as a truck driver, accidentally meets mobster Russell Bufalino. Once Frank becomes his trusted man, Bufalino sends him to Chicago with the task of helping Jimmy Hoffa, a powerful union leader related to organized crime, with whom Frank will maintain a close friendship for nearly twenty years.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Space Force
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A four-star general begrudgingly teams up with an eccentric scientist to get the U.S. military's newest agency — Space Force — ready for lift-off.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Never Have I Ever
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The complicated life of a modern-day first generation Indian American teenage girl, inspired by Mindy Kaling's own childhood.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Extraction
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Tyler Rake, a fearless black market mercenary, embarks on the most deadly extraction of his career when he's enlisted to rescue the kidnapped son of an imprisoned international crime lord.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Synchronic
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Two New Orleans paramedics' lives are ripped apart after they encounter a series of horrific deaths linked to a designer drug with bizarre, otherworldly effects.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Yes, God, Yes
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Alice, a young innocent Catholic girl, is tempted into masturbating after an AOL chat suddenly turns sexual, however is conflicted as the act would be considered a sin.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Enola Holmes
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: While searching for her missing mother, intrepid teen Enola Holmes uses her sleuthing skills to outsmart big brother Sherlock and help a runaway lord.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Comey Rule
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An immersive, behind-the-headlines account of the historically turbulent events surrounding the 2016 presidential election and its aftermath, which divided a nation. This two-part biopic tells the story of two powerful figures, Comey and Trump, whose strikingly different personalities, ethics and loyalties put them on a collision course.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Old Guard
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Four undying warriors who've secretly protected humanity for centuries become targeted for their mysterious powers just as they discover a new immortal.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Black Summer
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In the dark, early days of a zombie apocalypse, complete strangers band together to find the strength they need to survive and get back to loved ones.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Scary Stories to Tell in the Dark
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Mill Valley, Pennsylvania, Halloween night, 1968. After playing a joke on a school bully, Stella and her friends decide to sneak into a supposedly haunted house that once belonged to the powerful Bellows family, unleashing dark forces that they will be unable to control.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Devil All the Time
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In Knockemstiff, Ohio and its neighboring backwoods, sinister characters converge around young Arvin Russell as he fights the evil forces that threaten him and his family.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Fantastic Fungi
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Fantastic Fungi is a descriptive time-lapse journey about the magical, mysterious and medicinal world of fungi and their power to heal, sustain and contribute to the regeneration of life on Earth that began 3.5 billion years ago.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The King
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: England, 15th century. Hal, a capricious prince who lives among the populace far from court, is forced by circumstances to reluctantly accept the throne and become Henry V.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Dark Crystal: Age of Resistance
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Return to the world of Thra, where three Gelfling discover the horrifying secret behind the Skeksis' power and set out to ignite the fires of rebellion and save their world.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: When They See Us
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Five teens from Harlem become trapped in a nightmare when they're falsely accused of a brutal attack in Central Park.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Rambo: Last Blood
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After fighting his demons for decades, John Rambo now lives in peace on his family ranch in Arizona, but his rest is interrupted when Gabriela, the granddaughter of his housekeeper María, disappears after crossing the border into Mexico to meet her biological father. Rambo, who has become a true father figure for Gabriela over the years, undertakes a desperate and dangerous journey to find her.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Haunting of Bly Manor
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After an au pair’s tragic death, Henry Wingrave hires a young American nanny to care for his orphaned niece and nephew who reside at Bly Manor with the estate’s chef Owen, groundskeeper Jamie and housekeeper, Mrs. Grose. But all is not as it seems at the manor, and centuries of dark secrets of love and loss are waiting to be unearthed in this chilling tale.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: 1BR
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When Sarah lucks into a sweet one-bedroom at Asilo Del Mar Apartments in Los Angeles, she think she's hit the jackpot. It's got plenty of space, friendly tenants, group BBQs and even a cute neighbour next door. All is not what it seems: loud noises start keeping her awake at night; her cat is missing; everyone seems to be a little too helpful and friendly, except for the weirdo, Lester. Soon, Sarah learns she didn't choose this apartment — it chose her.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Trading Paint
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A stock car racing legend is drawn back to the dirt track when his son, an aspiring driver, joins a rival racing team.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sweet Magnolias
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Lifelong friends Maddie, Helen and Dana Sue lift each other as they juggle relationships, family and careers in the small, Southern town of Serenity.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sweetheart
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Jenn has washed ashore a small tropical island and it doesn’t take her long to realize she’s completely alone. She must spend her days not only surviving the elements, but must also fend off the malevolent force that comes out each night.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Official Secrets
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The true story of British intelligence whistleblower Katharine Gun who—prior to the 2003 Iraq invasion—leaked a top-secret NSA memo exposing a joint US-UK illegal spying operation against members of the UN Security Council. The memo proposed blackmailing member states into voting for war.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Warrior Nun
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After waking up in a morgue, an orphaned teen discovers she now possesses superpowers as the chosen Halo-Bearer for a secret sect of demon-hunting nuns.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Pieces of a Woman
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When a young mother's home birth ends in unfathomable tragedy, she begins a year-long odyssey of mourning that fractures relationships with loved ones in this deeply personal story of a woman learning to live alongside her loss.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Freaks
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Kept locked inside the house by her father, 7-year-old Chloe lives in fear and fascination of the outside world, where Abnormals create a constant threat—or so she believes. When a mysterious stranger offers her a glimpse of what's really happening outside, Chloe soon finds that while the truth isn't so simple, the danger is very real.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: 21 Bridges
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An embattled NYPD detective, is thrust into a citywide manhunt for a pair of cop killers after uncovering a massive and unexpected conspiracy. As the night unfolds, lines become blurred on who he is pursuing, and who is in pursuit of him.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: 6 Underground
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After faking his death, a tech billionaire recruits a team of international operatives for a bold and bloody mission to take down a brutal dictator.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mank
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: 1930s Hollywood is re-evaluated through the eyes of scathing social critic and alcoholic screenwriter Herman J. Mankiewicz as he races to finish the screenplay of Citizen Kane (1941).

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: I Care a Lot
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A crooked legal guardian who drains the savings of her elderly wards meets her match when a woman she tries to swindle turns out to be more than she first appears.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Midnight Gospel
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Traversing trippy worlds inside his universe simulator, Clancy the space caster explores existential questions about life, death and everything in between.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: El Camino: A Breaking Bad Movie
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In the wake of his dramatic escape from captivity, Jesse Pinkman must come to terms with his past in order to forge some kind of future.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Always Be My Maybe
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Reunited after 15 years, famous chef Sasha and hometown musician Marcus feel the old sparks of attraction but struggle to adapt to each other's worlds.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Social Dilemma
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This documentary-drama hybrid explores the dangerous human impact of social networking, with tech experts sounding the alarm on their own creations.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Straight Up
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Todd and Rory are intellectual soul mates. He might be gay. She might not care. A romantic-comedy drama with a twist; a love story without the thrill of copulation.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Outpost
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A small unit of U.S. soldiers, alone at the remote Combat Outpost Keating, located deep in the valley of three mountains in Afghanistan, battles to defend against an overwhelming force of Taliban fighters in a coordinated attack. The Battle of Kamdesh, as it was known, was the bloodiest American engagement of the Afghan War in 2009 and Bravo Troop 3-61 CAV became one of the most decorated units of the 19-year conflict.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Hateful Eight: Extended Version
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Trapped at a stagecoach stop as a storm rages outside, two bounty hunters and an outlaw face a gallery of rogues. Features never-before-seen footage.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Triple Frontier
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Struggling to make ends meet, former special ops soldiers reunite for a high-stakes heist: stealing $75 million from a South American drug lord.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Eurovision Song Contest: The Story of Fire Saga
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Two small-town aspiring musicians chase their pop star dreams at a global music competition, where high stakes, scheming rivals and onstage mishaps test their bond.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Family
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An enigmatic conservative Christian group known as the Family wields enormous influence in Washington, D.C., in pursuit of its global ambitions.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: After We Collided
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Based on the 2014 romance novel of the same name, this follows the love life of two young adults.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: In the Shadow of the Moon
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In 1988, Philadelphia police officer Thomas "Locke" Lockhart, hungry to become a detective, begins tracking a serial killer whose crimes defy scientific explanation. When the killer mysteriously resurfaces nine years later, Locke's obsession with finding the truth threatens to destroy his career, his family, and possibly his sanity.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Code 8
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In Lincoln City, some inhabitants have extraordinary abilities. Most live below the poverty line, under the close surveillance of a heavily militarized police force. Connor, a construction worker with powers, involves with a criminal gang to help his ailing mother. (Based on the short film “Code 8,” 2016.)

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Crash Landing on You
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A paragliding mishap drops a South Korean heiress in North Korea -- and into the life of an army officer, who decides he will help her hide.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Crash Landing on You
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A paragliding mishap drops a South Korean heiress in North Korea -- and into the life of an army officer, who decides he will help her hide.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Fractured
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Driving cross-country, Ray and his wife and daughter stop at a highway rest area where his daughter falls and breaks her arm. After a frantic rush to the hospital and a clash with the check-in nurse, Ray is finally able to get her to a doctor. While the wife and daughter go downstairs for an MRI, Ray, exhausted, passes out in a chair in the lobby. Upon waking up, they have no record or knowledge of Ray's family ever being checked in.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Love Is Blind
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Singles who want to be loved for who they are, rather than what they look like, have signed up for a less conventional approach to modern dating.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Hollywood
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A group of aspiring actors and filmmakers in post-World War II Hollywood try to make it big — no matter the cost.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Chef Show
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Writer, director and food enthusiast Jon Favreau and chef Roy Choi explore food in and out of the kitchen with accomplished chefs and celebrity friends.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Raising Dion
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A widowed single mom discovers that her son has super powers and tries to figure out how to raise him safely and responsibly.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ava
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A black ops assassin is forced to fight for her own survival after a job goes dangerously wrong.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Trial of the Chicago 7
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: What was supposed to be a peaceful protest turned into a violent clash with the police. What followed was one of the most notorious trials in history.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sweet Home
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: As humans turn into savage monsters and wreak terror, one troubled teen and his apartment neighbors fight to survive — and to hold on to their humanity.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sweet Home
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: As humans turn into savage monsters and wreak terror, one troubled teen and his apartment neighbors fight to survive — and to hold on to their humanity.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Dirt
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The story of Mötley Crüe and their rise from the Sunset Strip club scene of the early 1980s to superstardom.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ratched
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An origins story, beginning in 1947, which follows Ratched's journey and evolution from nurse to full-fledged monster tracking her murderous progression through the mental health care system.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Can You Keep a Secret?
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Thinking they're about to crash, Emma spills her secrets to a stranger on a plane. At least, she thought he was a stranger...Until she later meets Jack, her company's young CEO, who now knows every humiliating detail about her. Based on the blockbuster NYT bestseller.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Politician
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Payton has known since childhood that he's going to be president. First he'll have to navigate the most treacherous political landscape: high school.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Murder Mystery
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: On a long-awaited trip to Europe, a New York City cop and his hairdresser wife scramble to solve a baffling murder aboard a billionaire's yacht.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Da 5 Bloods
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Four African-American Vietnam veterans return to Vietnam. They are in search of the remains of their fallen squad leader and the promise of buried treasure. These heroes battle forces of humanity and nature while confronted by the lasting ravages of the immorality of the Vietnam War.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Midnight Sky
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This post-apocalyptic tale follows Augustine, a lonely scientist in the Arctic, as he races to stop Sully and her fellow astronauts from returning home to a mysterious global catastrophe.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Cursed
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Im Jin Hee is a gung ho reporter, out to do the ring thing. She covers a violent case involving Forest, the biggest IT company in South Korea. The chairman of Forest is Jin Jong Hyun. He relies heavily on shamanism. During her investigation, Im Jin Hee learns of a spiritual consulting company that is affiliated with Forest. The head of that affiliate company is Jin Kyung. While trying to reveal the secret behind Forest, Im Jin Hee meets So Jin. She is possessed by a spirit and she has a special ability.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Cursed
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Im Jin Hee is a gung ho reporter, out to do the ring thing. She covers a violent case involving Forest, the biggest IT company in South Korea. The chairman of Forest is Jin Jong Hyun. He relies heavily on shamanism. During her investigation, Im Jin Hee learns of a spiritual consulting company that is affiliated with Forest. The head of that affiliate company is Jin Kyung. While trying to reveal the secret behind Forest, Im Jin Hee meets So Jin. She is possessed by a spirit and she has a special ability.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Society
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When everyone else mysteriously vanishes from their wealthy town, the teen residents of West Ham must forge their own society to survive.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Wine Country
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A group of friends head to the land of oaky Chardonnays and big, bold Cabernet Sauvignons for one member of the squad’s 50th birthday party.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Movies That Made Us
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Unwrap the real stories behind these iconic Christmas blockbusters, thanks to insider interviews and behind-the-scenes peeks.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Wrong Missy
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A guy meets the woman of his dreams and invites her to his company's corporate retreat, but realizes he sent the invite to the wrong person.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: She
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An undercover assignment to expose a drug ring becomes a timid Mumbai constable's road to empowerment as she realizes her dormant sexuality's potential.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Five Feet Apart
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Seventeen-year-old Stella spends most of her time in the hospital as a cystic fibrosis patient. Her life is full of routines, boundaries and self-control — all of which get put to the test when she meets Will, an impossibly charming teen who has the same illness. There's an instant flirtation, though restrictions dictate that they must maintain a safe distance between them. As their connection intensifies, so does the temptation to throw the rules out the window and embrace that attraction.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Brahms: The Boy II
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After a family moves into the Heelshire Mansion, their young son soon makes friends with a life-like doll called Brahms.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: After
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Tessa Young is a dedicated student, dutiful daughter and loyal girlfriend to her high school sweetheart. Entering her first semester of college, Tessa's guarded world opens up when she meets Hardin Scott, a mysterious and brooding rebel who makes her question all she thought she knew about herself -- and what she wants out of life.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Cursed
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In this fresh take on the Arthurian legend, teenager Nimue joins forces with mercenary Arthur on a quest to find Merlin and deliver an ancient sword.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Someone Great
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An aspiring music journalist lands her dream job and is about to move to San Francisco when her boyfriend of nine years decides to call it quits. To nurse her broken heart, she and her two best friends spend one outrageous last adventure in New York City.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Living with Yourself
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Burned out on life, Miles undergoes a strange procedure at a strip mall spa -- and wakes to find he's been replaced by a better version of himself.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Two Popes
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Frustrated with the direction of the church, Cardinal Bergoglio requests permission to retire in 2012 from Pope Benedict. Instead, facing scandal and self-doubt, the introspective Pope Benedict summons his harshest critic and future successor to Rome to reveal a secret that would shake the foundations of the Catholic Church.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Wind
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Lizzy is a tough, resourceful frontierswoman settling a remote stretch of land on the 19th-century American frontier. Isolated from civilization in a desolate wilderness where the wind never stops howling, she begins to sense a sinister presence that seems to be borne of the land itself, and when a newlywed couple arrive at a nearby homestead, their presence amplifies Lizzy's fears, setting into motion a shocking chain of events.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bad Trip
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Two pals embark on a road trip full of funny pranks that pull real people into mayhem.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Half of It
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Shy, straight-A student Ellie is hired by sweet but inarticulate jock Paul, who needs help wooing the most popular girl in school. But their new and unlikely friendship gets tricky when Ellie discovers she has feelings for the same girl.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dolemite Is My Name
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The story of Rudy Ray Moore, who created the iconic big screen pimp character Dolemite in the 1970s.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Prom
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A troupe of hilariously self-obsessed theater stars swarm into a small conservative Indiana town in support of a high school girl who wants to take her girlfriend to the prom.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Jeffrey Epstein: Filthy Rich
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Stories from survivors fuel this docuseries examining how convicted sex offender Jeffrey Epstein used his wealth and power to carry out his abuses.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ophelia
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Ophelia comes of age as lady-in-waiting for Queen Gertrude, and her singular spirit captures Hamlet's affections. As lust and betrayal threaten the kingdom, Ophelia finds herself trapped between true love and controlling her own destiny.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ma Rainey's Black Bottom
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Tensions rise when trailblazing blues singer Ma Rainey and her band gather at a recording studio in Chicago in 1927.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Call
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Connected by phone in the same home but 20 years apart, a serial killer puts another woman’s past — and life — on the line to change her own fate.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Call
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Connected by phone in the same home but 20 years apart, a serial killer puts another woman’s past — and life — on the line to change her own fate.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Hillbilly Elegy
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An urgent phone call pulls a Yale Law student back to his Ohio hometown, where he reflects on three generations of family history and his own future.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Selling Sunset
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The elite real estate brokers at The Oppenheim Group sell the luxe life to affluent buyers in LA. The drama ramps up when a new agent joins the team.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: I Am Not Okay with This
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Sydney is a teenage girl navigating the trials and tribulations of high school while dealing with the complexities of her family, her budding sexuality, and mysterious superpowers just beginning to awaken deep within her.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Paradise Hills
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A young woman is sent to Paradise Hills to be reformed, only to learn that the high-class facility's beautiful facade hides a sinister secret.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: WHAT / IF
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In this neo-noir thriller series, a pair of cash-strapped newlyweds accept a lucrative but morally dubious offer from a mysterious female benefactor.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Highwaymen
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In 1934, Frank Hamer and Manny Gault, two former Texas Rangers, are commissioned to put an end to the wave of vicious crimes perpetrated by Bonnie Parker and Clyde Barrow, a notorious duo of infamous robbers and cold-blooded killers who nevertheless are worshiped by the public.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Unsolved Mysteries
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Real cases of perplexing disappearances, shocking murders and paranormal encounters fuel this gripping revival of the iconic documentary series.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Fast Color
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A woman is forced to go on the run when her superhuman abilities are discovered. Years after having abandoned her family, the only place she has left to hide is home.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Cheer
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The stakes on the mat are high, but for these cheerleaders, the only thing more brutal than their workouts and more exceptional than their performances are the stories of adversity and triumph behind the athletes themselves.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: DC Super Hero Girls
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The world may know them as Wonder Woman, Supergirl and Batgirl, but not-so-typical teenagers Diana, Kara and Barbara, alongside their Super Hero friends have much more to deal with than just protecting Metropolis from some of the most sinister school-aged Super-Villains. After all, being teens is tough enough, what with school, friends, family and the chaos that comes with managing a social life. But add super powers and a secret identity to the mix, and things can get a lot more complicated.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Order
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Out to avenge his mother's death, a college student pledges a secret order and lands in a war between werewolves and practitioners of dark magic.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Countdown
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A young nurse downloads an app that tells her she only has three days to live. With time ticking away and a mysterious figure haunting her, she must find a way to save her life before time runs out.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Down to Earth with Zac Efron
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Actor Zac Efron journeys around the world with wellness expert Darin Olien in a travel show that explores healthy, sustainable ways to live.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Extremely Wicked, Shockingly Evil and Vile
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A chronicle of the crimes of Ted Bundy, from the perspective of his longtime girlfriend, Elizabeth Kloepfer, who refused to believe the truth about him for years.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Kipo and the Age of Wonderbeasts
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A girl explores the possibilities in a post-apocalyptic world.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: We Summon the Darkness
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Three best friends attending a heavy-metal show cross paths with sadistic killers after they travel to a secluded country home for an after party.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Paper Tigers
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Three middle aged men polish their martial arts skills to avenge their fallen master.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Between Two Ferns: The Movie
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Galifianakis dreamed of becoming a star. But when Will Ferrell discovered his public access TV show, 'Between Two Ferns' and uploaded it to Funny or Die, Zach became a viral laughing stock. Now Zach and his crew are taking a road trip to complete a series of high-profile celebrity interviews and restore his reputation.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Too Hot to Handle
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: On the shores of paradise, gorgeous singles meet and mingle. But there’s a twist. To win a $100,000 grand prize, they’ll have to give up sex.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Game Changers
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: From the UFC Octagon in Las Vegas and the anthropology lab at Dartmouth, to a strongman gym in Berlin and the bushlands of Zimbabwe, the world is introduced to elite athletes, special ops soldiers, visionary scientists, cultural icons, and everyday heroes—each on a mission to create a seismic shift in the way we eat and live.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dick Johnson Is Dead
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: With this inventive portrait, director Kirsten Johnson seeks a way to keep her 86-year-old father alive forever. Utilizing moviemaking magic and her family’s dark humor, she celebrates Dr. Dick Johnson’s last years by staging fantasies of death and beyond. Together, dad and daughter confront the great inevitability awaiting us all.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Velvet Buzzsaw
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Big money artists and mega-collectors pay a high price when art collides with commerce. After a series of paintings by an unknown artist are discovered, a supernatural force enacts revenge on those who have allowed their greed to get in the way of art.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Another Life
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After a massive alien artifact lands on Earth, Niko Breckinridge leads an interstellar mission to track down its source and make first contact.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: L.A.'s Finest
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Syd Burnett has left her complicated past behind to become an LAPD detective. Paired with a new partner, Nancy McKenna, a working mom with an equally complex past, Syd is pushed to examine whether her unapologetic lifestyle might be masking a greater personal secret. These two women don't agree on much, but they find common ground when it comes to taking on the most dangerous criminals in Los Angeles.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Tiger King
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A zoo owner spirals out of control amid a cast of eccentric characters in this true murder-for-hire story from the underworld of big cat breeding.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Old Ways
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Cristina, a journalist of Mexican origin, travels to her ancestral home in Veracruz to investigate a story of sorcery and healing. There, she is kidnapped by a group of locals who claim she's the devil incarnated.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Laundromat
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When her idyllic vacation takes an unthinkable turn, Ellen Martin begins investigating a fake insurance policy, only to find herself down a rabbit hole of questionable dealings that can be linked to a Panama City law firm and its vested interest in helping the world's wealthiest citizens amass larger fortunes.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Project Power
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An ex-soldier, a teen and a cop collide in New Orleans as they hunt for the source behind a dangerous new pill that grants users temporary superpowers.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: In the Tall Grass
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After hearing a child screaming for help from the green depths of a vast field of tall grass, Becky, a pregnant woman, and Cal, her brother, park their car near a mysterious abandoned church and recklessly enter the field, discovering that they are not alone and because of some reason they are unable of escaping a completely inextricable vegetable labyrinth.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: #Alive
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: As a grisly virus rampages a city, a lone man stays locked inside his apartment, digitally cut off from seeking help and desperate to find a way out.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Graboids are illegally taken to a new island resort by a rich playboy as a dangerous form of trophy hunting, and Burt Gummer steps up to save the day.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: It tells an unpredictable 24-hour love story of the four-dimensional innocent girl Jung Saet Byeol who was once a troublemaker and the adorkable caring male store manager, Choi Dae Hyun, in the context of a convenience store. They have met each other accidentally 4 years ago, back then Saet Byeol asked Dae Hyun to buy cigarettes for them. Until now, Saet Byeol comes to the convenience store Dae Hyun runs for a part-time job, their hilarious romantic story starts.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The lives of several cheerleaders are changed forever when a shocking crime rocks their quiet suburban world.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When he's invited to manage a hotel for dead souls, an elite hotelier gets to know the establishment's ancient owner and her strange world.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Pushed to his breaking point, a master welder in a small town at the foot of the Rocky Mountains quietly fortifies a bulldozer with 30 tons of concrete and steel and seeks to destroy those he believes have wronged him.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An unlikely friendship between two neighbors becomes an unexpectedly emotional journey when the younger man is diagnosed with terminal cancer.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The last in a line of Chosen Ones, a wannabe chef teams up with a homicide detective to unravel an ancient mystery and take down supernatural assassins.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When Mari Gilbert's daughter disappears, police inaction drives her own investigation into the gated Long Island community where Shannan was last seen. Her search brings attention to over a dozen murdered sex workers.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Fyre
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: He promised supermodels and yachts, but delivered tents and cheese sandwiches. How one man engineered a music festival disaster.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Gentlemen's League
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: These former sports superstars were record-breaking Olympians; but on the soccer field, they’re all just middle-aged dads trying to do their best.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: These former sports superstars were record-breaking Olympians; but on the soccer field, they’re all just middle-aged dads trying to do their best.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Sudan, East Africa, 1980. A team of Israeli Mossad agents plans to rescue and transfer thousands of Ethiopian Jews to Israel. To do so, and to avoid raising suspicions from the inquisitive and ruthless authorities, they establish as a cover a fake diving resort by the Red Sea.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Teenage Bounty Hunters
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After joining forces with a veteran bounty hunter, sixteen-year-old fraternal twin sisters Sterling and Blair dive into the world of bail skipping baddies while still navigating the high stakes of teenage love and sex.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Thackeray
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Based on the life of Keshav Thackeray, an Indian politician who is also known as Balasaheb Thackeray.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Away
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: American astronaut Emma Green must leave her husband and teenage daughter behind to command an international space crew embarking upon a treacherous mission. A series about hope, humanity and how we need one another if we are to achieve impossible things.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Charlie Says
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Three young women were sentenced to death in the infamous Manson murder case, but when the death penalty was lifted, their sentence became life imprisonment. One young graduate student was sent in to teach them - and through her we witness their transformations as they face the reality of their horrific crimes.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Crip Camp: A Disability Revolution
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Down the road from Woodstock in the early 1970s, a revolution blossomed in a ramshackle summer camp for disabled teenagers, transforming their young lives and igniting a landmark movement.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Floor is Lava
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Teams compete to navigate rooms flooded with lava by leaping from chairs, hanging from curtains and swinging from chandeliers.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Julie and the Phantoms
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Teenage Julie finds her passion for music and life while helping the Phantoms -- a trio of ghostly guys -- become the band they were never able to be.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Polar
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When a retiring assassin realizes that he is the target of a hit, he winds up back in the game going head to head with a gang of younger, ruthless killers.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Spenser Confidential
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When two Boston police officers are murdered, ex-cop Spenser teams up with his no-nonsense roommate Hawk to take down criminals.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Circle
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Players start off isolated in an apartment, and with their online interactions as their only means of any communication. The players use a social media platform called "The Circle".

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Messiah
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A wary CIA officer investigates a charismatic man who sparks a spiritual movement and stirs political unrest. Who exactly is he? And what does he want?

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Doom: Annihilation
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A group of UAC Marines responds to a distress call from a top-secret scientific base on Phobos, a Martian moon, only to discover it's been overrun by demons.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Get Organized with The Home Edit
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Expert home organizers Clea and Joanna help celebrities and everyday clients edit, categorize and contain their clutter to create stunning spaces.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Daybreak
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Living his best life in post-apocalyptic LA, a slacker strives to find the girl of his dreams while outwitting mindless ghouls and cliquish gangs.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Pharmacist
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After his son's tragic death, a Louisiana pharmacist goes to extremes to expose the rampant corruption behind the opioid addiction crisis.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: American Pie Presents: Girls' Rules
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: It's Senior year at East Great Falls. Annie, Kayla, Michelle, and Stephanie decide to harness their girl power and band together to get what they want their last year of high school.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Cut Throat City
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Four boyhood friends return to New Orleans’ Lower Ninth Ward after Hurricane Katrina, to find their home decimated and prospects for work swept away. Turning to a local gangster for employment, the crew is hired to pull off a daring casino heist, right in the heart of the city.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Blood of Zeus
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a brewing war between the gods of Olympus and the titans, Heron, a commoner living on the outskirts of ancient Greece, becomes mankind's best hope of surviving an evil demon army, when he discovers the secrets of his past.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Schulz Saves America
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Comedian Andrew Schulz takes on the year's most divisive topics in this fearlessly unfiltered and irreverent four-part special.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Hoping to save his sick mother, a boy named Gunner and his friend Jo venture into the remote Wild Horse forest to search for a mythical figure who possesses the secret to immortality. data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: As a young scientist searches for a way to save a dying Earth, she finds a connection with a man who's racing to catch the last shuttle off the planet.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In this animated musical, a girl builds a rocket ship and blasts off, hoping to meet a mythical moon goddess.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Sheds light on an alternative approach to farming called “regenerative agriculture” that could balance our climate, replenish our vast water supplies, and feed the world.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An investigative look and analysis of gender disparity in Hollywood, featuring accounts from well-known actors, executives and artists in the Industry.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Young entrepreneurs aspiring to launch virtual dreams into reality compete for success and love in the cutthroat world of Korea's high-tech industry.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A New York City grad student moonlighting as a dominatrix enlists her gay BFF from high school to be her assistant.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A documentary film following the quest to understand the most mysterious objects in the universe, black holes.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A group of supernatural demon hunters known as "Counters," each with unique abilities, disguise themselves as employees of a noodle restaurant, while tracking down evil spirits that terrorize the mortal world.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A group of supernatural demon hunters known as "Counters," each with unique abilities, disguise themselves as employees of a noodle restaurant, while tracking down evil spirits that terrorize the mortal world.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When alien invaders capture Earth's superheroes, their kids must learn to work together to save their parents - and the planet.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Two teens facing personal struggles form a powerful bond as they embark on a cathartic journey chronicling the wonders of Indiana.

Tae-goo rejects the offer that results in the murder of his sister and niece. In revenge, Tae-goo brutally kills Chairman Doh and his men and flees to Jeju Island where he meets Jae-yeon, a terminally ill woman. Though, the henchman of the Bukseong gang, Executive Ma is mercilessly hunting Tae-goo to take revenge.
