data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sarah Cooper: Everything's Fine
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Comedian and Trump lip-synching sensation Sarah Cooper tackles politics, race and other light topics in a sketch special packed with celebrity guests.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Home Game
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This docuseries profiles unique and dangerous traditional sports from around the world, as well as the communities and cultures where they thrive.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: A Christmas Prince: The Royal Baby
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Christmas brings the ultimate gift to Aldovia: a royal baby. But first, Queen Amber must help her family and kingdom by finding a missing peace treaty.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Go! Go! Cory Carson
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Based on the Go. Go. toy line from VTech, children's series follows the adventures of Cory Carson.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Out of the Clear Blue Sky
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Returning to Earth as an imitator, the legendary Mexican artist Pedro Infante must prove that he is no longer a womanizer to enter paradise.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Gather
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A portrait of a growing movement amongst Indigenous Americans to reclaim their spiritual and cultural identities through obtaining sovereignty over their ancestral food systems, while battling against the historical trauma brought on by centuries of genocide.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bombay Rose
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: BOMBAY ROSE is a beautiful hand-painted animation created by award winning animator Gitanjali Rao. Amidst the bustle of a magnetic and multifaceted city, the budding love between two dreamers is tested by duty and religious divides.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Jo Pil-ho: The Dawning Rage
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: On the run from a dogged internal affairs agent, a corrupt cop reluctantly teams up with a defiant teen to unravel a conspiracy before it's too late.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Jo Pil-ho: The Dawning Rage
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: On the run from a dogged internal affairs agent, a corrupt cop reluctantly teams up with a defiant teen to unravel a conspiracy before it's too late.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Amy Schumer: Growing
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Amy Schumer's live stand-up set performed in Chicago where she jokes about marriage, pregnancy and personal growth.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Motichoor Chaknachoor
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A hilarious story of a 36-year-old jobless man Pushpender, trying to find a wife and Anita who's also looking for a husband. But there's a catch - Anita wants to settle abroad after marriage.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Chris D'Elia: No Pain
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Chris D'Elia takes the stage in Minneapolis to offer his thoughts on everything from self-censorship to problematic dolphins to lame mutant powers.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: A New York Christmas Wedding
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: As her Christmas Eve wedding draws near, Jennifer is visited by an angel and shown what could have been if she hadn't denied her true feelings for her childhood best friend.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Charlie's Colorforms City
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Charlie creates fun stories using different shapes, and he needs your help! Take off for adventures in outer space, the Wild West -- and right at home.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Nailed It! Spain
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: On this competition show, novice bakers try to avoid a fiasco while duplicating stunning sweets. At stake are a trophy and 5,000 euros.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Indoo Ki Jawani
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A feisty girl from Ghaziabad makes her profile on an online dating app and her left and right swipes on the app lead to hilarious consequences.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Door Ke Darshan
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When the matriarch of a dysfunctional family wakes up after a long induced coma, the members of the household set aside their differences to help her adapt to the changes.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Class of '83
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A hero policeman shunted to a punishment posting as the Dean of the police academy decides to punish the corrupt bureaucracy and its criminal allies in return by training five lethal assassin policemen.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Million Dollar Beach House
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The competition is fierce — and the drama undeniable — as a group of young and hungry agents try to seal the deal on luxury listings in the Hamptons.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Kabir Singh
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Kabir, a genius yet hostile medical student, falls in love with Preeti from his college. When Preeti's father spots the couple kissing, he opposes their relationship and decides to marry her off.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Seth Meyers: Lobby Baby
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: SNL alumnus and subversive master of late-night Seth Meyers comes out from behind the desk to share some lighthearted stories from his own life.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Firebrand
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: While she advocates for her female clients in divorce cases, a lawyer's trauma from sexual violence impacts her own marriage.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Deadly Switch
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When a foreign exchange student, Ana, studying abroad in America becomes the target of a dangerous stalker, she accepts the invitation to move in with her roommate's family in their idyllic town.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Whitney Cummings: Can I Touch It?
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In her fourth stand-up special, Whitney Cummings returns to her hometown of Washington, D.C., and riffs on modern feminism, relationships, technology and, of course, sex robots. She also brings a very special guest to say hi.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Hyena
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: To survive in a dog-eat-dog world, two rival lawyers with high-class clientele tear apart anything that stands in the way of their ambitions.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Hyena
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: To survive in a dog-eat-dog world, two rival lawyers with high-class clientele tear apart anything that stands in the way of their ambitions.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Jeff Dunham: Beside Himself
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The ventriloquist, Jeff Dunham, taped his second Netflix special in his hometown of Dallas, TX in the American Airlines Center. He returns with his normal cast of characters including Walter, Bubba J, Peanut, José Jalapeño on a Stick, Achmed the Dead Terrorist, and one of his newest additions Larry, a high strung, chain-smoking, on-again, off-again personal adviser to the President.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Uma Maheswara Ugra Roopasya
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Defeated and humiliated in a fight while trying to defuse a conflict among his fellow villagers, a photographer vows revenge on his attacker.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Gunjan Saxena: The Kargil Girl
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Inspired by the life of a fearless young officer who made history by becoming the first Indian female Air Force officer to fly in a combat zone during the 1999 Kargil War

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Nate: A One Man Show
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Tough talk takes a soft turn as Nate, played by comedian Natalie Palamides, explores humor, heartbreak, sexuality and consent — with a live audience.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Cargo
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Prahastha, a lonely astronaut, works in a spaceship. Every morning, his spaceship comes close to Earth and Cargos are delivered at the arrival bay. These Cargos are people who have just died on Earth and we learn that Prahastha works for Post Death Transition Services — a large, pioneering, bureaucratic company that stores, transitions, and recycles dead people for rebirth. Today, after many years, a young, popular astronaut — Yuvishka, trained in cutting edge technology, will join the spaceship as his assistant.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Uyare
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An aspiring pilot fights for her future -- and justice -- after surviving an acid attack from her abusive boyfriend.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Choked: Paisa Bolta Hai
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A bank employee weighed down by her jobless husband's debts - and her own broken dreams - finds a secret source of seemingly unlimited cash in her home.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Travis Scott: Look Mom I Can Fly
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: While crafting his Grammy-nominated album "Astroworld," Travis Scott juggles controversy, fatherhood and career highs in this intimate documentary.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Canvas
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After a heartbreaking loss, a grandfather struggling to reclaim his passion for painting finds the inspiration to create again.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Lies Within
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Kim Seo-hui’s life is changed forever when her politician father dies in a car crash and her husband disappears – all in one day. She enters the world of politics and join hands with small-town detective Jo Tae-sik to uncover the truth when she finds out that the car crash might not have been an accident after all.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Lies Within
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Kim Seo-hui’s life is changed forever when her politician father dies in a car crash and her husband disappears – all in one day. She enters the world of politics and join hands with small-town detective Jo Tae-sik to uncover the truth when she finds out that the car crash might not have been an accident after all.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Queer Eye: We're in Japan!
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The team of Queer Eye take their gorgeous, uplifting make-over skills to the Land of the Rising Sun.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Trap
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A man returns home to Atlanta to help and turn around his family's struggling restaurant with the help of a new chicken recipe.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Larry the Cable Guy: Remain Seated
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Larry the Cable Guy is back to Git R Done. Remain Seated, his latest solo special, will show you why this Grammy nominated, multi-platinum recording artist, and Billboard award winner is at the top of his game. Coming to you straight from the Rialto Square Theatre in Joliet, IL to your seat at home!

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Crystal Calls - Making The Dark Crystal: Age of Resistance
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Go behind the scenes with stars, puppeteers and creators as they bring Jim Henson's magical world of Thra back to life in a sweeping fantasy series.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Spooky Tale of Captain Underpants Hack-a-Ween
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When Melvin tries to cancel Halloween, clever best friends Harold and George create their own spooky holiday -- and it's a huge success.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Road to El Camino: Behind the Scenes of El Camino: A Breaking Bad Movie
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Aaron Paul, Vince Gilligan and other cast members, producers and crew share stories and footage from the making of "El Camino."

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Tiffany Haddish Presents: They Ready
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Tiffany Haddish introduces her favorite comedians in a series of stand-up performances.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ek Ladki Ko Dekha Toh Aisa Laga
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Sweety has to contend with her over-enthusiastic family that wants her to get married but the ultimate truth is that her love might not find acceptance in her family and society.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Los Briceño, una familia todo terreno
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This is the story of "La Chiqui", the youngest daughter of a family of truckers. In this universe of trucks, where macho men, popular music, and roadside love stories rule, "La Chiqui" gets pregnant. Her father kicks her out of her family home, forcing her to face a world where no one believes in her because she is a woman. However, she will manage to get ahead with her job, becoming a respected woman in her guild.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ben Platt: Live from Radio City Music Hall
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Backed by a full band and a ready wit, actor Ben Platt opens up a very personal songbook onstage -- numbers from his debut LP, "Sing to Me Instead."

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Larva Island Movie
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Back at home, Chuck relates the island shenanigans of his larva pals Red and Yellow to a skeptical reporter in this movie sequel to the hit cartoon.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Larva Island Movie
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Back at home, Chuck relates the island shenanigans of his larva pals Red and Yellow to a skeptical reporter in this movie sequel to the hit cartoon.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ken Jeong: You Complete Me, Ho
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In his first-ever stand-up special, Ken Jeong shares hilarious stories from his Hollywood career -- and reveals how "The Hangover" saved his life.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Larry Charles' Dangerous World of Comedy
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Legendary comedy writer and director Larry Charles travels the world in search of humor in the most unusual, unexpected and dangerous places.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Stand at Paxton County
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A military veteran comes home to find her father harassed by a sheriff intent on confiscating the livestock on their ranch under shady pretenses.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: YooHoo to the Rescue
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a series of magical missions, quick-witted YooHoo and his can-do crew travel the globe to help animals in need.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: YooHoo to the Rescue
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a series of magical missions, quick-witted YooHoo and his can-do crew travel the globe to help animals in need.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Murder to Mercy - The Cyntoia Brown Story
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After 16-year-old Cyntoia Brown is sentenced to life in prison, questions about her past, physiology and the law itself call her guilt into question.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Angela's Christmas Wish
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A determined Angela makes a wish to reunite her family in time for Christmas, then launches a plan to find her way from Ireland to Australia.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ramprasad Ki Tehrvi
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Ramprasad's entire family gathers under one roof for 13 days after his death, to perform and observe the Hindu traditions and rituals called the tehrvi. During the course, the family’s dynamics, politics, and insecurities come out, and then they realise that the importance of people and things are only evident in retrospect.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bulbbul
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A child bride grows up to be an enigmatic woman presiding over her household, harboring a painful past as supernatural murders of men plague her village.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Narcoworld: Dope Stories
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Documentary series that follows police officers as they hunt out drug smugglers around the world

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dolly Parton's Christmas on the Square
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A rich and nasty woman returns to her hometown to evict everyone but discovers the true meaning of Christmas thanks to the local townsfolk – and an actual angel. Features 14 original songs with music and lyrics by Dolly Parton!

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Rob Schneider: Asian Momma, Mexican Kids
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Former "Saturday Night Live" star Rob Schneider returns to the stage and shares his take on life, love and dinosaur dreams in this stand-up special. Ending with a surprise duet performance with his daughter, singer-songwriter Elle King, Rob talks about potty training his young daughters and his own pig potential.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Los Tigres del Norte at Folsom Prison
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The band Los Tigres del Norte visit both the male and female inmates of Folsom Prison. Inmates share their stories and how the music of Los Tigres del Norte speaks to them.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Tiffany Haddish: Black Mitzvah
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: On her 40th birthday, Tiffany Haddish drops a bombastic special studded with singing, dancing and raunchy reflections on her long road to womanhood.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: I'm with the Band: Nasty Cherry
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In an unfiltered, intimate docuseries, pop star mentor Charli XCX finds out what it takes to build -- and break -- a real, badass all-girl punk band.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Rogue Warfare: The Hunt
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The next installment of the Rogue Warfare Trilogy. Daniel has been captured and it is up to the TEAM to find him before it is to late.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: 99 Songs
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Challenged to compose 100 songs before he can marry the girl he loves, a tortured but passionate singer-songwriter embarks on a poignant musical journey.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: John Was Trying to Contact Aliens
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: John Shepherd spent 30 years trying to contact extraterrestrials by broadcasting music millions of miles into space. After giving up the search, he makes a different connection here on earth.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bennett's War
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After surviving an IED explosion in combat overseas, a young soldier with the Army Motorcycle Unit is medically discharged with a broken back and leg. Against all odds he trains to make an impossible comeback as a motocross racer in order to support his family.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Shikara
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In 1990, 4 lakh Kashmiri Pandits (Hindus) were forced to leave their home under the threat of life. Till today, they continue to live as refugees in their own country, in small refugee camps in the city of Jammu. Vidhu Vinod Chopra's 'Shikara' follows the story of Shiv and Shanti, two Kashmiri Pandits, chronicling their survival through 30 years of exile. In the current season of hate, love is all that keeps hope alive.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Man Who Feels No Pain
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Leveraging his ability to withstand pain, a young man trains to follow in the footsteps of his martial arts hero.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Boys in the Band: Something Personal
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Decades after his play first put gay life center stage, Mart Crowley joins the cast of the 2020 film to reflect on the story's enduring legacy.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Holiday Rush
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After his sudden firing, a popular radio DJ moves in with his aunt, bringing along his four spoiled children, and a plan to return to the airwaves.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: GAME ON: A Comedy Crossover Event
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Worlds collide in this special event featuring familiar faces, surprise cameos and stories of spirited competition from four different comedy series.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Love
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The story of a family and the various situations navigated by a husband and wife.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Body
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When the body of a powerful businesswoman goes missing from the morgue, the inspector-in-charge hunts for the truth. When he questions her husband he realizes that there is much more to the case than meets the eye.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Thambi
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Brother and sister who get separated and reunite years later when the brother has grown to be a criminal.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sillu Karupatti
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An anthology of four romantic stories across four age groups connected by that magical thread called love.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: K. D.
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: As his children plot his death to claim their inheritance, an aging patriarch leaves home, befriending a spunky boy who adds direction to his life.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Torbaaz
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: At an Afghanistan refugee camp, an ex-army doctor seeks to bring children joy through cricket and soon realizes that the stakes go beyond the sport.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ma Rainey's Black Bottom: A Legacy Brought to Screen
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Viola Davis, Denzel Washington, George C. Wolfe and more share the heart, soul and history that brought August Wilson's timeless play to the screen.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Iliza Shlesinger: Unveiled
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Comedian Iliza Shlesinger dissects her recent wedding with riffs on screeching bachelorette parties, that creepy garter removal tradition and more.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Vikruthi
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Mistaking the sleeping passenger on his train for a drunk, a young man posts a picture of him online, unaware of his impulsive act's ugly repercussions.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Manmadhudu 2
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Under pressure to marry, a perennial bachelor hires a much younger woman to act as his fiancée, but her bond with his family throws his plan for a loop.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Cops and Robbers
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Animation and activism unite in this multimedia spoken-word response to police brutality and racial injustice.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Miss India
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Uprooted to America, an aspiring Indian entrepreneur confronts disapproval, sexism and rivalry as she draws from her culture to start a tea business.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dance Dreams: Hot Chocolate Nutcracker
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This documentary spotlights Debbie Allen's career and follows her group of dance students as they prepare for Allen's annual "Hot Chocolate Nutcracker," a reimagining of the classic ballet.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Once Again
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After a chance phone call leads to daily conversations, a widowed restaurant owner and a lonely film actor plan to finally meet in person.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: True: Terrific Tales
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Through the magic of the Story Spinner, True and her friends create their own versions of Pinocchio, Little Red Riding Hood and other classic tales.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dragons: Rescue Riders: Hunt for the Golden Dragon
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The Rescue Riders have been asked to find a precious golden dragon egg, and keep it safe from evil pirates.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Vir Das: For India
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: From the Vedas to Vasco de Gama to vacuous Bollywood plotlines, comedian Vir Das celebrates the history of India with his one-of-a-kind perspective.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Shimla Mirchi
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: While on holiday, Avi meets Naina and falls in love with her. Smitten, he decides to stay and work in her cafe. He confesses his love in a letter, however it's Naina's mother who mistakenly reads it.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Oh! Baby
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A 70-year-old woman transforms into her 24-year-old self after she's photographed at a studio, changing her life and those of the people around her forever.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Penalty
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A story of a North-east Indian football player who's fighting day and night with the society in order to achieve his dreams. The film covers all kinds of layers in one single film from negative backlashes, social pressures to a complete change over in one's life.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Singapore Social
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Peer into the lives of young Singaporeans as they defy expectations and traverse the tricky terrain of career, romance and family.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Living Undocumented
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Eight undocumented families' fates roller-coast as the United States' immigration policies are transformed.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: All in My Family
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After starting a family of his very own in the United States, a gay filmmaker documents his loving, traditional Chinese family's process of acceptance.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Albert  Pinto Ko Gussa Kyun Aata Hai?
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Albert Pinto goes missing one day and his girlfriend and family start making rounds at the police station to track him down. Unknown to them, he is on his way to Goa to carry out his first assignment as a hitman.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Spirit Riding Free: Spirit of Christmas
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Lucky and her friends venture into town on Christmas Eve in an attempt to fulfill their holiday plans. But when distractions lead to delays, they must figure out how to get home in time for Christmas in the middle of a serious snowstorm!

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: AK vs AK
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After a public spat with a movie star,  a disgraced director retaliates by kidnapping the actor's daughter, filming the search for her in real-time.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Varane Avashyamund
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A divorced woman trying to get hired as a French tutor and teaching classical dance, and she has a daughter. Her brother Manuel also resides in a flat in Chennai. Their next door neighbours are Unnikrishnan, a retired Major who has a pet dog, Prabhakaran and Bibeesh who lives with a serial-actress aunt (not related by blood) and his young school going brother. The story revolves around the divorced mother and daughter finding happiness of love in their own ways. The film explores commonality of romantic love in different stages of life.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Fabulous Lives of Bollywood Wives
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Cameras follow the banter and bonding between four fun-loving women from Bollywood's inner circle as they juggle professions, family and friendship.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Chopsticks
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A gifted but insecure woman is in for a transformative experience when she enlists the help of an enigmatic con artist to recover her stolen car

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Kappela
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Set in the village areas of Wayanad, Malappuram and Kannur, Kappela revolves around an ordinary, innocent girl who comes to Kozhikode city from a high range area called Poovarmala.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Holiday Home Makeover with Mr. Christmas
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Mr. Christmas, a veteran in the interior design industry with a healthy obsession with the holiday season, takes you behind the scenes as he puts his design expertise and vast Christmas collection to good use.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: After the Raid
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A large immigration raid in a small Tennessee town leaves emotional fallout as well as far-reaching questions about justice, faith and humanity.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Hasmukh
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A timid, small-town comedian's long-awaited big break takes a dark turn when he realizes committing murder is the only way to keep his onstage mojo.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Chaman Bahar
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An ambitious young man, in a small town in Central India, sets up a paan shop to a floundering start. His fortunes start to change dramatically when a family shifts in the house across the road. Hordes of boys start following the teenage girl from the family and set up an "adda" at Billu's shop. His business flourishes tremendously but Billu is now more unhappy than ever, as he has fallen for the girl himself!

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sugar Rush Christmas
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: It's everything you love about "Sugar Rush" -- with a holly jolly holiday twist -- in this Christmas-themed spin on competitive baking.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sethum Aayiram Pon
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Meeting after many years, a makeup artist and her grandmother revisit tensions from an old family feud that still hangs heavy between them.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: ReMastered: The Lion's Share
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After discovering the family of Solomon Linda, the writer of "The Lion Sleeps Tonight," a reporter tries to help them fight for fair compensation.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ray Romano: Right Here, Around the Corner
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Ray Romano cut his stand-up teeth at the Comedy Cellar in New York. Now, in his first comedy special in 23 years, he returns to where it all began.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Arsenio Hall: Smart and Classy
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In his first stand-up special, Arsenio Hall discusses getting older, the changing times and culture, social issues and even bothersome baby toes.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Cricket Fever: Mumbai Indians
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Follow Indian Premier League champions Mumbai Indians through the 2018 season in this series featuring insider insights and intense cricket action.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Guna 369
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Guna is a happy-go-lucky guy who believes the solution to solving issues is not through violence but through compromise.When he is framed for a crime he didn't commit by someone close to him, Guna is left with no choice and forced to the extremes to prove his innocence.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Buddi
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The Buddis bounce, spin, glide and giggle through their magical world, learning new things and sharing the joy of friendship.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Chico Bon Bon: Monkey with a Tool Belt
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: STEM children's series focusing on construction and how mechanical things work.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Felipe Esparza: Bad Decisions
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Two live performances, one in English and one in Spanish. No matter the language, Felipe Esparza is muy muy.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mighty Little Bheem
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An innocent toddler’s boundless curiosity -- and extraordinary might -- lead to mischief and adventure in his small Indian town.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bulbul Can Sing
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Coming-of-age drama about a young girl living in rural India, fighting her way through love and loss as she figures out who she really is.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Maska
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Determined to make it in showbiz, an aspiring young actor considers turning his back on the beloved Irani café run by his family for generations.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ginny Weds Sunny
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Delhi girl Ginny lives with her matchmaker mother and is set up with Sunny, who has given up on the idea of love. He just wants to get married and settle down. But, the match is not that simple. As Ginny meets Sunny, there’s a lot more that comes to the fore than previously imagined in this tale of love, life, weddings and music.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dark City Beneath the Beat
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Dark City Beneath The Beat is an audiovisual experience that defines the soundscape of Baltimore city. Inspired by an all original Baltimore club music soundtrack, the film spotlights local club artists, DJs, dancers, producers, and Baltimore’s budding creative community as they are realizing their life dreams. Rhythmic and raw, these stories illustrate the unique characteristics of the city’s landscape and social climate through music, poetry, and dance. From the city’s social climate to its creative LGBTQ community, Dark City Beneath The Beat showcases Baltimore club music as a positive subculture in a city overshadowed by trauma, drugs, and violence.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Car: Road to Revenge
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a dilapidated cyberpunk city plagued by crime and corruption, an unscrupulous District Attorney is savagely murdered and tossed out of a building onto his brand new car. Mysteriously, the District Attorney and his car come back to life as a single being with a thirst for vengeance. The eerie driver-less car embarks on a vicious rampage exacting revenge on the criminals who murdered him. The Car: Road to Revenge is the stylized sequel to the unconventional horror cult classic The Car (1977), and features an homage to the original with the return of Ronny Cox as the Mechanic.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Jezebel
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A true story. In the last days of her mother’s life, 19-year-old Tiffany crashes with five family members in a Las Vegas studio apartment. In order to make ends meet, her sister, a phone sex operator, introduces her to the world of fetish cam girls.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Kenny Sebastian: The Most Interesting Person in the Room
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Fusing his musical and stand-up chops, Kenny Sebastian gets analytical about frumpy footwear, flightless birds and his fear of not being funny enough.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Father Soldier Son
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When Sgt. First Class Brian Eisch is critically wounded in Afghanistan, it sets him and his sons on a journey of love, loss, redemption and legacy.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Juanita
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Fed up with her deadbeat grown kids and marginal urban existence, Juanita takes a Greyhound bus to Paper Moon, Montana - where she reinvents herself and finds her mojo.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: A Family Reunion Christmas
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: M'Dear and her sisters struggle to keep their singing act together before a church Christmas pageant while Grandpa teaches the kids a valuable lesson.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Chippa
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: On the eve of his tenth birthday, when Chippa receives a letter for his long-absent father, he decides to leave his pavement abode to find out more.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Fire in Paradise
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In this documentary, survivors recall the catastrophic 2018 Camp Fire, which razed the town of Paradise and became California’s deadliest wildfire.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bread Barbershop
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a town filled with food, Bread is a master cake decorator who gives life-changing makeovers that will put any customer in an amazing mood.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bread Barbershop
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a town filled with food, Bread is a master cake decorator who gives life-changing makeovers that will put any customer in an amazing mood.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Spookley and the Christmas Kittens
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Spookley and Mistletoe encounter three stray kittens for whom they must brave a raging winter storm to find a home.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Colin Quinn: Red State, Blue State
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Stand-up comedian Colin Quinn calls out the hypocrisies of the left and the right in this special based on his politically charged Off-Broadway show.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Malibu Rescue: The Next Wave
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: It’s summer again, and everyone’s favorite Junior Rescuers, The Flounders, are back at Tower 2. With the International Junior Rescue Championships headed to Southern California, the eyes of the entire planet are on Malibu Beach. But when Team USA falls victim to a bout of food poisoning, it’s up to Tyler, Dylan, Eric, Lizzie and Gina to represent their country in the world's most extreme lifeguard challenge!

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Kaali Khuhi
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When a restless spirit curses a Punjab village that has a history of female infanticide, the town's fate lies in the hands of a 10-year old girl, Shivangi.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: George Lopez: We'll Do It for Half
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Comedian George Lopez tackles the future and the past of Latinx culture in America, touching on immigration, his tough relatives, aging and much more.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bhangra Paa Le
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Jaggi comes from a Punjabi background and he aspires to take the popular Punjabi dance form of 'Bhangra' to an international platform and passionately works towards his dream. He meets his college rival in Simi and they both compete with each other to win the international dance competition.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Milestone
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: As soon as veteran driver Ghalib’s truck touches the 500,000 kilometers mark - a record at his company - he is struck by a sudden pain in his back. As Ghalib struggles with this ache, an existential threat begins to overwhelm him when he is asked to train a young new driver.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bhaag Beanie Bhaag
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Facing disapproving parents, a knotty love life and her own inner critic, an aspiring comic ditches her cushy but unsatisfying life to pursue stand-up.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Saavat
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The journey of a woman who overcomes her personal anguish to help deliver justice to another woman trapped in a web of deceit and deception.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dorasani
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Dorasani explores the periodic tale of love between a rich lady Devaki and a poor boy Raju.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Axone
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This bittersweet comedy follows immigrants in Delhi who are attempting to organise a wedding party, but soon find everything going wrong.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: A Go! Go! Cory Carson Christmas
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When a familiar-looking stranger crashes in without a memory, cory helps him remember the magic of Christmas to save the holiday for everyone

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: 90 ML
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Thamara, Paru, Kajal and Suganya are four friends who are rather tired of their uneventful routine. However, things take a turn for the better with the arrival of the spirited and outgoing Rita, a young woman who encourages them to live their lives to the fullest.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Adam Devine: Best Time of Our Lives
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Frenetic comic Adam Devine talks teen awkwardness, celebrity encounters, his "Pitch Perfect" audition and more in a special from his hometown of Omaha.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Kaagar
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a small Maharashtrian town, a woman's rise in the political hierarchy creates ripples across the social-political spectrum. Directed by Makarand Mane, KaaGaR stars Rinku Rajguru in the lead role.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bypass Road
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The story revolves around a young man, Vikram, who is a fashion prodigy. The story is layered with a murder in town.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ahaan
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Jilted by his wife, a man with OCD finds eye opening common ground and camaraderie with his neighbor, a young man with Down Syndrome.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Deon Cole: Cole Hearted
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Embracing his belief that comedy is the last raw form of expression, Deon Cole explains the right time to thank Jesus and the wrong time to say "welp."

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mere Pyare Prime Minister
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A story about four children living in a Mumbai slum in India. An eight-year old Kanhu writes a letter to the Prime Minister after a dramatic incident with his mother.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Netflix Afterparty: The Best Shows of The Worst Year
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: David Spade, Fortune Feimster and London Hughes welcome guests from Tiger King, Emily in Paris, The Queen's Gambit, and more.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: You Are My Home
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This drama follows the relationship of a heartbroken woman and a young immigrant girl who has lost her mother at the border, coming together just before Christmas.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Jai Mummy Di
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Jai Mummy Di is a light-hearted family comedy that portrays the trials and tribulations a couple has to undergo due to the dynamics between their respective mothers.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Dolly Kitty and Those Twinkling Stars
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A disillusioned Delhi wife (Dolly), and her new-in-town cousin (Kitty), navigate damning secrets, dreams and their thorny dynamic on their respective roads to freedom.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Giving Voice
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Every year, thousands of high schoolers enter the August Wilson monologue competition for a chance to perform on Broadway. This film follows these students, examining how Wilson and his characters speak to a new generation, inspiring them to listen to his words and find their own voice.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Kevin Hart's Guide to Black History
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Kevin Hart highlights the fascinating contributions of black history's unsung heroes in this entertaining -- and educational -- comedy special.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: London Hughes: To Catch A D*ck
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: London Hughes, the sauciest comedian to come out of the UK, takes us on a brilliant and bold tour of her d*ck catching history.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Voices of Fire
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Pharrell Williams's hometown community leaders attempt to build one of the world's most inspiring gospel choirs.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Magic School Bus Rides Again: The Frizz Connection
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Lightning splits the Magic School Bus into three pieces, scattering the class across the globe with different versions of Ms. Frizzle aboard each bus!

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Country Ever After
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Country artist Coffey Anderson and his wife, hip-hop dancer Criscilla, juggle family life, career goals and tests of faith in this reality series.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Velvet Colección: Grand Finale
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Christmas 1969: the upcoming sale of Velvet brings the former and current staff together in Madrid for good memories, a second chance and a new beginning.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Aaviri
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A thriller film directed by Ravi Babu, starring Ravi Babu and Neha Chauhan in the lead roles.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Claudia Kishi Club
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Asian American creatives pay passionate tribute to the iconic, stereotype-busting "Baby-Sitters Club" character in this heartfelt documentary short.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: A Trash Truck Christmas
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When Santa crash-lands in the junkyard on Christmas Eve, Hank, Trash Truck and their animal friends all have a hand in rescuing the holiday for everyone.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sitara
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A Bangaldeshi housewife crosses the border to start her a new life where she struggles to deal with the pain and betrayal of her own family and making a living on her own.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Léa & I
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Best friends travel though Latin America meeting shamans, experimenting with plant medicines, and wondering about what makes a life well-lived when one of them might have half the time to live it.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mundina Nildana
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Three different people with three different goals set out on a liberating journey that is supposed to take them to their next destination in life.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bookmarks: Celebrating Black Voices
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Celebrity readers share children's books by Black authors to spark kid-friendly conversations about empathy, equality, self-love and antiracism.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Go! Go! Cory Carson: The Chrissy
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The Carson kids win a talent show with a dance that Cory created. But when "The Chrissy" catches on, his little sister gets all of the attention.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Guddiyan Patole
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Guddiyan Patole is a Punjabi movie starring Sonam Bajwa, Gurnam Bhullar and Nirmal Rishi in prominent roles. It is a drama directed by Vijay Kumar Arora, with Jagdeep Sidhu as writer, forming part of the crew.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Kaamyaab
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The human drama is based on an interesting premise of a seasoned character actor who decides to come out of retirement and begin a quest for a record of some sorts, that elusive 500th role, the one for which he shall be remembered forever.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: A Go! Go! Cory Carson Summer Camp
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Cory's spending the summer at Camp Friendship with his best friend, Freddie. But jealousy flares when Freddie brings his cousin Rosie along for the ride.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Zoya Factor
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An advertising agency executive Zoya Singh Solanki meets the Indian cricket team and ends up becoming their lucky charm at the 2011 Cricket World Cup.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Yeh Ballet
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Discovered by an eccentric ballet master, two gifted but underprivileged Mumbai teens face bigotry and disapproval as they pursue their dancing dreams.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Andhaghaaram
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: As a blind librarian, dispirited cricketer and desolate psychiatrist each seek retribution and release, their lives overlap under eerie influences.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Southern Survival
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The BattlBox crew tests out products designed to help people survive dangerous situations, including explosions, natural disasters and intruders.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Super Monsters Save Christmas
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: On Christmas Eve, the Super Monsters get together to make decorations, but end up having to find Santa's missing reindeer in order to save their holiday.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: I'm Leaving Now
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: After 16 years in Brooklyn, working three low-paying jobs and sending the bulk of his earnings to his wife and children, undocumented immigrant Felipe decides to return home to his family in Mexico. But when he informs them of his plans, he discovers that they've squandered the money, are deeply in debt and don’t want him to return. They need him to stay in the U.S. and continue to earn.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ludo
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Ludo is about the butterfly effect and how, despite all the chaos and crowd of the world, all our lives are inextricably connected. From a resurfaced sex tape to a rogue suitcase of money, four wildly different stories overlap at the whims of fate, chance and one eccentric criminal.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mallesham
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The life of Padma Shri winner Chintakindi Mallesham, who invented the ASU machine that processes yarn for sarees mechanically, is being recreated in this biopic.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mike Epps: Only One Mike
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A 2019 stand-up comedy special by comedian Mike Epps, where he tackles sexual misconduct, special education, aging body parts and more.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Styling Hollywood
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Stylist and interior designer Jason Bolden and husband Adair Curtis of JSN Studio make the magic happen on the red carpet and at home for A-listers.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Birders
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Bird watchers on both sides of the U.S.-Mexico border share their enthusiasm for protecting and preserving some of the world's most beautiful species.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: A Tale of Two Kitchens
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Two countries, two restaurants, one vision. At Gabriela Cámara's acclaimed Contramar in Mexico City, the welcoming, uniformed waiters are as beloved by diners as the menu featuring fresh, local seafood caught within 24 hours. The entire staff sees themselves as part of an extended family. Meanwhile at Cala in San Francisco, Cámara hires staff from different backgrounds and cultures, including ex-felons and ex-addicts, who view the work as an important opportunity to grow as individuals. A Tale of Two Kitchens explores the ways in which a restaurant can serve as a place of both dignity and community.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Asura Guru
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Shakti, who becomes obsessed with money from childhood, goes on to become a tech-savvy thief. However, he becomes a changed man due to certain circumstances when cops nab him.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Kaake Da Viyah
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A guy's family wants him to get married but it is harder than he thought. On one hand, his grandmother wants him to get married to a girl of her choice, and on the other, his mother is eager to select a girl for him. On top of that, he is already in love with a girl. His dilemma of being stuck between three women forms the crux of the story.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: House Arrest
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A world-weary man's self-imposed home confinement becomes a comedy of errors with the simultaneous arrivals of a peculiar package and a curious journalist.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bombairiya
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: It follows the story of Meghna, who gets embroiled in a series of events after her phone gets stolen.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Rooting for Roona
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In rural India, a child with hydrocephalus gets a chance at life-changing surgery after her photos go viral. This documentary charts her journey.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Uriyadi 2
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A young man struggles for justice for the victims who are affected by the chemical plant leakage which lead to many deaths in the village.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Irandam Ulagaporin Kadaisi Gundu
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A hardworking lorry driver who works at an old paper mart learns about the presence of a bomb and does everything he can to stop it from exploding.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Carlos Almaraz: Playing with Fire
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Explore the life of Carlos Almaraz, a Chicano activist, sexual outlaw, and visionary painter of some of the most unforgettable images of Southern California.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Hamid
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Eight year-old Hamid learns that 786 is God's number and decides to try and reach out to God, by dialing this number. He wants to talk to his father, who his mother tells him has gone to Allah. One fine day the phone call is answered.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Life Overtakes Me
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Hundreds of refugee children in Sweden, who have fled with their families from extreme trauma, have become afflicted with 'uppgivenhetssyndrom,' or Resignation Syndrome. Facing deportation, they withdraw from the world into a coma-like state, as if frozen, for months, or even years.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: David A. Arnold Fat Ballerina
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Stand up comedy special featuring David A. Arnold.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Upstarts
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Hoping to do good while making millions, three college graduates create a startup. But as business begins to flourish, their own bond starts to fray.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Mehandi Circus
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A music shop owner falls in love with a girl from a circus troupe that visits his village, but caste and class stand in the way.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sarvam Thaala Mayam
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Peter who tries to find his place in the world of classical Indian music embarks on a journey that helps him evolve personally, spiritually and musically.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Spirit Riding Free: Ride Along Adventure
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Join Lucky and her friends on an interactive mission to save Maricela’s beloved mare from greedy horse thieves who've taken her captive with a wild herd.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: American Factory: A Conversation with the Obamas
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Barack and Michelle Obama talk with the directors of the documentary American Factory about the importance of storytelling and the impact of their film.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Amit Tandon: Family Tandoncies
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: From the death of romance in marriage to the injustices of modern-day parenting, Amit Tandon shares wisdom and wisecracks as a battle-scarred family guy.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: 15 August
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: On India's Independence Day, a zany mishap in a Mumbai chawl disrupts a young love story while compelling the residents to unite in aid of a little boy.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sur Sapata
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: This story is about young boys who have capabilities of playing KABADDI but the society is against them, they took this as challenge and their journey starts from here. Boys went out of the box after facing hardship and being discouraged from their guru and parents to win hearts of people. To feel the thrill, motivation, entertainment, comedy, sportsmanship; come and watch movie along with your family and friends.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Super Monsters Back to School
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Lobo's cousin Vida moves to town, Lobo shows her his favorite places around town, and the next day Vida has her first day of school.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Marjoun and the Flying Headscarf
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A teenager in Arkansas searches for identity in the headscarf and a motorcycle in the aftermath of her father's imprisonment. Set in 2006, the film explores the results of Arab and Muslim Americans being increasingly detained for "guilt by association". The film links the civil rights struggle of Arab/Muslim Americans with that of African Americans through Marjoun's attendance of Central High School. It weaves her story into the lineage of the Little Rock Nine. This film is set also at Magnolia Grove Monastery in Mississippi. This Zen Buddhist monastery has been established in the tradition of the friendship of Dr. Martin Luther King, Jr. and Zen Master Thich Nhat Hanh, bringing together the themes of civil rights movements and interfaith practice. This is an expansion of the short film by the same title, that was an official selection of the Sundance Film Festival.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Kilometers and Kilometers
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When a debt-ridden man reluctantly agrees to drive an American tourist around India, their stark differences lead to bickering… and unexpected bonding.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ghosts of Sugar Land
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Shocked when their friend embraces extremism, a group of Muslim Americans in Texas recount their time with him and theories about his fate.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Pinkfong & Baby Shark's Space Adventure
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Follow PinkFong and Baby Shark’s space journey as they visit mysterious planets to help find the special star for PinkFong!

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Pinkfong & Baby Shark's Space Adventure
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Follow PinkFong and Baby Shark’s space journey as they visit mysterious planets to help find the special star for PinkFong!

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Pinkfong & Baby Shark's Space Adventure
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Follow PinkFong and Baby Shark’s space journey as they visit mysterious planets to help find the special star for PinkFong!

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Maniyarayile Ashokan
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When his unlucky horoscope doesn't bode well for his future wife, an earnest bachelor goes to surprising lengths to get the family he's always wanted. Will the stars align?

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: To Be of Service
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A documentary film about veterans with PTSD who find that, after other treatments fall short, a service dog helps them return to an independent-feeling life.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: What are the Odds?
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A drama film directed by Megha Ramaswamy, starring Priyanka Bose, Manu Rishi Chadha and Yashaswini Dayama in the lead roles.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: DeMarcus Family Rules
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Rascal Flatts bassist Jay DeMarcus and ex-beauty queen Allison DeMarcus write their own rules for juggling family and fun in this reality show.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Super Monsters: Dia de los Monsters
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The Super Monsters celebrate Día de los Muertos in Vida’s hometown with her magical family, some new monster friends and a spook-tacular parade!

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: RK Nagar
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: RK Nagar is an upcoming Indian Tamil comedy film, written and directed by Saravana Rajan. The film features Vaibhav and Sana Althaf in the lead roles, while Sampath Raj plays a supporting role.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Evvarikee Cheppoddu
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Hari and Harathi are in love, but Harathi's father won't agree to their relationship because of their caste differences.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Yours Sincerely, Kanan Gill
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Revisiting life goals set in a letter written as a teen to his future self, comedian Kanan Gill reports back on if he's lived up to his own expectations.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ladies Up
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Rising India-based comics Prashasti Singh, Kaneez Surka, Supriya Joshi, and Niveditha Prakasam bring no-holds-barred humor to this stand up series

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Ainu Mosir
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Kanto, 14, a descendant of Japan's indigenous Ainu people, decides to visit a hole in the forest -- a path to the other side of the world where dead people live, hoping to see his deceased father.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Bhai - Vyakti Ki Valli 2
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The second part of the P.L Deshpande biopic which starts off where the first one left off and essays the achievements of the writer.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Free Rein: Valentine's Day
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Love is in the air as Zoe and friends go on a quest to find a fabled Maid's Stone. But when rivalry blinds them to danger, it's Raven to the rescue!

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The App That Stole Christmas
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A tech entrepreneur's Christmas shopping app is a smashing success, but he starts to realize his invention might be ruining the holiday spirit.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Park Na-rae: Glamour Warning
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Korea's beloved comedian and favorite big sister figure talks sex, relationships and celebrity life. And she's sassier and dirtier than ever before.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Park Na-rae: Glamour Warning
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Korea's beloved comedian and favorite big sister figure talks sex, relationships and celebrity life. And she's sassier and dirtier than ever before.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: True Tunes
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: True and her friends are dropping sweet, silly beats with freshly modern music videos set to the sounds of classic nursery rhyme songs.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Rakkhosh
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The movie explores the horrors and fantasies of a patient trapped in a mental asylum.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Motu Patlu in the Game of Zones
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A board game becomes all too real for buddies Motu and Patlu when they get transported into its world of monsters, magic and mayhem.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: After Maria
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Strong Puerto Rican women forced to flee the island after Hurricane Maria have bonded like family in a FEMA hotel in the Bronx. They seek stability in their new life as forces try to pull them apart.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Nenjamundu Nermaiyundu Odu Raja
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Two ambitious youngsters who make a living through a YouTube channel agree to perform a few tasks for a businessman when the latter offers them huge money.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Miranda Sings Live... Your Welcome
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Viral video star Miranda Sings and her real-world alter ego Colleen Ballinger share the stage in a special packed with music, comedy and "magichinry."

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Thottappan
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When his partner in crime goes missing, a small-time crook’s life is transformed as he dedicates himself to raising the daughter his friend left behind.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Super Monsters: Santa's Super Monster Helpers
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When Santa needs serious help prepping all of his presents, the Super Monsters lend a hand - and some monster magic - to get every gift out on time.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: High End Yaariyaan
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: High End Yaariyaan is a tale of 3 friends Ranjit Bawa, Jassie Gill, and Ninja who lives abroad. The story narrates how their friendship has evolved over a period of time and the struggles they each go through while living away from their homeland.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Gray Man
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When a shadowy CIA agent uncovers damning agency secrets, he's hunted across the globe by a sociopathic rogue operative who's put a bounty on his head.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Resident Evil
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Nearly three decades after the discovery of the T-virus, an outbreak reveals the Umbrella Corporation's dark secrets. Based on the horror franchise.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: RRR
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A fictional history of two legendary revolutionaries' journey away from home before they began fighting for their country in the 1920s.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Sing 2
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Buster and his new cast now have their sights set on debuting a new show at the Crystal Tower Theater in glamorous Redshore City. But with no connections, he and his singers must sneak into the Crystal Entertainment offices, run by the ruthless wolf mogul Jimmy Crystal, where the gang pitches the ridiculous idea of casting the lion rock legend Clay Calloway in their show. Buster must embark on a quest to find the now-isolated Clay and persuade him to return to the stage.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Man from Toronto
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In a case of mistaken identity, the world’s deadliest assassin, known as the Man from Toronto, and a New York City screw-up are forced to team up after being confused for each other at an Airbnb.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Persuasion
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Living with her snobby family on the brink of bankruptcy, Anne Elliot is an unconforming woman with modern sensibilities. When Frederick Wentworth - the dashing one she once sent away - crashes back into her life, Anne must choose between putting the past behind her or listening to her heart when it comes to second chances.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Hustle
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A basketball scout discovers a phenomenal street ball player while in Spain and sees the prospect as his opportunity to get back into the NBA.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Spiderhead
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In the near future, convicts are offered the chance to volunteer as medical subjects to shorten their sentence. One such subject for a new drug capable of generating feelings of love begins questioning the reality of his emotions.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Lincoln Lawyer
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Sidelined after an accident, hotshot Los Angeles lawyer Mickey Haller restarts his career — and his trademark Lincoln — when he takes on a murder case.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: The Sea Beast
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: When a young girl stows away on the ship of a legendary sea monster hunter, they launch an epic journey into uncharted waters - and make history to boot.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Girl in the Picture
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A young mother’s mysterious death and her son’s subsequent kidnapping blow open a decades-long mystery about the woman’s true identity, and the murderous federal fugitive at the center of it all.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: How to Change Your Mind
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Author Michael Pollan leads the way in this docuseries exploring the history and uses of psychedelics, including LSD, psilocybin, MDMA and mescaline.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: God's Favorite Idiot
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Clark Thompson, a midlevel tech-support employee, finds love with co-worker Amily Luck at exactly the same time he becomes the unwitting messenger of God. Also, there's rollerskating, a lake of fire and an impending apocalypse.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Keep Sweet: Pray and Obey
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In interviews and rare home video footage, ex-FLDS members share the truth about their isolated community — and the events that pushed them to leave.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Umma
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Amanda and her daughter live a quiet life on an American farm, but when the remains of her estranged mother arrive from Korea, Amanda becomes haunted by the fear of turning into her own mother.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: D.B. Cooper: Where Are You?!
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: The series looks at the 50-year quest to find the mysterious man who hijacked a Northwest Airlines passenger jet in November 1971 and escaped with $200,000, never to be seen again.  Five decades. Few clues. Too many suspects. The identity of skyjacker D.B. Cooper remains one of the greatest mysteries of the 20th century.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Boo, Bitch
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Two senior BFFs make a last-ditch attempt to be seen. But when one of them becomes a ghost, she'll need to really live her best life — while she can.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Operation Mincemeat
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In 1943, two British intelligence officers concoct Operation Mincemeat, wherein their plan to drop a corpse with false papers off the coast of Spain would fool Nazi spies into believing the Allied forces were planning to attack by way of Greece rather than Sicily.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Midnight Mass
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: An isolated island community experiences miraculous events - and frightening omens - after the arrival of a charismatic, mysterious young priest.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Inventing Anna
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A journalist with a lot to prove investigates the case of Anna Delvey, the Instagram-legendary German heiress who stole the hearts of New York’s social scene – and stole their money as well.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Anatomy of a Scandal
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: A sexual consent scandal amongst British privileged elite and the women caught up in its wake.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Arcane
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: Amid the stark discord of twin cities Piltover and Zaun, two sisters fight on rival sides of a war between magic technologies and clashing convictions.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Squid Game

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Pray Away
data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.description: In the 1970s, five men struggling with being gay in their Evangelical church started a bible study to help each other leave the "homosexual lifestyle." They quickly received over 25,000 letters from people asking for help and formalized as Exodus International, the largest and most controversial conversion therapy organization in the world. But leaders struggled with a secret: their own “same-sex attractions” never went away. After years as Christian superstars in the religious right, many of these men and women have come out as LGBTQ, disavowing the very movement they helped start. Focusing on the dramatic journeys of former conversion therapy leaders, current members, and a survivor, PRAY AWAY chronicles the “ex gay" movement’s rise to power, persistent influence, and the profound harm it causes.

data-8cf064338105a22427fdf725b81e4445.title: Moxie
